VALUES
	(1,'.hack//Legend of the Twilight','Plot Sumary:\r\nSet four years after the .hack games, the anime folows the adventures of a pair of twins–Rena and Shugo. The story takes place in a fictional MORPG caled The World. After wining a contest, Rena is in posesion of a pair of avatars in the design of the legendary .hackers known as Kite and Black Rose. After an od ocurence, Shugo obtains the Twilight Bracelet. Shugo embarks on an adventure to find “Aura” and unravel the mystery of the Twilight Bracelet. An item that both aids and hinders those involved with it. Along the way, Shugo and Rena met many friends. Together, the friends play together in The World, but the fun quickly ends when Rena is kiled by a monster and goes into a coma. Shugo and friends franticaly search for a solution, whilst a group of four children are planing something terible on the outside world. What wil become of Rena and Shugo, during their adventure in “The World”?\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction/Fantasy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hacklegend-of-the-twilight.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:44:41'),
	(2,'.hack//Liminality','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe story folows thre girls, Mai Minase, Yuki Aihara, and Kyoko Tohno, and a former C Corp. director of the Japanese version of The World, Junichiro Tokuoka. They investigate as to why several people have falen into a coma while playing the game. The amine starts with the colapse of Mai and her boyfriend, (Tomonari Kasumi). It is son revealed that she heard a certain sound (which is also present at important points in .hack/Sign) shortly before colapsing. She later wakes up to the same sound, the sound that tunes. “A In C Minor”. Through the knowledge of al the the characters, the constantly search for the answer to why there have ben so many victims due to “The World”. Wil they be able to batle something that doesn’t even exist in the real world?\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction/Science Fiction','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hackliminality.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:44:42'),
	(3,'.hack//Quantum','Plot Sumary:\r\nTobias, Mary, and Sakuya chalenge the impregnable \"The One Sin\", but they lose their way in the maze and unintentionaly trap other guild members. A mysterious cat is watching their blunder.','<img  src=\"http://www.anime44.com/images/hackquantum.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:44:42'),
	(4,'.hack//Roots','Plot Sumary:\r\n.hack/Rots is the prequel to the .hack/ videogames. It folows the story of Haseo a member of the Twilight Brigade guild. In the year 2015 the C.C. Corp’s building was burned down, and with it most of the data for “The World” was lost. By mixing the remaining data with that of another game, the C.C. Corp was able to create the game, “The World: R2?, unlike the games before this game alowed player versus player combat. The anime starts when Haseo logs into The World R:2 for the first time and fals victim to the PKers that reside within. He is saved by Ovan, which prompts him to join the Twilight Brigade. The Twilight Brigade members are on a mision to find the Key of the Twilight, however, the TAN guild oposes. Their curent mision is to find the 6 virus cores before TAN does, and Haseo has 2 of them, how wil he escape from the TAN Guild, and find the Key of Twilight, which might be the answer to everything.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction/Fantasy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hackroots.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:44:42'),
	(5,'.Hack//Sign','Plot Sumary:\r\nTaking place 2 years after the “Pluto’s Kis” crisis. “The World” once again returns. This time being the only PC game in existence. Tsubasa a boy who started playing only a few weks before, finds himself taken to a mysterious zone, where he mets Aura, Morgana, and a mysterious player that has the apearance of a cat. Son after realizing that he can’t logout, he is forced to stay in “The World”, but unlike other characters he can stil fel pain, he stil has his emotions. He slowly separates himself from those who try to help him, the only ones that can help him. His friends Bear and Black Rose, constantly try to comfort him in his strugle, but he always pushes them away. He only wants to search for the answer to why he can’t logout, and to the real question of who he realy is.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAdventure/Mystery/Fantasy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hacksign.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:44:43'),
	(6,'009-1','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn an alternate world, the Cold War has continued to persist for 140 years. As a result, the world was divided into two factions: the West Block, and the East Block. As the Cold War drags on, the tension betwen the two factions, as wel as the amount of nuclear weapons they have, rise. Mylene Hofman is a female cyborg who is a spy for the West Block. Together with thre other agents, Mylene partakes in various misions isued by her superiors.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: science fiction\r\nThemes: asasins, cold war, Cyborg, Iner Demons, secret agents, spies','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/009-1.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:44:43'),
	(7,'07 Ghost','Plot Sumary:\r\nOut of 50 students in the military academy, only 20 wil pas the dificult graduation exam to become begleiters (Asistant Executive Oficers). Teito Klein, the chairman’s favorite, is one of them. He is disliked by the other students because of his relations with the chairman and his mysterious past. After Teito and his best from, Mikage, finish the first phase, Teito begins to have strange dreams again about a man. Later on he eavesdrops on people talking about him. During this conversation, Teito recognizes the man in his dreams and another man that kiled him. When he is caught he is sent to prison, but escapes with the help of his best friend. Teito left Mikage and was found faling from the sky and unconscious by a group of guys.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy, Fantasy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/07-ghost.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:44:44'),
	(8,'11eyes','Plot Sumary:\r\nSatsuki Kakeru lost his sister by suicide and has ben living a dul life ever since then. One day, he is transported into a bizare world \"Red Night\" along with his friend Minase Yuka. In order to survive and escape from Red Night, he fights against Dark Spirits (Ralva) and Black Nights.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, fantasy, romance\r\nThemes: Harem','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/11eyes.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:44:44'),
	(9,'2×2 Shinobuden','Plot Sumary:\r\nShinobu is a naive ninja-in-training. In order to test her ninja abilites, she must steal the panties of al the high schol girls. The first house she stops at is the abode of one Kaede Shiranui, who hapens to catch Shinobu in the act. Kaeda is the voice of reason and the two girls become quick friends, despite a round yelow bal-thing who claims to be a ninja master and tries to get in the way of their friendship.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/2x2-shinobuden.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:44:44'),
