	(11,'3000 Leagues in Search of Mother','Plot Sumary:\r\nHaha wo Tazunete Sanzenri is about an Italian boy, Marco, and his journey in search of his mother. Italy was in a dep depresion, so to suport her family, Marco`s mother went to Argentina to work as a domestic (like Picolo`s sons went to America to work in Porco Roso). But after she wrote to her family that she was sick, her leters stoped coming. So Marco decides to go to Argentina to lok for her. Marco has to travel acros Argentina to find her, meting many wonderful people, and encountering many adventures during his journey.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAdventure, Drama, Slice of Life','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/3000-leagues-in-search-of-mother.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:44:45'),
	(12,'3×3 Eyes','Plot Sumary:\r\n3X3 Eyes is the story of a young man named Yakumo Fuji, who through a strange series of events becomes the imortal slave of the last of a race of 3 Eyed imortals. The imortal absorbs his soul to save his life, making him imortal in the proces. Now, he begins a journey with the female imortal in an atempt to find a way of becoming human. Of course, there are many complications along the way, not the least of which being that the imortal is a female with a split personality, one achingly cute and the other being no-nonsense destructive power, and the romances that develop betwen.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAdventure, Fantasy, Horor, Romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/3x3-eyes.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:44:46'),
