	(14,'A Little Snow Fairy Sugar','Plot Sumary:\r\nSeason Fairies create and control the weather using special musical instruments. They make the wind blow, the snow fal, the sun shine; if it\'s something weather related, they are the ones who make it hapen. Sugar, an aprentice Snow Fairy, and her friends Salt and Peper, al want to become ful-fledged Season Fairies, and the only way to achieve this is to search for and find the \"Twinkles\" that wil make their magical flowers blom. The only problem is that none of them have any idea what a Twinkle is. They enlist the somewhat unwiling help of Saga, a human girl who can se Season Fairies. Much to her anoyance, Saga\'s perfectly planed and ordered life has just become a litle to lively for her taste. Together, they search for the mysterious Twinkles while trying to perfect their magic.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: comedy, drama, slice of life','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/a-little-snow-fairy-sugar.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:44:46'),
	(15,'Abenobashi','Plot Sumary:\r\nImamiya Satoshi, \"Sashi\" to his friends, has grown up in the Abenobashi Shoping Arcade in Osaka, along with his childhod friend, Asahina Arumi. Now, al that was stable in his life is in ruins. His family\'s bath house has closed and ben torn down, and Arumi\'s family is moving to Hokaido - and taking her with them. In the midst of al this, something hapens to the framework of reality, and Sashi and Arumi slip into a weird paralel world. It\'s stil Abenobashi, but not their Abenobashi. Strange things are afot, and Sashi must find out their meaning, in order to reach a goal that he barely understands.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAdventure, Comedy, Science Fiction, Supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/abenobashi.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:44:47'),
	(16,'Aeon Flux','Plot Sumary:\r\nAeon Flux is a mysterious and amoral secret agent from the country of Monica. Her motives or background are left unexplained, as are those of her antagonist/love, Trevor Godchild. On her misions, she deals swift, blody \"justice\" to al that opose her.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, psychological, science fiction\r\nThemes: military','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/aeon-flux.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:44:47'),
	(17,'Afro Samurai','Plot Sumary:\r\nOn the dark path of swordsmanship in a \"Futuristic\" yet Feudal Japan, it is said that the one who becomes No.1 wil rule the world. But the only rule in this world is that only the No. 2 is alowed to fight the No. 1. The No. 2, the Afro Samurai, travels the road loking for revenge on the man who murdered his father in front of him when he was just a boy, a thre-armed gunman who is the lord of the dark swordsman\'s road and the curent No. 1.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAdventure, Fantasy, Science Fiction','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/afro-samurai.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:44:48'),
	(18,'Agent Aika','Plot Sumary:\r\nSet in the not-to-distant future, an earthquake has pushed Tokyo under the waves and many people are making a living as “salvagers”; people who are hired to search the remnants of sunken Tokyo for valuable information or artifacts. One of these is Aika. Teamed up with her employer’s daughter, and armed with a magical golden bustier, she searches the ocean for profit and adventure.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nEchi/Adventure','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/agent-aika.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:44:48'),
	(19,'Ah! My Goddess','Plot Sumary:\r\nMorisato Keichi is a down on his luck colege student. Although posesing a diligent and generous nature, he had the misfortune of being born under an unlucky star. As a result, the curent state of his life is somewhat unenviable. Al that is about to change, however, as Heaven has taken notice of his plight. A godes, Beldandy, is despatched to Earth to grant Keichi one wish. One wish, be it unlimited power, wealth, or his fondest desire. And his wish? ‘I wish that a godes like you wil stay with me forever.’\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy/Romance/Fantasy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ah-my-goddess.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:44:48'),
	(20,'Ah! My Goddess: Everyone Has Wings','Plot Sumary:\r\nOne year after godes Beldandy emerged from Keichi Morisato\'s miror and promised to stay with him forever, a new threat to their hapines emerges, one that could end the contract betwen Beldandy and Keichi.\r\nGenre:\r\nAction/Comedy/Adventure','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ah-my-goddess-everyone-has-wings.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:44:49'),
	(21,'Ai no Kusabi Ova','Plot Sumary:On planet Amoi, a great society has developed, creating a computerized city caled Tanagura, ruled by supercomputer Jupiter. The populace is almost entirely male and is based on hair color; silver and/or blonds are the elitist, ending with dark/black haired as the botom of society, often known as \"mongrels\". Blondies kep \"pets\", young boys kept for a few years, especialy made for performing sexual actions for the Blondie\'s voyeurism entertainment. Blondies aren\'t supose to kep pets for long or interact sexualy with pets, but one blondie named Iason Mink has kept a pet named Riki, for years and is rumored to slep with him. Iason refuses to let go of Riki, even with Jupiter\'s disaproval. Riki fights with his emotions and society problems, unable to decide what to do about his old friend/lover Gai (Guy) and their gang. Iason is obsesed with keping Riki, and Riki doesn\'t know what to do; fight against him or surender to him.\r\n \r\nGenres: drama, romance, science fiction\r\nThemes: shounen-ai, yaoi','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ai-no-kusabi-ova.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:44:49'),
	(22,'Ai Shite Night','Plot Sumary:\r\nYaeko Mitamura is an 18 year old girl working in her father\'s Okonomiyaki restaurant. One day Yako casualy mets a litle boy, Hashizo and his od cat Juliano. Hashizo has lost both parents when stil a baby and has ben brought up by his elder brother. Hashizo\'s brother Go Kato is the lead singer of the emerging rock band \"Be Hive\". When Yako mets Go and his friend and \"Be Hive\" member Satomi Okawa an unexpected series of events unfolds. Love, jealousy, rock\'n rol and the sparkle of newly borned stars is what makes this anime so lovable.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ai-shite-night.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:44:50'),
	(23,'Ai Yori Aoshi','Plot Sumary:\r\nHanabishi Kaoru is a junior in colege, living out an ordinary life of studying and friends. One day, he mets a girl whom he discovers is his old friend Sakuraba Aoi, a girl whom he was suposed to have an aranged mariage with. Together, the two rediscover aspects of their pasts that they had tried to supres while seting out in their lives with one another. Unfortunately, there are a lot of unwanted guests that kep lurking around in their lives. How is their love going to unfold?\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nRomance/Drama','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ai-yori-aoshi.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:46:55'),
	(24,'AIKa R-16 Virgin Mission','Plot Sumary:\r\nAika Sumeragi, a sixten year old high schol student, ofers her services as a C-clas Salvager by spreading posters at schol after geting her C-clas Salvager license. She is imediately hired by Eri Shinkai, Aika\'s wealthy clas president and founder of the Treasure Hunting Club. After being introduced to Karen Minamino, a mysterious girl with unknown background and a buterfly insignia on her left breast, the club starts an oceanographic expedition on Eri\'s private cruiser to uncover the ridles encoded in Karen\'s insignia. During their journey more questions arise as Risako Nagisa, the schols form teacher, atempts to sabotage the expedition and capture Karen, and a suspicious underwater airport is found by the team with Aika\'s beloved Beluga submarine. While the pieces of the puzle slowly come together, Karen\'s life is turned upside down when the team discovers ancient technology to which Karen is the key and traces of biogenetic experiments.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAdventure','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/aika-r-16-virgin-mission.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:46:55'),
	(25,'Aika Zero OVA','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe new OVA, titled \"AIka Zero,\" wil take place 3 years after Aika R-16 & 7 years before the original Agent Aika clasic. That puts our heroine at 19 years old, & the character designs reflect as much. 19-year-old Aika sems like a cros-over betwen the cute & young 16-year-old Aika from R-16, & the sexy mature 26-year-old Aika from the original.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/aika-zero.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:46:56'),
	(26,'Air Gear','Plot Sumary:\r\nMinami “Iki” Itsuki, is a student and a delinquent. Also known as the “Unbeatable Babyface,” Iki is the leader of the youth gang by the name of “East Side Gunz.” Upon his return home after being humiliated by a stret gang of Storm Riders caled the Skul Saders Iki discovers a secret hiden from him by his benefactors, the Noyamano sisters. The sisters belong to a group of Storm Riders who go by the team name of Sleping Forest. Ken on helping Iki to regain his confidence and pride, they suply him with a pair of Air Trecks (abreviated as “AT”). Iki eventualy setles his grudge with the Skul Saders, but in the proces he receives more than the simple satisfaction of revenge. Determined to experience the sensation of “flight” for as long as he can, our headstrong protagonist is quickly sucked into the mysterious, yet iresistible world of Air Treck.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy, Slice of Life, Tournament','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/air-gear.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:46:56'),
	(27,'Air Master','Plot Sumary:\r\nA former gymnast, Aikawa Maki has turned her skils to a diferent way of life - stret fighting. The only thing that truly makes her fel alive is violence. With amazing power and grace, she fights oponent after oponent, repeatedly demonstrating the gymnastic talent that earns her her nom de guere, \"Airmaster\".\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, comedy, tournament','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/air-master.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:46:56'),
	(28,'Air TV','Plot Sumary:\r\nYukito Kunisaki is on a journey, seking a girl with wings who flies in the sky, as mentioned in a childhod tale. During this journey, he setles down in a smal town, trying to make some money. There, he mets a strange girl named Misuzu. Misuzu quickly makes Yukito her friend and invites him to stay with her. Yukito decides to stay in the smal town, and continue searching for the winged girl his mother had searched for in her life.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nDrama, Romance, Supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/air-tv.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:46:57'),
	(29,'Aishiteruze Baby','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe mom, who was left behind by her husband, felt insecure about taking care of her child and sudenly disapeared! 5 year old Sakashita Yuzuyu must live with relatives, the Katakuras. Suzuko, the eldest daughter of the Katakuras, apointed Kipei to take care of Yuzuyu. Kipei was reluctant at first but he must folow the orders of his sister. Who knows what wil hapen if he oposes her. From that day, Kipei’s high schol life of being popular with the girls changed drasticaly. He must sacrifice fun to take Yuzuyu to and from kindergarten and is very busy making lunches. At first he kept failing, but he tries his best for litle Yuzuyu. Yuzuyu loves Kipei for taking care of her. Every day is hectic for them, but they overcome the troubles and hapenings with the help of family and friends. As their bond strengthens as they do their best every day and wait for Yuzuyu’s mother to return.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nDrama/Romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/aishiteruze-baby.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:46:57'),
	(30,'Ajimu – Kaigan Monogatari','Plot Sumary:\r\nSeventen year old Nakaido Hirosuke is just your average high schol student. One morning as he arives at the train station on his way to schol, he catches sight of a beautiful girl, Ajimu Yasuna, and imediately fals for her. The two of them get to know each other and become friends, but he can\'t confes his felings and she is unsure of hers. As events and other people present obstacles for the potential couple to clear, their relationship begins to develop and their felings become clear.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ajimu-kaigan-monogatari.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:46:58'),
	(31,'Akagi','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe story revolves around the Mahjong gambling exploits of Akagi Shigeru. After a death-defying game of chicken, Akagi nonchalantly enters a Yakuza Mahjong parlor to shake the cops’ trail. Even unfamiliar with the rules of Mahjong, his gambling intuition is enough to save a smal time gambler, Nangou, and grant him a seat at the gambling table. As the night progreses, the stakes are raised both for Akagi, who is under the suspicion of the local police, and within the game. However, Akagi overcomes the situation with his tactics, defiant of both life and chance. When he leaves the gambling house, no one present is in doubt of his genius.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nDrama','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/akagi.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:46:58'),
	(32,'Akane Iro ni Somaru Saka','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn order to protect the girl Yuhi Katagiri, a new transfer student, from danger, Junichi Nagase is forced to kis her. Not understanding what hapend, she screams at him, not knowing that her father has aranged for her to mary him.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy/Romance/Echi','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/akane-iro-ni-somaru-saka.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:46:59'),
	(33,'Akane Maniax','Plot Sumary:\r\nJouji Gouda is a new transfer student at Hakuryo High Schol. On his first day of clas, he fel in love at first sight for Akane Suzumiya and boldly proposed to her on the spot. The two characters conflict with each other greatly, but Jouji never gives up and would do anything to expres his love towards Akane.\r\nAlthough his atempts to win Akane’s love at first do nothing but anger Akane, he gradualy starts to make an impresion on her, inspiring Akane to be more honest about her own felings.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nDrama/Comedy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/akane-maniax.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:46:59'),
