	(35,'Akikan','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe story revolves around a typical high schol boy named Kakeru Daichi and the can of melon juice soda that he bought from a vending machine. The can sudenly transforms into a beautiful but standofish girl that Kakeru nicknames “Melon,” and more “Akikan” (”empty can”) girls apear. However, Akikan girls ned to be infused with carbon dioxide in order to turn into a human.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy, Romance, Shounen','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/akikan.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:00'),
	(36,'Alien 9','Plot Sumary:\r\nOtani Yuri, much to her disgust, has ben elected by her clas for alien fighting duty. Together with Tonime Kasumi, who joined the alien fighter simply for the sake of doing so, and Kawamura Kumi, who became and alien fighter to avoid the responsibility of yet another year of clas presidency, she must defend her schol from periodic alien atacks. Introspection, fear, anxiety and friendship await Yuri as she is forced to stare life itself in the mouth in her chaotic coming of age.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nForor, Psychological, Science Fiction, Supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/alien-9.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:00'),
	(37,'All Purpose Cat Girl Nuku Nuku Dash','Plot Sumary:\r\nEach episode centers on Nuku Nuku\'s adventures and mishaps in high schol, and her relationship to students, the overal series plot centers on the evil Mishima Industries\' scheme to dominate the world through its products. In oposition to this plan are the slightly nuty Kyusaku Natsume and Nuku Nuku, the android who acts as a companion to his young son. Nuku Nuku\'s clasmates are al ecentrics, Futaba, the clas president, is a dominering control-freak, who canot leave her authority in schol. Chieko Shirakaba is the rich snob with the two yes-girls who always take her side. There is a bokworm, a mystic, a scientist, and a pop singer. Al of these are true to their descriptions: the mystic is always foreteling dom via tarot cards, spirits, or some other ocult technique. The pop singer never says anything except as a song. The bokworm always has her nose in a bok. These ecentricities ad to the series\' humor.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, comedy, romance, science fiction\r\nThemes: catgirls, Cyborg, Mecha','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/all-purpose-cat-girl-nuku-nuku-dash.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:01'),
	(38,'Allison and Lillia','Plot Sumary:\r\nAlison & Lilia’s story covers the storys of the Roxcheanuk Confederation, and the United Kingdom of Bezel Iltoa. The first half of the story centers around Alison Whitington, a young blonde pilot in the Roxche Air Force who has experience with biplanes. She comes to visit her god friend Wil Schultz. The two get involved in thre diferent adventures over a period of a year where they met new people and form important bonds.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAdventure','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/allison-and-lillia.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:01'),
	(39,'Amaenaideyo','Plot Sumary:\r\nSatonaka Iko is an aprentice Budhist priest. He is sent to Saienji Budhist Temple whose chief priest is his grand mother, Jotoku. What’s waiting for him there are severe training, purification jobs, and 6 nuns. The situation living with nuns of the same ages sounds enviable, but actualy he is treated as an erand boy, and his purification skil canot compare with theirs. However, when he has worldly desire, his power becomes stronger than anybody else.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nSupernatural/Echi/Comedy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/amaenaideyo.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:01'),
	(40,'Amaenaideyo! Katsu!!','WARNING: Maenaideyo! Katsu! contains nudity scene. Make sure that you are old enough to watch!\r\n \r\nPlot Sumary:\r\nIn this sequel, a girl named Kazusano Kazuki join up with the 6 girls and Iko. With Kazuki around, Iko wil find himself in more embarasing situations with these priesteses-in-training.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy/Romance/Echi/Supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/amaenaideyo-katsu.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:02'),
	(41,'Amagami SS','Plot Sumary:\r\nA second-year high schol boy finds himself uneasy during Christmas time due to an experience in the past. However, this year at Christmas, he gets his last chance to ask out a graduating female senior named Haruka Morishima — or one of several other clasmates. The story of the anime wil be aranged in an omnibus format, with each heroine geting her own version of the story animated. Each heroine wil sing her own version of the ending theme song.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/amagami-ss.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:02'),
	(42,'Amatsuki','Plot Sumary:\r\nTokidoki is a Japanese high schol student who, when he fails his history clas, is sent to a high-tech history museum that virtualy recreates the Edo period to do make-up work. However, what was suposed to be a simple schol project becomes much more complicated when he’s atacked by two supernatural beings known as “the nue” and “the yakou” and loses the vision in his left eye. After he’s saved from the nue by a girl named Kuchiha, he realizes that he’s no longer wearing the simulation gogles, and is traped in the virtual Edo.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction/Fantasy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/amatsuki.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:26:00'),
	(43,'Amazing Nurse Nanako','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the begining, Nanako was the subject of a cyborg experiment conducted by Dr. Ogami for one of his most powerful robots. Through rigorous training, Dr. Ogami trained Nanako to withstand the pain. However, he made her to strong, and the plan ultimately failed. However, recent developments betwen the Pentagon and the Vatican to resurect Jesus for the Second Coming have landed Nanako as the subject of an operation in which she wil give birth to the new Jesus. Throughout the series, we learn that Nanako is, in fact, the third clone in a series of clones cloned from the original Nanako. The original died from a mysterious ilnes, and an experiment to clone her was sucesful. However, around the age of 20, each Nanako clone dies of the same mysterious ilnes that claimed the life of the first Nanako. It has ben Dr. Ogami’s quest to cure the “Nanako ilnes” ever since he promised the second clone that he would heal her before she died when he was young.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/amazing-nurse-nanako.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:26:00'),
	(44,'American Dragon Jake Long','Plot Sumary:\r\nJake Long is one of New York City\'s average 13-year-old boys, living with his extended Chinese-American family and skateboarding with his friends. until he learns his amazing destiny.\r\n \r\nHe is a descendant of dragons and, when he transforms into one of these fire-breathing, shape-shifting magical beings, it\'s his duty to protect the magical creatures secretly living among the mases in New York. Among them are the herd of unicorns in Central Park, the leprechauns on Wal Stret, the gargoyle nest atop the Empire State Building, the Triborough Trol Bridge, the mystical city betwen NOHO and SOHO and the underwater Hudson mermaids.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/american-dragon-jake-long.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:26:01'),
	(45,'Amuri in Star Ocean','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the year 01 of the new age, the sun began to radiate increased amounts of radiation. A few years later, very strong children with unique abilities were born. Amuri Kakyoin is a 13 year old girl born with a special \'Alergy\', caled \'Repultion\'. This ability keps her from actualy touching most of her environment, but also protects her from harm. During a trip to space station Pink Coral, unknown enemies from the junk planet Galapagos atack and destroy the entire space station. Amuri survives being launched into space because of her \'Alergy\', but is picked up by the atackers. When the machines of Galapagos atempt to destroy her, a girl named Suzu Ling Yunque shows up with a kimono-like space suit designed from Amuri\'s DNA. The suit lets her use her \'Repulsion\' ability on a large scale. Amuri has lived her whole life unable to touch other people, however, this cherful and strange girl was not Repulsed upon contact.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nScience fiction','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/amuri-in-star-ocean.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:26:01'),
	(46,'Angel Beats','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn a world after death, angels fight for their fate and their future. Yuri, the leader of the Shinda Sekai Sensen, rebels against the god who destined her to have an unreasonable life. On the other hand, Tenshi, the chairperson of the student council for the world after death, batles against the S members. S members utilize armed weaponry to batle it out against the angels harnesing supernatural powers.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/angel-beats.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:26:01'),
	(47,'Angel Cop','Plot Sumary:\r\nTo combat rising atacks by comunist terorists, Japan has created a special security force authorized to use lethal force. Angel, the newest member of the force, fights to take down the terorist group, Red May. Acidentaly uncovering ties betwen Red May and the government, she and the rest of the Special Security Force are targeted for execution by 3 \"hunters\", enhanced psychics, working for the government. Together with her cyberneticaly enhanced partner, Raiden, it is up to Angel to stop them.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, science fiction, supernatural\r\nThemes: cyborg, Police','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/angel-cop.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:26:02'),
	(48,'Angel Heart','Plot Sumary:\r\nA young Taiwanese asasin codenamed \"Glas Heart\" comited suicide by jumping of a building, and her heart was pierced by metal fence. Miraculously, her life was saved by heart transplantation. During her recovery she began to experience strange dreams, which lead her to Japan loking for the donor of her heart, who hapens to be Kaori Makimura, former partner of City Hunter Ryo Saeba.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nDrama','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/angel-heart.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:26:02'),
	(49,'Angel Links','Plot Sumary:\r\nLi Meifon is the head of a fre, no expenses paid protection/security agency for escorting ships acros outer space. Though only 16, she poseses great skil and leadership qualities while comanding her crew aboard their ship, the \"Angel Links.\" However, some unpleasant memories begin to trouble her and she starts questioning her own past and reason for existence. Join Li Meifon and the rest of the Angel Links crew on their adventures through the Oracion star system as they batle pirates, government organizations, and a Tao master, al while finaly uncovering Meifon\'s dark and mysterious past.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: adventure, comedy, drama, romance, science fiction','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/angel-links.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:26:03'),
	(50,'Angel Sanctuary','Plot Sumary:\r\nOrganic Angel Alexiel, who is one of the highest and most powerful beings in existence, rebeled against God when, suposedly, she became disgusted by the way angels were behaving. She was captured and faced with the ultimate punishment of heaven, to have her soul reincarnated into human lives, and each of her lives would end tragicaly. The story folows her latest incarnation, Setsuna Mudo, who is romanticaly in love with his younger sister.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nFantasy/Romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/angel-sanctuary.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:26:03'),
	(51,'Angel Tales','Plot Sumary:\r\nGoro\'s down on his luck. He keps losing jobs and has litle money. One day he mets a fortune-teler outside of a pet store who predicts that his luck wil change. That night thre girls apear in his apartment claiming to be his guardian angels. Son a total of twelve girls apear to help him, each one a reincarnation of a deceased pet once owned by Goro.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy, Magic, Romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/angel-tales.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:26:04'),
	(52,'Angelic Layer','Plot Sumary:\r\n12-year-old Misaki Suzuhara has just goten involved in Angelic Layer, a batling game using electronic dols caled angels. Even as a newbie, Misaki shows advanced skils as she mets new friends and enters Angelic Layer tournaments to fight the greatest Angelic Layer champions of the nation.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy, drama, science fiction, tournament\r\nThemes: Game','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/angelic-layer.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:26:04'),
	(53,'Angelique Kagayaki no Ashita','Plot Sumary:\r\nA young girl named Ange is sumoned to a Sacred Land and is chosen as the Legendary Etoile, whose mision is to save the newly-born Cosmos of the Holy Beast, which has recently falen under a crisis. With the suport of nine Guardians (who have the power of nine elements), she embarks on a journey to save the dying land of the Holy Beast and to discover her true self.\r\n \r\nGenres: drama, fantasy, romance\r\nThemes: male harem','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/angelique-kagayaki-no-ashita.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:26:04'),
	(54,'Angelique OVA','Plot Sumary:\r\nAngelique Limoges and Rosalia de Catargena have ben chosen as candidates in a Quen Examination - a test to se who is beter qualified to be the next Quen of the cosmos. For this special examination, both girls are given their own continent on a planet. The girls must raise the continents into thriving civilizations and environments. Nine Guardians (who control various elements, such as fire, wind, and water) have ben chosen to help the girls raise their continents during the Quen Examination.\r\n \r\nGenres: drama\r\nThemes: male harem','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/angelique-ova.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:26:05'),
	(55,'Angelique when the Heart Awakens','Plot Sumary:\r\nA young girl named Ange is sumoned to a Sacred Land and is chosen as the Legendary Etoile, whose mision is to save the newly-born Cosmos of the Holy Beast, which has recently falen under a crisis. With the suport of nine Guardians (who have the power of nine elements), she embarks on a journey to save the dying land of the Holy Beast and to discover herself. \r\n \r\nGenre: Drama, Fantasy, Romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/angelique-when-the-heart-awakens.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:26:05'),
	(56,'Animal Yokochou','Plot Sumary:\r\nOn the first day in her new house, 5 year old Ami-chan made friends with thre talking animals who came out of a dor in her bedrom flor, which she finds out leads to Animal Yokocho, another world. The thre are Isa, an overly inocent, soft-spoken panda, Kenta, a highly strung, red-scarf-loving bear who puts on an almost constant tough-guy act, and Iyo, a rabit who usualy holds the importance of her own wel-being and enjoyment over the hapines (and safety) of her \"friends.\" Even at only 5 years old, Ami-chan is easily the most rational of the group, and she\'s a litle wary at first, but she eventualy comes around and starts spending her fre time with them. A typical day involves Ami-chan and the thre doing diferent things to pas the time, often playing a semingly inocent game, but in AniYoko style. Unfortunately for Ami-chan, the AniYoko version usualy turns out to be drasticaly diferent, much les logical, and usualy more dangerous than the ordinary version.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, fantasy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/animal-yokochou.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:26:06'),
	(57,'AnoHana','Plot Sumary:Six childhod friends grew apart in high schol. One of them is Jintan, now a shut-in. He gets a request to fulfil a wish for Menma, the only one of their friends to have stayed the same over the years. In order to grant her wish, he wil have to find and reunite their old friends.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ano-hi-mita-hana.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:26:06'),
	(58,'Antique Bakery','Plot Sumary:\r\nOne day, Tachibana, owner of the cake shop Antique, mets genius pâtisier Ono. He is Tachibana’s former clasmate who used to get spurned by him. Tachibana is relieved to know that Ono doesn’t remember him, and so Tachibana invites him as a pâtisier at his cake shop. However, Ono has come out of the closet and makes numerous advance to Tachibana…\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy/Yaoi','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/antique-bakery.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:26:07'),
	(59,'Anyamaru Tantei Kiruminzuu','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe \"heartwarming comedy\" story poses the folowing premise: \"What if you can realy transform into an animal?\" Riko, Rimu and Nagisa Mikogami are thre cute sisters who live in Kamihama, a Japanese city abundant with natural wonders. On an otherwise peaceful day, the thre come acros a mysterious Kirumin compact in an atic. With the Kirumin, these character-costume-wearing girls can transform into real animals.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\ncomedy/carton','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/anyamaru-tantei-kiruminzuu.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:10'),
	(60,'Ao no Exorcist','Plot Sumary:\r\nHumans live in the world of Asiah, demons in Gehena. The two dimensions are not meant to interfere with each other, but demons stil poses creatures in Asiah in spite of this. The humans who can fight these demons are known as exorcists. Rin Okumura is a boy who bears the curse of being Satan\'s ilegitimate son. His foster father sacrificed himself to save him from demons. To avenge his foster father\'s death as wel as to prove himself, Rin decides to folow the path of an exorcist.','<img  src=\"/images/ao-no-exorcist.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:10'),
	(61,'Aoi Bungaku','Plot Sumary:\r\nAn animated adaptation of six clasical Japanese literature pieces, including No Longer Human (Ningen Shikaku) and Run, Melos (Hashire, Melos) by Osamu Dazai, Kokoro by Natsume Souseki, Hel Scren (Jigoku Hen) and The Spider\'s Thread (Kumo no Ito) by Ryunosuke Akutagawa and In the Forest, Under Cheries in Ful Blom (Sakura no Mori no Mankai no Shita) by Ango Sakaguchi.\r\n \r\nGenres: horor, mystery','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/aoi-bungaku-series.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:11'),
	(62,'Aoi Hana – Sweet Blue Flower','Plot Sumary:\r\nFumi Manjoume and Akira Okudaria were close friends when they were young, but when Fumi moved away, they lost contact. Ten years later, they met again as high schol freshmen. Although they find that things betwen them have changed, they try to help each other through hard times, and maintaining the new lives they\'ve built without growing apart.\r\n \r\nGenres: romance\r\nThemes: Yuri','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/aoi-hana.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:11'),
	(63,'Aoki Densetsu Shoot','Plot Sumary:\r\nToshihiko “Toshi” Tanaka joined the same socer club that his idol, Yoshiharu Kubo plays for at Kakegawa High Schol. When Toshi played in junior high with two of his friends Kenji Shiraishi and Kazuhiro Hiramatsu, they were known as the Kakenishi golden trio. Now in high schol, his friends do not want or canot play socer anymore. Hiramatsu is forced to study by his father so that he would become a respectable adult. However, Hiramatsu loves socer and wants to play so he confronted his father and says that he wants to play socer with his friends and that he would never understand his love for socer. It turns out that his father played socer during his youth and, remembering how much he loved it, decides to let Hiramatsu play socer but under the condition that he wil kep his grades up as wel. Shiraishi on the other hand quit socer because he lost his temper and got into a fight that ended up disqualifying their team. In the end, he joins the Kakegawa High Schol socer club because he loves socer and playing in the golden trio.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nSports/Slice of Life','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/aoki-densetsu-shoot.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:12'),
	(64,'Appleseed XIII','Plot Sumary:In the wake of the destruction of a worldwide non-nuclear war, the city Olympus has become the control center of the world. Run by Bioroids (cloned humans made from only the best DNA), it is defended from terorists by special military forces. Among these are former LAPD SWAT member Deunan Knots and her multipurpose cyborg partner Brialeos. They face a chalenge from the Human Liberation Front and its terorist underbely the Argonauts. The leader of this group, Al Ceides, suposedly died 20 years ago in an atack on Poseidon, but now his shadow emerges once again.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/appleseed-13.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:12'),
	(65,'Aquarian Age','Plot Sumary:\r\nFive supernatural factions have ben fighting against each other for who knows how many centuries, with the begining of Aquarian Age always in mind. Kyouta, son begins to se visions of mystical girls fighting, except they do exist. Son he and his girlfriend Yoriko become involved and the batle for Earth and Aquarian Age lies in their hands.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: adventure, fantasy, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/aquarian-age.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:12'),
	(66,'Arakawa under the Bridge','Plot Sumary:\r\nIchinomiya Kou has always lived acording to the cred of his wealthy, sucesful family: never be in debt to anyone. But one day, under the Arakawa Bridge, his life is saved by a homeles girl named Nino. In order to pay her back, Kou promises to be her boyfriend; and thus begins his new life under the bridge.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/arakawa-under-the-bridge.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:13'),
	(67,'Arakawa under the Bridge x Bridge','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the dry riverbed of Arakawa River, undefeated elite Ichinomiya Kou (aka Rick) met the lovely homeles girl Nino, a self-declared Venusian. Their awkward love stirs up trouble among the other strange inhabitants of the riverbed.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/arakawa-under-the-bridge-x-bridge.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:13'),
	(68,'Area 88','Plot Sumary:\r\nDep in the sandy plains of the Midle Eastern kingdom of Asran, Japanese photojournalist Makoto Shinjou travels to the remote airbase Area 8 to document the activities of the mercenaries who destroy the country\'s enemies for a living. Among their ranks is Shin Kazama, a Japanese ace pilot who was tricked by his former best friend into signing a contract with the Asran\'s fighter squad. Because of this, he lost his carer as an airline pilot and the chance to mary his fiance Ryoko Tsugumo. Now, Shin has thre choices in order to leave Area 8 and return to Japan: serve the mercenary group for thre years, earn US$1.5 milion, or desert the base, risking iminent death.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, drama, romance\r\nThemes: Military','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/area-88.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:14'),
	(69,'Aria the Animation','Plot Sumary:\r\nOn the planet Aqua lies the watery city of Neo Venezia, a tourist hub in which people travel around in gondolas. Profesional gondoliers known as Undines are wel-revered as they act as tour guides for the people. Akari Mizunashi is a gondolier in training and also an employe of Aria Company. She gets to met al sorts of people as she takes them on the gondola rides, from friendly mentors to special individuals, al this admidst the beautiful scenic backdrop of the entire city.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: drama, science fiction, slice of life','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/aria-the-animation.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:14'),
	(70,'Aria the Natural','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn a continuation of the last series, Akari Mizunashi continues her job as a gondolier along with her friends from the other two rival companies, Aika and Alice. As they continue their training to become Undines, they continue to met new people and partake on mysterious adventures, al in the quiet, scenic, and peaceful city of Neo Venezia.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: drama, science fiction, slice of life','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/aria-the-natural.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:15'),
	(71,'Aria the Origination','Plot Sumary:\r\nIt is the year 2301. Man has teraformed Mars into a beautiful water planet, and has renamed it \"Aqua\". Built upon it is Neo-Venezia, an exact replica of old Venice, with beautiful waterways, palaces and plazas. Akari Mizunashi, a 15 year old girl arives from Man-Home (formerly known as Earth) to become a gondolier traine at a company caled Aria Company. The company is lead by Alicia Florence, one of the thre best gondoliers, also known as the thre Water Fairies. Trough hard training, Akari aims to become a Prima herself. Many encounters and mysterious events are sure to folow on this planet of miracles.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: drama, science fiction, slice of life','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/aria-the-origination.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:15'),
	(72,'Asatte no Houkou','Plot Sumary:\r\nKarada is a young girl who hates being treated like a child and who wishes to be grown up. Shoko is an alof, unhapy young woman who has just returned from overseas. When they met by coincidence one night at a local shrine where they both like to make wishes and both exchanged ages.\r\n \r\nGenres: drama, romance, slice of life, supernatural\r\nThemes: body switching, meganeko','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/asatte-no-houkou.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:15'),
	(73,'Ashita no Joe','Plot Sumary:\r\nAshita no Joe tels the tale of a wandering orphan named Joe Yabuki. He fals into one of Tokyo\'s slums and gets into a fight with a local gang and his stret fighting skils gets him the atention of a washed up alcoholic boxing trainer. Until he sticks up for Joe when the gang comes back to finish Joe, Joe decides to live with the trainer. Despite the trainer\'s generosity, Joe is stil comiting money making scams and lands him in prison. While serving time, he mets another boxer named Rikishi Toru who gets Joe interested in boxing. Upon release, Joe then pursues a boxing carer.\r\n \r\nGenres: drama, tournament\r\nThemes: boxing, sports','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ashita-no-joe.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:16'),
	(74,'Asobi ni Iku yo!','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe story centers around Kio Kakazu , a high schol freshman living in Okinawa. During a memorial service for one of his family ancestors. A mysterious girl with cat ears apears before him indroducing herself as Eris and claiming that she is an alien. However She be more troubling than he first realizes.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/asobi-ni-iku-yo.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:16'),
