	(76,'Asu no Yoichi!','Plot Sumary:\r\nYoichi Karasuma is a young samurai who spent al his life training martial arts on a mountain in Japan. His father finaly sends him away to learn about the life in the city. There he starts to live with four girls and goes to a normal high schol. But modern life is harder to grasp than expected.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy, Romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/asu-no-yoichi.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:17'),
	(77,'Asura Cryin','Plot Sumary:\r\nTomo was a schol kid with just one problem: he had a ghost friend for a while. One day, his life is turned upside down as his world changes into a new one, one which he couldn\'t imagine before.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nSupernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/asura-cryin.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:17'),
	(78,'Aura Battler Dunbine','Plot Sumary:\r\nAfter a motocros acident, Show Zama was puled from Japan into the mystical world of Byston Wel, where he and others from Earth were reicruited by Lord Drake Luft to pilot his newest weapons, the Aura Batlers, a combination of Byston Wel magic and Earthien technology. However, in the heat of batle, Show is aproached by Marvel, a woman from Earth, who convinces him of Luft\'s sinister intentions.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, fantasy, science fiction\r\nThemes: mecha','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/aura-battler-dunbine.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:18'),
	(79,'Avatar The Last Airbender','Plot Sumary:\r\nA century prior to the series’ opening, when Aang was 12 years old, he was frozen into a state of suspended animation for 10 years. After being awoken by two children from the Southern Water Tribe, he finds the world at war with the Fire Nation. As the Avatar, he sets out to master the elements and ultimately defeat the Fire Lord and end the war. Each generation yields one person who is capable of Bending al four elements. This being is refered to as the Avatar, the spirit of the planet manifested in human form. When an Avatar dies, they are reincarnated into the next nation in the Avatar Cycle. The Avatar Cycle paralels the seasons: winter for The Water Tribes, spring for the Earth Kingdom, sumer for the Fire Nation, and autumn for the Air Nomads. Legend holds the Avatar must master each bending art in order, starting with their native element. This can sometimes be compromised when the situation requires it, as Aang demonstrates in the show. For the Avatar, learning to bend the element oposite their native element can be extremely dificult. This is because oposing Bending arts are based on oposing fighting styles and disciplines. Firebending and Waterbending are oposites, as are Earthbending and Airbending.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAdventure/Fantasy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/avatar_the_last_airbender.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:18'),
	(80,'Avenger','Plot Sumary:\r\nMars has ben colonized and is a world where children have ben replaced by robot servents known as \'dols\'. Layla is a skiled fighter with a tragic past who travels about the world. Her companions are Nei, a strange and unique dol with some unknown ties to Layla, and Spedy, who is a dol breder. The founders of Mars se the trio as a threat to their world, and each time they atack Layla and Nei a bit more of their mysterious past and future is revealed.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, adventure, fantasy, science fiction','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/avenger.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:19'),
	(81,'Ayakashi','Plot Sumary:Adapted from the 205 adults-only superhuman batle action visual novel game Ayakashi. Ayakashi is a parasite life force that gives superpowers to its host, taking in return the host\'s entire life force. Kusaka Yu is a student that lost his wil to live after the death of a dear childhod friend, until the day a mysterious girl, named Yoake Eimu, apears. From that moment on, his life would never be the same again. Hunted by Ayakashi and their hosts, the power within Yu awakens and a never ending batle begins.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, fantasy, horor, supernatural\r\nThemes: Iner Demons, superpowers','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ayakashi.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:19'),
	(82,'Ayakashi Japanese Classic Horror','Plot Sumary:\r\nA colection of thre clasic Japanese horor stories: \"Yotsuya Kaidan,\" the story of a wife betrayed by her husband who seks vengeance even in death, \"Tenshu Monogatari,\" the story of forbiden love betwen a godes and a human, and \"Bakeneko,\" the story of a mysterious cat monster with a vendeta against a certain family.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nFantasy, Horor, Supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ayakashi-japanese-classic-horror.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:19'),
	(83,'Ayashi no Ceres','Plot Sumary:\r\nCeres was a tenyo (Celestial maiden) who came down from the heavens to bathe in a stream. She hung her hagoromo (robe) on a tre nearby, which was her key to returning to the heavens. But the robe was stolen and the man who had stolen it forced her to become his wife, thus producing a family ful of human and tenyo blod mixed. Now, in modern day time, Aya Mikage is a descendent of Ceres, and has quite an amount tenyo blod. On her 16th birthday, she and her twin brother, Aki, are thrown a party. At the \"party\", Aya\'s grandpa plans to kil her, for she has tenyo powers unlike the rest of the family, and can actualy become Ceres herself and destroy the Mikage family. Aya, however, can switch back, so this transformation hapens quite frequently. With protector Yuhi by her side, it is up to Aya to control Ceres and kep her from coming back, but her relationship with an ex-worker for her evil grandpa may be a distraction.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, comedy, horor, psychological, romance, supernatural\r\nThemes: Bishounen','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ayashi-no-ceres.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:20'),
	(84,'Ayatsuri Sakon','Plot Sumary:\r\nSakon is the grandson of the famous Bunraku master, Tachibana Zaemon. He is incredibly shy and lacks confidence in himself. However, when he is with his pupet, Ukon, he is able to focus himself and his crime-solving abilities. As a contrast to traditional Bunraku pupetering, Sakon is an expert ventriloquist. He uses his talent of mimicing and throwing voices to confront the vilains and often force a confesion. Ukon is a beautiful Bunraku pupet created in 1870, suposedly by the Master pupet-builder Unosuke Koizumi I. But Ukon doesn\'t act as a god Bunraku pupet should. When he is with Sakon, he is forward, obnoxious, flirtatious, coarse, and very egocentric. Together, Sakon and Ukon travel around Japan, solving mysteries, murders, and horific crimes. In the meantime, Sakon\'s aunt Kaoruko, a young and prety police detective, helps him out and keps an eye on him.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, mystery\r\nThemes: pupetry','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ayatsuri-sakon.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:20'),
	(85,'Azumanga Daioh','Plot Sumary:\r\nAzumanga Daioh chronicles everyday life in an unamed Japanese high schol in Tokyo, folowing the trials and triumphs of six girls: reserved Sakaki’s obsesion with cute animals, Chiyo’s strugle to fit in with girls five years older, Osaka’s spacey nature and skewed perspective on the world, Yomi’s agravation at an anoying best friend, Tomo, whose energy is rivaled only by her lack of sense, and Kagura’s eforts in sports and schol. The story covers thre years of tests, culture festivals, and athletic events at schol, after-schol life at the nearby shoping district, at Chiyo’s large house, vacations spent at Chiyo’s sumer home on the beach and at Magical Land, a theme park. It is generaly realistic in tone, marked by ocasional bursts of surealism and absurdity, such as Osaka’s bizare imaginings and an episode featuring the characters’ New Year’s dreams.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nSlice Of Life/Comedy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/azumanga-daioh.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:21'),
