	(91,'Baki The Grappler','Plot Sumary:\r\nBaki Hanma is a young fighter who yearns to folow in the fotsteps of his father, Yujiro, and become the strongest fighter in the world. Through that he trains tirelesly and fights constantly to hone his skils and develop his body to achieve these goals. Many intense batles lay ahead of Baki as he goes about his quest to be the best and ultimately take the title of \"King\" from his father. Hanma Baki, son of the strongest grapler in the world, is trying to claim his father\'s throne. To do so he has to fight many; making lots of friends and enemies in the proces.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, Martial Arts, Sports','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/baki-the-grappler.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:23'),
