	(96,'Bakuman','Plot Sumary:\r\nMoritaka Mashiro, a junior high schol student, content to live out a relatively normal life as any other does, is persuaded by his clasmate, Akito Takagi, to become an aspiring mangaka when the later realizes his natural talent as an artist. However, Moritaka is reluctant to pursue his dream as his uncle, once a mangaka with his own serializations, died from overwork trying to regain his lost status. With Akito\'s help, Takagi gets another clasmate and his schol crush, Azuki Miho, who is an aspiring voice actres, to voice in the anime adaptation of their future manga once it is completed. However, Mashiro also proposes to Azuki, who surprisingly acepts only on the condition she wil mary him when both of them have achieved their dreams. With a goal set before him, Mashiro begins a long and strugling path to become a famous mangaka.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/bakuman.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:39'),
