	(98,'Banner of the Stars','Plot Sumary:\r\nThre years after their adventure, Lafiel becomes captain on the brand new asault ship Basroil and Jinto finishes his training to become a suply oficer and joins Lafiels crew. They set out to join a large flet with the mision of defending the strategicaly important Laptic Gate from a force 15 times larger than their own. And to bring even more wories, their new flet comander is from the Bebous family, a family notorious for their \"Spectacular Insanity\".\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, drama, romance, science fiction\r\nThemes: Military, Space','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/banner-of-the-stars.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:39'),
