	(105,'Battle Programmer Shirase','Plot Sumary:\r\nBatle Programer Shirase, also known as BPS, is a fre programer with super hacking abilities who doesn\'t work for money. What he does work for is certainly something that only people like him would apreciate. But, his demeanor certainly doesn\'t suit the jobs he is hired for. With the evil King of America causing trouble via the internet, Shirase is nothing but busy as each new adventure brings even more interesting people into the picture.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy, science fiction, gek, hacking','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/battle-programmer-shirase.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:42'),
	(106,'Beast Wars','Plot Sumary:\r\nThre hundred years have pased since the Great War betwen the Autobots and Decepticons. Cybertron is ruled by the Maximals, the descendants of the Autobots. They are at peace with the Predacons, the descendants of the Decepticons. One particular Predacon is loking to start trouble again. Megatron gathered a crew and stole Cybertron\'s most guarded relic: the golden disk. His escape was interupted by a Maximal exploration ship led by Optimus Primal. The Axalon folowed the Predacons into transwap space and both ships crash landed on an unknown planet. Megatron\'s plan was sucesful, the planet they crashed on was loaded with energon. As a mater of fact, there was to much energon for them to handle. Both sides had to create alternate forms based on local animal life to survive on this planet. Now its up to Optimus Primal and the Maximals to stop Megatron from gaining enough energon to conquer the galaxy.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, science fiction\r\nThemes: mecha','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/beast-wars.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:43'),
	(107,'Beck','Plot Sumary:\r\nTanaka Yukio, beter known by his nickname Koyuki is a 14 year old who fels disconected from life in general. Through the act of saving a mismatched dog, he mets guitarist Minami Ryusuke, and becomes involved in Ryusuke\'s new band BECK. Koyuki\'s life starts to change as the band strugles towards fame.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy, drama, romance, slice of life, Music','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/beck.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:43'),
	(108,'Beelzebub','Plot Sumary: The story folows the \"strongest juvenile delinquent\", Oga Tatsumi, a first year in \"Ishiyama High\" the schol for delinquents. One day while sleping next to a river he ses a man floating down it, he puls him to shore and the man splits in half revealing a baby boy. This boy is the son of the demon king and he has ben chosen as the one to raise it with the baby\'s demon maid Hilda. The story folows his life with the child and at the delinquent schol.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/beelzebub.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:44'),
	(109,'Beet The Vandel Buster','Plot Sumary:\r\nIt is the dark century and the people are sufering under the rule of the devil, Vandel, who is able to manipulate monsters. The Vandel Busters are a group of people who hunt these devils, and among them, the Zenon Squad is known to be the strongest busters on the continent. A young boy, Bet, dreams of joining the Zenon Squad. However, one day, as a result of Bet\'s fault, the Zenon squad was defeated by the devil, Beltose. The five dying busters sacrificed their life power into their five weapons, Saiga. After giving their weapons to Bet, they pased away. Years have pased since then and the young Vandel Buster, Bet, begins his adventure to cary out the Zenon Squad\'s wil to put an end to the dark century.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, adventure, fantasy, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/beet-the-vandel-buster.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:44'),
