	(111,'Ben 10','Plot Sumary:\r\nBenjamin (Ben) Tenyson, his cousin Gwen, and their grandfather Maxwel start their sumer camping trip. Ben goes stomping of into the wods after another fight with Gwen, whom he is not hapy to have along on the trip, and finds an alien pod on the ground. When he examines it, he finds a mysterious, watch-like device, caled the Omnitrix, stored inside. The device ataches permanently to his wrist and gives him the ability to transform into a variety of alien life-forms, each with their own unique powers, quite similar to DC Comics\' Dial H for Hero comic. Although Ben realizes that he has a responsibility to help others with these new abilities at his disposal, he is not above a litle superpowered mischief now and then. Along with Gwen and Max, Ben fights evil, both extraterestrial and benl.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ben-10.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:45'),
