	(116,'Binbou Shimai Monogatari','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe Yamada sisters, Kyo (15) and Asu (9), are students studying in secondary and primary schols respectively. Their mother has pased away while their father ran away after incuring debts due to gambling. Despite the dificult circumstances, both of them decide to overcome the unhapines and welcome their days with enthusiasm and pride. Fortunately, with the change in the law system several years ago, Kyo is able to study and simultaneously, take up temporary jobs (such as distributing newspapers and tutoring) so as to suport the family and make ends met. On the other hand, Asu wil take charge of household chores, prepare meals and manage the financials to asist her older sister. Surounding them are also god and kind neighbours such as the novelist, Saegusa-san, and the aunt at the public bath who wil watch over them. Although life is dificult and at times painful, the sisters are hapy to have each other.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: comedy, drama, slice of life','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/binbou-shimai-monogatari.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:57','2012-03-07 01:47:47'),
