	(139,'Boku wa Tomodachi ga Sukunai','Plot Sumary:Hasegawa Kodaka has transfered schols, and he\'s having a hard time making friends. It doesn\'t help that his blond hair tends to make people think he\'s a delinquent. One day, he runs into his bad-tempered solitary clasmate Yozora while she\'s talking animatedly to her imaginary friend Tomo. Realizing that neither of them have any actual friends, they decide that the best way to alter this situation is to form a club and start recruiting.\r\n\r\nThat is how \"Rinjinbu\" was formed, a club specificaly designed for people who don\'t have very many friends. As other lonely clasmates slowly join their litle club, they\'l try to learn how to build friendships through coking together, playing games, and other group activities. But wil this group of relationship-chalenged misfits realy be able to get along?','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/boku-ha-tomodachi-ga-sukunai.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:47:57'),
