	(144,'Boukyaku no Senritsu','Plot Sumary:\r\nA great war ocured in the 20th century betwen humans and monsters. Since that time, the monsters rule the world in fear but kep relatively hiden from public view. A boy named Boka ponders the past and wonders what became of the Meros Wariors who defended the world so bravely against the demons. He son mets Kurofune and learns of the power of the Meros and the I-bar machines they ride in batle. Wariors are the only ones who can se and hear the Melody of Oblivion, a phantom girl hiden away waiting to be rescued and be the savior of mankind. During a batle betwen Kurofune and a demon, Boka discovers something only his wildest dreams could posibly imagine.he to can hear that melody. Throughout his journeys, Boka mets many monsters and their agents, friends, and companions as he discovers the true extent of his new powers. He must continue to batle evil in the hope of releasing Boukyaku no Senritsu and fre a world that has forgoten its once beautiful melody.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, horor, psychological, romance, science fiction, supernatural\r\nThemes: Mecha','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/boukyaku-no-senritsu.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:47:59'),
