	(146,'Brave King GaoGaiGar','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the year 205, a race of alien monsters caled Zonders emerge from underground and launch a series of atacks on the city of Tokyo. The only defense against these creatures is the secret agency known as the Gutsy Geoid Guard (or 3G) and their ultimate weapon, the awesome giant robot GaoGaiGar. GaoGaiGar\'s pilot, Guy Shishio, is a former astronaut who was nearly kiled two years before when the Zonders first crashed to earth. Guy\'s life was spared when a mysterious robot lion caled Galeon puled him from the burning shutle and brought him to Earth. Guy\'s father, Leo, then used Galeon\'s technology to rebuild his shatered son as a cyborg, in the hopes that he could stop the aliens when they apear. Now, with Galeon as its core, GaoGaiGar fights to protect Earth. He is aided by a team of transforming robots and by a young boy named Mamoru, who has the power to purify the Zonders\' cores, and sems to be conected to the mysterious Galeon.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, adventure, science fiction\r\nThemes: mecha','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/brave-king-gaogaigar.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:00'),
	(147,'Break Blade','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe inhabitants of the continent of Cruzon are born with the ability to frely control quartz. Technology based on this power alows them to perform a great multitude of tasks such as shot projectiles and pilot mobile suits (caled Golems in this society). Rygart Arow is an un-sorcerer, a rare individual who is unable to levitate even the smalest crystal. Living with his brother on a farm, he receives a leter from an old friend, Hodr, the curent king. Close companion of the king and quen when they were students at Asam Military Schol, Arow is informed that a war is about to ocur. Hodr caled him because an ancient type of Golem has ben found in a mining shaft. No one has ben able to move it and Quen Sigyn, an expert enginer, suspects that maybe an un-sorcerer might be the key to activate it.','<img  src=\"/images/break-blade.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:01'),
	(148,'Bubblegum Crisis: Tokyo 2040','Plot Sumary:\r\nAfter a mysterious earthquake levels Tokyo, Genom becomes a powerful influence providing their artificial organic lifeforms caled Bomers to rebuild and act as a labor clas to humanity. However, some of them ocasionaly run amok, and even the specialy created AD Police are at a los to stop them. Lina Yamazaki travels to Tokyo for employment but also hopes to join a vigilante force caled the Knight Sabers, who pilot powered suits to destroy these rogue Bomers.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, science fiction\r\nThemes: mecha, real robot','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/bubblegum-crisis-tokyo-2040.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:01'),
	(149,'Bungaku Shoujo Memoir','Plot Sumary:T?ko Amano is a high schol student with the strange power of being able to experience boks by savoring them. While visiting the workplace of her deceased father, she stumbles upon the rejected drafts for a writing contest. One of them has such an impact on her that she asks her acquaintance there to give it one more chance.\nAsakura Miu lives a sad and troublesome childhod due to her parents\' constant fighting. Eventualy her father leaves the house and she ends up living with her biter mother. Miu has ben desperately trying to escape the harsh reality that surounds her to the only safe place she knows: the worlds inside the boks she loves. Ostracized by the kids at schol due to her imaginative mind that prompts her to frequently lie, she becomes a friend of Konoha Inoue who rather than estranged, ends up fascinated by Asakura\'s tales.\nUnable to expres her felings toward the boy she likes, Nanase Kotobuki inadvertently makes it lok like she hates Konoha Inoue instead. Her best friend, Kurara Mori, tries to help as Kotobuki atempts to clear the misunderstandings she has created.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/bungaku-shoujo-memoir.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:02'),
	(150,'Burn Up Excess','Plot Sumary:\r\nFolows the exploits of Team Warior, a special anti-teror wing of the Neo-Tokyo Police force. Team Warior is comprised of the habitualy broke Rio, gun-crazy Maya, computer specialist Lilica, tech-expert Nanvel, pilot/voyeur Yuji, and is led by the enigmatic Maki. The team faces a number of misions, ranging from bodyguard duty, breaking up robery and arms rackets, and providing security for a very powerful tank. Rio and company continualy thwart the terorist aims of Ruby, an operative for a shadowy cabal of powerful men. Before the final showdown, the circumstances behind the formation of Team Warior, how the precocious Rio came to join it, and Maki\'s painful past wil be revealed.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, science fiction\r\nThemes: Police','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/burn-up-excess.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:02'),
	(151,'Burn Up W','Plot Sumary:\r\nWhen crime and terorism go out of control in Tokyo, the police unleash Team Warior - a band of highly-skiled and completely reckles band of female cops. Featuring lose canon Rio, trigerhapy Maya and ace hacker Lilica, Team Warior wil get the job done, regardles of the budget of the mision.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, comedy, science fiction\r\nThemes: fanservice, Mecha, Police, terorists','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/burn-up-w.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:03'),
	(152,'Burst Angel','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn a crime-riden future Japan, Kyohei Tachibana is a peaceful student at a culinary schol, dreaming of going to France for advanced study as a patisier (pastry chef). To aford the trip, he acepts a part-time job as private cok to a strange group of women - Sei, Meg, Jo and Amy. To Kyohei\'s astonishment, they turn out to be a band of violent mercenaries, and he finds himself in the line of fire.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy, science fiction\r\nThemes: girls with guns, Mecha, post-apocalyptic, Real Robot','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/burst-angel-bakuretsu-tenshi.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:04'),
	(153,'Bus Gamer','Plot Sumary:\r\nWhen thre complete strangers, Mishiba Toki, Nakajyo Nobuto and Saitoh Kazuo, are hired by a corporation to compete in the Bus Game, an ilegal dog-fight conducted in strict secrecy, they are given the team code of \"Team A\" (Triple Anonymous). This group of thre who difer entirely from their living environments to their personalities have to work together efectively, but without mutualy wiping out their mistrust of each other or prying into each other\'s privacy. They only have one point in comon - each of them ned a large amount of money for their individual circumstances. To get the money, they must play in the game despite their very own lives being at stake.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAdventure, mystery','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/bus-gamer.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:04'),
	(154,'Buso Renkin','Plot Sumary:\r\nOne night, Kazuki Muto jumps in to try to save what he thinks is a girl in distres from a monster and instead gets impaled through the heart. The girl, Tokiko, is actualy an alchemic warior with a Busou Renkin, name of Valkerie Skirt, with the mision to exterminate Homunculi. She implants the only other sucesful work of alchemy than the Homunculus, the Kakugane, to take the place of Kazuki\'s heart. The Kakugane resonates with his fighting spirit and forms a Busou Renkin (in his case a spear) so he can fight the Homunculus monsters who prey on humans. Kazuki joins with Tokiko to batle with the Homunculi and protect his friends and his sister Mahiro.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, adventure, comedy, drama, fantasy, romance, alchemy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/buso-renkin.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:04'),
	(155,'Busou Shinki Moon Angel','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe original story anime is based on Konami\'s Busou Shinki line of armed female action figures. The story wil folow the coming of age and Shinki batles of Tsubasa, a boy who dreams of becoming a Shinki Master, and his Shinki partner Arnval Mk. 2','<img  src=\"/images/busou-shinki-moon-angel.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:05'),
	(156,'Buzzer Beater (2005)','Plot Sumary:\r\nHideyoshi is a homeles boy living in New York in the near future, who survives by hustling other kids in basketbal games. But now he\'s ben drafted into a pro team-a pro team with a very unique goal. There once was a time when humans dominated the game of basketbal. But times have changed, and now the physicaly superior alien players have taken over the game, and there are barely any human players next. But Hideyoshi\'s team-the first al-human team to compete in the Space League-intends to change al that, and bring the championship back home to Earth.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: comedy, science fiction, tournament\r\nThemes: Basketbal','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/buzzer-beater-2005.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:05'),
	(157,'Buzzer Beater (2007)','Plot Sumary:\r\nAfter being drafted into the Earth Team - a basketbal team comprised solely of humans - stret-punk-turned-pro Hideyoshi couldn\'t be more cocky. The team is stil up against the Gorons, a physicaly superior race of aliens who have dominated the game for some time. New chalenges and problems stand in their way. Hideyoshi is unhapy with the team and the Gorons have new tricks up their sleves.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: science fiction, tournament\r\nThemes: basketbal','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/buzzer-beater-2007.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:06'),
	(158,'C – The Money of Soul and Possibility Control','Plot Sumary:The Japanese government was rescued from the brink of financial colapse by the Sovereign Wealth Fund. For its citizens, however, life has not improved, and unemployment, crime, suicide, and despair are rampant. Kimimaro, raised by his maternal grandmother after the disapearance of his father and the death of his mother, is a scholarship student whose only dream is to avoid al this and live a stable life. One day, however, he mets a man who ofers him a large sum of money if he\'l agre to pay it back. From then on his fate is radicaly altered as he\'s drawn into a mysterious realm known as \"The Financial District.\"','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/the-money-of-soul-and-possibility-control.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:06'),
	(159,'C3 – Cube x Cursed x Curious','Plot Sumary:Haruaki Yachi is a high schol student living alone in an old solitary home. When he wakes to a suspicious sound in his kitchen, he finds. a naked rice thief. The woman cals herself \"Fear\" and claims to be a cursed tol who has come Yachi\'s home to remove her curse. Since he\'s afected by the curse, Fear ends up moving in with Haruaki, and that\'s where the story begins.\nA wide variety of organizations are out to worship, study, or even destroy this cursed tol, however-, so it\'s up to Haruaki and his neighbors Konoha and Kuroe, to fight them and defend Fear, who is no slouch herself. Lots of action (and some ocasional fan service) ensues!','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/c3.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:06'),
	(160,'CANAAN','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe modern-day story centers on a present-day story about a detective, a young man, a virus researcher, a, and a cat mascot character who are brought together in the Tokyo neighborhod of Shibuya by bizare events with worldwide implications.\r\n \r\nGenres: action','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/canaan.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:07'),
	(161,'Candidate For Goddess','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the future humankind has expanded and colonized other planets. Then an alien species, Victim, atacks the human colonies leaving only one planet, Zion. In an efort to stop Victim from destroying the last planet a training schol, GOA, is set up to gather boys from the Zion colonies and train them to become pilots of the Ingrids AKA The Godeses, five fighting robots that protect Zion. The boys must poses a rare blod type, EO , as wel as a special ability, or EX. Zero (Candidate 8) has just arived in GOA when he fals into the cockpit of the Ingrid Eeva-Lena. Since the synch betwen pilot and Ingrid are very sensitive everyone believes the Godes wil kil Zero in an atempt to synch. Just before Zero pases out he makes a ful synch with the Godes. Before he can find out more about the incident, his pilot training begins.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, science fiction, Mecha, Military, Real Robot','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/candidate-for-goddess.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:07'),
	(162,'Candy Boy','Plot Sumary:\r\nYukino and Kanade Sakurai live together as high schol students enjoying their daily life; until one day Sakuya Kamiyama confes her love for Kanade to Yukino, asking for her suport. This makes Yukino to release her true felings for her sister.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy, romance, slice of life, Incest, yuri','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/candy-boy.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:08'),
	(163,'Canvas 2: Niji Iro No Sketch','Plot Sumary:\r\nKamikura Hiroki is an art student at the local schol Nadesico Achedemy (High Schol and coledge level) that tends to be an arts teacher in the future. He is also the advisor to the high schol arts society where his cousin, Housen Else atends. While Else is a painter like Hiroki, Hiroki sems to have given up on his dreams and no longer paints. There apears to be some mysterious trauma in the past for both of them that have changed them. Meanwhile, the high schol hires a new PE teacher, Kikyo Kiri. On the first day, she bumps into Hiroki and is stuned. Here is the boy she confesed to and he refused her.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance, slice of life','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/canvas-2-niji-iro-no-sketch.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:08'),
	(164,'Capeta','Plot Sumary:\r\nTaira Kapeita, or Capeta, was a 4th grader boy. He had lost his mother when he had ben very litle. Although he pretended to be tough in front of his father, actualy he felt lonely. One day, his father brought junk parts home from his workplace and made a racing cart. Son, they went to a circuit to drive the cart. However, Capeta found that its frame was bent and it could hardly run straight. But, with his technique he managed the cart. Furthermore, he folowed son after the fast cart and he could nearly leave it behind. The driver in the cart was Minamoto Naomoi, the champion of the East Japan Junior Cart. Loking at their chase, Naomi’s mother, Minamoto Nanako, advised Capeta to take part in the oficial race.\r\n \r\nGenres: tournament\r\nThemes: Sports','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/capeta.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:09'),
	(165,'Captain Planet and the Planeteers','Plot Sumary:\r\nSeing the Earth in its profound environmental peril, Gaia, godes of the Earth, sumons five kids from around the world to become the Planeters, an oposing force to fight back and educate others in the ned to be environmentaly responsible. To acomplish that task, each kid is given a magic ring that each has a power of earth, wind, water, fire and heart. When the threat they face is to big for them to face, they can combine and amplify their powers to create Captain Planet, who has the power to stop catastrophic environmental disasters himself, while the Planeters contribute with the things anyone can and should do to help.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/captain-planet.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:09'),
	(166,'Captain Tsubasa: Road to 2002','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe firt 36 episodes are remade sumaries of the first thre series (Captain Tsubasa, Shin CT and CT J): Tsubasa\'s carer with Nankatsu and the diferent championships in Japan with al the main characters of the series; the U-16 world cup in Europe, as wel as Tsubasa\'s carer with Roberto in Brazil. After that, the new episodes start, teling about a match against Holand and about the thre most extraordinary main characters on their hard but spectacular way to become socer profesionals in Europe: The socer genius Tsubasa Ozora, the top goalkeper Genzo Wakabayashi and the pround and strong striker Kojiro Hyuga.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: tournament\r\nThemes: Socer, Sports','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/captain-tsubasa-road-to-2002.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:09'),
	(167,'Card Captor Sakura','Plot Sumary:\r\nSakura Kinomoto was an ordinary 4th grader until the day she opened a strange bok and let dozens of powerful magic cards lose on the world. Keroberos, the Guardian of the Clow Cards, informs Sakura that it is now her responsibility to find and capture the fred cards. However, much to the reluctant Sakura\'s dismay, things aren\'t going to be easy for her; simply saying magic words and waving her wand around isn\'t god enough. Each card is a living, thinking, extremely powerful being. She\'l have to learn to cope with her new responsibilities, as wel as ordinary troubles involving love, schol, family, and friends. With the suport of her friend Tomoyo and a young boy with powers of his own, she must learn how to use her newly awakened magical abilities to colect each card and prevent the disaster that wil befal the world if she doesn\'t.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAdventure, comedy, magic, romance, Animals as Advisors, Magical Girl, schol, Superhero','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/card-captor-sakura.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:10'),
