	(169,'Cardfight!! Vanguard','Plot Sumary:The protagonist of this story, Sendo Aichi, is a timid boy in his third year of midle schol. He had ben living his life loking backward rather than forward, trying not to stand out. However, he had one thing that kept him going - the \"Blaster Blade,\" a card from a card game that was given to him when he was litle. That card is the reason why he begins to engage in Card Fights, something that changes his life drasticaly.\nThe name of the card game is \"Vanguard.\" The game takes place in a diferent planet caled \"Klay,\" and due to a never before sen play system, it becomes popular throughout the world.\nAichi, imediately atracted by Vanguard, mets friends such as Togura Misaki and Katsuragi Kamui, along with other rivals. Through friendly rivalry with them, Aichi begins to enjoy a fulfiling life. Aichi, however, has a goal: to once again batle with a Vanguard Fighter by the name of Kai Tosihki. Kai Toshiki is an alof and cold-hearted high scholer who has outstanding abilities in the world of Vanguard. He is also the reason why Aichi started playing the game. For him, Toshiki is the person who saved him from his boring life and introduced him to Vanguard. In order to get beter at Vanguard, Aichi puts his soul into it every day. He wishes that someday, he\'l be able to batle Toshiki and have him recognize his worth.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/cardfight-vanguard.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:11'),
	(170,'Carnival Phantasm','Plot Sumary:This anime is based on Takenashi Eri’s Take Mon manga and comemorates Type-Mon’s 10th aniversary. Various characters from Type-Mon’s works such as Kara no Kyoukai, Fate/Stay Night, and Tsukihime are featured in this.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/carnival-phantasm.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:11'),
	(171,'Carried by the Wind: Tsukikage Ran','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the Edo or Tokugawa period (160-1868),Ran,a female wandering samurai whose skil with the katana is only matched by her taste for sake (rice wine),is joined by a chinese martial artist who cals herself Lady Meow of the Iron Cat Fist.Together,these two women face antagonists of al kinds.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, adventure, comedy, Historical','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/carried-by-the-wind-tsukikage-ran.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:12'),
	(172,'Casshern Sins','Plot Sumary:\r\nAfter decades since the original anime series, the cybernetic warior returns in this franchise rebot, Cashern Sins. In a world where the powerful robot leader known as Braiking Bos rule over humanity with an iron fist, a mysterious girl named Luna is sumoned by the people for salvation. To retaliate against this potential threat, Braiking sends 3 of his most powerful cyborgs, Cashern, Dio and Reda to dispose of her. Cashern manages to kil Luna, plunging the world into a slow descent of anhilation. Hundreds of years later, humanity is almost extinct. Robots constantly replace their body parts, fearing the corosion of rust: their only form of death. In this wretched time and place, Cashern returns after a lengthy disapearance since his murder of Luna. Having lost his memory, Cashern now defends the humans from the robots, and find out his true identity and purpose. \r\n \r\nAfter the murder of Luna, the robot society that rules the planet starts to rust and decay. Death and despair spread through the land like wildfire. The only one unafected by what becomes known as \"The Ruin\" is Luna\'s asasin, Cashern. Unable to remember if he realy trigered this capital sin against the entire mechanized civilization, Cashern embarks on a journey to unravel the mystery that conects him, Luna, and the plague.\r\n \r\nCashern, a subordinate of Braiking Bos, was sent to asasinate Luna after she apeared as a savior to the human race. After the asasination, Cashern disapears with his memory lost. Years later, he resurfaces to fight of anti-human robots in a post-apocalyptic Earth where humans and robots are dying due to \"The Ruin\", an unknown phenomenon which kils of robots by roting their bodies while forcing humans to survive by hiding.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, drama, science fiction, Cyborg','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/casshern-sins.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:12'),
	(173,'Cat Shit One','Plot Sumary:\r\nPacky and Botasky are members of a private military company, a new form of mercenary system. Somewhere on a desert region, they are on a rescue mision and due to the circumstances they must enter combat imediately.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/cat-shit-one.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:12'),
	(174,'Centurions','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the near future, an evil genius, the cyborg Doc Teror, seks to conquer the earth; he is asisted by Hacker, the cyborg sidekick and an army of Dom Drones. There were two types of drones: Traumatizers, the most comonly sen drones, are walking robots with laser blasters for arms, while the Strafer is a flying robot armed with misiles and lasers. Later, a wheled Drone with a large scren and canons as wel as a submarine drone were aded. Doc Teror and Hacker are able to fly by swaping their purely robot half for a Strafer mising one set of wings.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/centurions.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:13'),
	(175,'Chaos Head','Plot Sumary:\r\nTakumi is a high schol student. He is withdrawn and is not interested in 3D things. In his town, a mysterious serial murder case hapens and people get panicked. One day, when he chats on the internet, a man sudenly contacts him and gives him an URL. He goes to the website and finds a blog image that sugests a next murder case. On the next day, it realy hapens.\r\n \r\nTakumi Nishij? sufers from intense delusions as a result of his aparent schizophrenia and the extremely secluded lifestyle he lives as a hikikomori. One day he acidentaly stumbles upon a gruesome murder scene, a part of a chain of events caled \"New Generation.\" After this, his life gets caught up in these events, and he mets a bunch of increasingly insane anime girls with swords.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, drama, horor, mystery, psychological, romance, science fiction, supernatural, thriler','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/chaos-head.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:13'),
