	(177,'Cheeky Angel','Plot Sumary:\r\nMegumi-chan is a girl with a secret past. She used to be a boy until she met a person she thought was a magic user. This person gave him/her a magical bok from which a genie apears to grant one wish when blod is aplied to it. Megumi made the wish to be a man in a man\'s body but the genie has a twist: he grants wishes backwards so he turns Megumi-kun aged 9 to Megumi-chan. Years pas and Megumi enters High Schol where she imediately beats up the schol buly who of course fals in love with her. She is loking for that bok again to be able to reverse the spel placed upon her.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, comedy, romance, supernatural\r\nThemes: gender switch','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/cheeky-angel.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:14'),
