	(179,'Chihayafuru','Plot Sumary:Al her life, Chihaya\'s dream was to se her model sister become Japan\'s best. That is, until a quiet, unasuming transfer student named Arata tels her otherwise. A dream, he explains to her, is something she neds to work at herself.\nArata plays a competitive version of a traditional Japanese card game-known as Hyakunin Ishu-in a way Chihaya has never sen before. After taking Arata\'s place in a game, Chihaya discovers she has a pasion for it. Now Chihaya wants to become number one in the world, the Quen of Karuta.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/chihayafuru.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:15'),
	(180,'Chobits','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the future, personal computers have developed into \"Persocons\", mobile computers that lok like human beings. Hideki Motosuwa, a prep schol student, desperately wants to buy a Persocon but canot aford to. One day he finds a Persocon that has ben thrown away and decides to kep it. When he turns on the Persocon, al she can say is \"Chi\" so he decides to name her that. After a while it starts to become aparent that Chi is more than an average Persocon. Having much beter performance, it sems that Chi might be a \"Chobit\", a type of advanced Persocon rumoured to have independent thought.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy, drama, romance, science fiction, Love, Robot Girl','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/chobits.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:15'),
	(181,'Chocotto Sister','Plot Sumary:\r\nHaruma Kawagoe is an only child. A long time ago, at Christmastime, his mother miscaried the child that was to have ben his baby sister. That night, young Haruma knelt down and ofered up an earnest prayer: \"Please make my mother wel again, and please give me a litle sister.\" Years have pased, and Haruma has nearly forgoten his prayer. But Santa hasn\'t. one Christmas, when Haruma is least expecting it, he gets an unusual present - his sister.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance, slice of life\r\nThemes: fanservice, lolicon, meganeko','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/chocotto-sister.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:16'),
	(182,'Chrome Shelled Regios','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the distant future, a poluted world has ben overtaken by havoc-wreaking creatures caled filth monsters. Humanity, having ben forced to relocate itself, must live in isolated mobile cities caled Regios. A mysteriously skiled fighter named Layfon Alseif enrols in the Academy city of Zuelni and is imediately noticed by Nina Antalk, leader of the 17th Military Arts Unit. He then reluctantly joins her squad, uncertain of what future awaits him and his new teamates within the city as wel as the impending dangers in the midst of a plagued world.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAdventure, fantasy, science fiction, Harem, Martial Arts, Military, Post-Apocalyptic','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/chrome-shelled-regios.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:16'),
	(183,'Chrono Crusade','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe year is 1928 A.D. The place is New York, U.S.A. The economic prosperity brought forth after the Great War also heightened the presence of something far darker and much more sinister: the demonic Siners. The Magdalene Order is an organization that tries to counter this force. Two of its exorcists are Rosete Christopher and her asistant, Chrono. Both apear out of place in an organization like this, and they are in a quest to find Rosete\'s mising brother, Joshua. Their relationships, secrets and fates can only be revealed in time.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, adventure, comedy, drama, romance, supernatural\r\nThemes: Demons, Girls with Guns, Historical, Religion, sad','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/chrono-crusade.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:17'),
	(184,'Chu-Bra!!','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe story centers on Nayu, a midle schol girl who shocks her scholmates on the first day of schol by wearing black lace panties. She likes this kind of underwear, and she tries to “spread the word on the merits of [these kinds of] underwear” via an underwear club with her scholmates, who are woried about their bodies’ development and which underwear to chose.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/chu-bra.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:17'),
