	(186,'Clannad','Plot Sumary:\r\nTomoya Okazaki is a third year high schol student resentful of his life. His mother pased away from a car acident when he was younger, causing his father to resort to alcohol and gambling. This results in fights betwen the two until Tomoya\'s shoulder is injured in a fight. Since then, Tomoya has had distant relationships with his father, causing him to become a delinquent over time. While on a walk to schol, he mets a strange girl named Nagisa Furukawa who is a year older, but is repeating due to ilnes. Due to this, she is often alone as most of her friends have moved on. The two begin hanging out and slowly, as time goes by, Tomoya finds his life shifting in a new direction.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy, drama, psychological, romance, supernatural, schol','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/clannad.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:18'),
	(187,'Clannad After Story','Plot Sumary:\r\nA sequel to the recently wraped anime based on the Key Clanad franchise. After Story is a path that opens in the original visual novel after al the other paths have ben opened.\r\n \r\nLife continues on for Tomoya. A few months have pased since he confesed his love to Nagisa. Now entering his graduating year, he continues to met a variety of diferent people, expanding his own world in the proces. As wel, Tomoya and Nagisa\'s relationship begins to enter a level of intimacy unlike before. Through his relationship with Nagisa, and his various encounters, Tomoya begins to understand the meaning and importance of family. Unfortunately, as Tomoya and Nagisa begin their own family together, they are faced with many hardships and chalenges along the way.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy, drama, psychological, romance, supernatural, schol','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/clannad-after-story.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:18'),
