	(191,'Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe Empire of Britania has invaded Japan using giant robot weapons caled Knightmare Frames. Japan is now refered to as Area 1, and its people the 1\'s. A Britanian who was living in Japan at the time, Lelouch, vowed to his Japanese friend Suzaku that he\'d destroy Britania. Years later, Lelouch is in high schol, but regularly skips out of schol to go play ches and gamble on himself. One day, he stumbles on terorists 1\'s who\'ve stolen a military secret and is caught by a member of the Britanian task force sent after them, who is Suzaku. As the rest of the squad arives, Suzaku is shot for disobeying orders, while the military secret, a young girl, gives Lelouch the power of Geas, which makes anyone obey any order. While Suzaku is secretly made the pilot of Britania\'s brand new prototype Knightmare, Lancelot, Lelouch becomes the masked Zero to lead the rebelion to destroy Britania once and for al.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, drama, psychological, science fiction, supernatural, Mecha, Military, Real Robot','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/code-geass-lelouch-of-the-rebellion.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:20'),
	(192,'Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion R2','Plot Sumary:\r\nIt\'s ben one year since the failure of the Black Rebelion and the suposed death of Zero. Britania has asigned Area 1 a \"corectional education\" status, where Elevens are made an example of by brute force, to try to prevent any future uprisings and supres rebelious thoughts. Unsuspecting high schol student Lelouch, oblivious to his rebelious past as Zero, stumbles upon a scheme on his life and the life of a mysterious woman known as C.C., who reveals to him his forgoten purpose and his \"true\" self. Destroying his asailants and declaring himself Zero once again, Lelouch sets out to finish what he started.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, drama, psychological, science fiction, supernatural, Mecha, Military, Real Robot','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/code-geass-lelouch-of-the-rebellion-r2.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:48:20'),
