	(209,'D Gray Man','Plot Sumary:\r\nAlen Walker, a young man with a cursed eye, lives to destroy a weapon known as Akuma. These weapons created by the Mileneum Earl are sent out by his comand to purge the world from humans. Alen Walker uses an anti-akuma weapon, Inocence, to counter the Earl\'s atempts at destroying humanity. He travels to the Black Order by his mentor\'s directions. There he mets with others who also fight against the Mileneum Earl\'s plans. But more questions start to apear as Alen and his friends move further along to reach their goal. And these questions that sem to conect to Alen\'s past.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, adventure, comedy, drama, fantasy, horor, supernatural, Historical','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/dgray-man.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:10'),
	(210,'Da Capo','Plot Sumary:\r\nJunichi Asakura lives with his adoptive sister Nemu in the crescent-shaped island of Hatsune Jima, a place where chery blosoms blom throughout the year. In this island, people have mysterious powers and atributes. For example, Junichi has the power to se other people\'s dreams, and he was also taught by his grandmother to magicaly create swets. One day, Junichi\'s cousin and childhod friend, Sakura Yoshino came back from America al of a suden. To Junichi\'s surprise, she loks exactly the same as the girl that moved away six years ago, and hasn\'t aged one bit. And she came back to remind Junichi of their childhod promise. It is a biterswet tale of magic, love, hiden desires, and unatainable dreams.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, psychological, romance, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/da-capo.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:10'),
	(211,'Da Capo II','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe protagonist, Yoshiyuki Sakurai, was born when Sakura Yoshino, weary of being alone for so long, wished upon a prototype artificial wish-granting magical sakura tre for a family. Similar to its predecesor, the story takes place on the same island, Hatsunejima, in Japan, and set fifty-thre years after the original anime. The Asakura sisters are the grandaughters of Junichi Asakura and Nemu Asakura from the first Da Capo. Sakura Yoshino and Junichi are the only returning characters, and Nemu is the only other character to be mentioned by name.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/da-capo-ii.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:11'),
	(212,'Daa! Daa! Daa!','Plot Sumary:\r\nMiyu is an 8th grade girl, whose parents have ben hired by NASA. They take of to America leaving Miyu with Mr. Saionji. Later, Mr. Saionji decides to go on a 1 year long trip to India leaving Miyu alone with his son, Kanata. More complications rise when an Alien baby and his babysiter pet crashes/lands in their house. To make things worse, alien baby starts caling Miyu and Kanata Mom and Dad, also showing ESP power and floating around.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, comedy, drama, mystery, romance, science fiction','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/daa-daa-daa.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:11'),
	(213,'Daiguard','Plot Sumary:\r\nThirten years after their suden disapearance, an alien race known as the Heterodyne resurface without warning. To combat the Heterodyne, thre ofice workers from the 21st Century Security Corporation operate Dai-Guard - a giant robot no longer regarded as an oversized paperweight. Unfortunately, Dai-Guard is somewhat obsolete and in disrepair. It\'s a tough job, but salarymen can also save the world.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, adventure, comedy, science fiction\r\nThemes: Mecha, Military','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/daiguard.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:12'),
