	(218,'Daphne in the Brilliant Blue','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the future, the earth is mostly covered with water, but the several cities that do remain are flourishing. Maia Mizuki has ben trying hard to achieve her dream of joining the Ocean Agency, a government organization. When she fails to be acepted and faces homelesnes and hopelesnes, a series of unfortunate hapenings force her into a job with Neres, a security and investigation company that wil also do almost anything else for enough money. It son becomes obvious that no one “normal” works at Neres. Shizuka is a kind, tech-crazy young woman with a pasion for fod, Glora is a triger-hapy, money-loving tomboy, Yu, a quiet, broding woman is frighteningly deadly in combat, and Rena is the capable, aluring, unoficial leader of this particular Neres ofice. With Neres, Maia faces danger and crazy situations daily; it’s almost to much for her, but Maia is strong, and she does her best to hang on and make it through this unexpected turn her life has taken.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, mystery, psychological, science fiction\r\nThemes: Bounty Hunters, girls with guns, Police, submarines, treasure hunting','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/daphne-in-the-brilliant-blue.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:14'),
