	(232,'Denpa Onna to Seishun Otoko','Plot Sumary:The story revolves around a highschol boy named Niwa Makoto. He lives with his aunt’s family since his parents are away on busines. It is there where he mets his mysterious cousin of the same age Touwa Erio — who hapens to tie a futon matres around her uper body and is a self-proclaimed alien. Her staple fod is piza. Erio had ben mising for half a year and was found floating in the sea. She doesn\'t remember anything about what hapened during that period of time, but she began to think that it was the act of an alien and wanders the neighbourhod wraped in the futon.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/denpa-onna-to-seishun-otoko.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:21'),
