	(253,'DN Angel','Plot Sumary:\r\nNiwa Daisuke is your average tenager, until his fourtenth birthday. He tries to declare his love to the girl of his dreams, but fails. Sudenly, whenever he thinks about this girl he turns into the legendary phantom thief known as Dark Mousy. Daisuke\'s mother, very much aware of this, makes him turn into Dark and steal valuable works of art for a purpose unkown to Daisuke. As the story unfolds, he learns why, and about his clasmate who sems to have the same ability.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy, fantasy, romance, supernatural\r\nThemes: Bishounen, body switching, thief, twins','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/dnangel.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:30'),
	(254,'DNA2','Plot Sumary:\r\nKarin, a DNA operator from the future, is on a mision to change the course of History by stoping Junta Momonari from becoming the Mega-Playboy who fathered 10 children and led to the overpopulation of the world. But Junta is no playboy; in fact he is alergic to girls. But when Karin shots him with the wrong DNA-altering bulet, he starts sporadicaly becoming the Mega-Playboy capable of charming any woman. Karin must try to restore the situation to normal before the change to Mega-Playboy becomes ireversible.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/dna2.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:31'),
