	(256,'Dogs: Bullets & Carnage OVA','Plot Sumary:\r\nSometime in the future, somewhere in Europe a city has many levels of underground, even secret dangerous levels that have answers to the past. Mihai is a retired asasin who has returned home to setle a vendeta and start a new life as a restaurant owner. Haine was geneticaly experimented on as a child, which led to him posesing dog like atributes. Badou is his clumsy chain smoking partner who becomes deranged when denied cigaretes. Naoto was orphaned as a child and has amnesia she was trained to wield the sword. Their pasts are somehow conected to the secret underground and the organization that controls it.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAdventure, drama, mystery, science fiction','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/dogs-bullets-carnage-ova.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:32'),
	(257,'Dojin Work','Plot Sumary:\r\nDoujin Work folows the life of a young girl named Najimi Osana and her exposure into the doujin world. She was first tempted into becoming a doujin artist after seing how much one of her friends can make at a convention. Najimi loves to draw, though son learns contrary to what she expected that this new world is anything but easy. As she atends more conventions and mets more people, Najimi eventualy manages to find a group of very interesting friends. These friends already have some experience in the field and help her out along the way so that she can someday make a name for herself creating doujinshi.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: comedy\r\nThemes: Art','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/dojin-work.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:32'),
