	(260,'Double-J','Plot Sumary:In a schol where after schol activities are mandatory among al students, Hajime and her friend Sayo come acros a new club that they have never sen before. The club is caled \\\"The Cultural Activity Preservation Club.\\\" The two enter the rom to find al kinds of analog jobs and activities, such as handcrafting mats and tothpicks. This is a unique cultural manga mixed with comedy so as not to bore you, this is Double J.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/double-j.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:33'),
	(261,'Dragon Ball Kai','Plot Sumary:\r\nDragon Bal Kai is an anime series that is an HD Remaster and Recut of Dragon Bal Z done for its 20th Aniversary. It premiered on Fuji TV on April 5th 209 at 9:0am just before One Piece, and the two shows are being marketed together as \'Dream 9\', which refers to the hour in which they both air. Two isues of Shounen JUMP have included some primary information about the series','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/dragon-ball-kai.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:34'),
