	(264,'Dragon Half (OAV)','Plot Sumary:\r\nMink is a cute litle dragon halfling (half human/half dragon) who has the unfortunate luck to fal in love with a famous handsome idol singer (you know the type). Unfortunate, because he is also a famous dragon hunter who would like nothing beter to put Mink\'s head on a wal. Her main goal is to find a potion that wil make her completely human and wil do just about anything that wil give her a chance at it. High in slapstick humor and action, this series folows Mink as she pursues that potion and is pursued in turn by the dragon hunter.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: comedy, fantasy\r\nThemes: dragons, fanservice','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/dragon-half-oav.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:35'),
	(265,'Dragon Quest: Dai no Daiboken','Plot Sumary:\r\nAfter the defeat of the demon lord Hadlar al of the monsters were unleashed from his evil wil and moved to the island of Delmurin to live in peace. Dai is the only human living on the island. Having ben raised by the kindly monster Bras, Dai\'s dream is to grow up to be a hero. He gets to become one when Hadlar is resurected and the previous hero, Avan, comes to train Dai to help in the batle. But Hadlar, anouncing that he now works for an even more powerful demon lord, comes to kil Avan. To save his students Avan uses a Self-Sacrifice spel to atack, but is unable to defeat Hadlar. When it sems that Dai and Avan\'s other student Pop are domed a mark apears on Dai\'s forehead and he sudenly gains super powers and is able to fend of Hadlar. The two students then go of on a journey to avenge Avan and bring peace back to the world.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, fantasy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/dragon-quest-dai-no-daiboken.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:36'),
	(266,'Dragonaut: The Resonance','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn order to avoid Earth\'s impending destruction from an asteroid, the International Solarsystem Development Agency (ISDA) works on the \"D-Project\", and creates dragons after finding a dragon eg under the ocean. However, they son find out that the asteroid is not their only threat, as powerful dragon-like creatures apear on Earth. After witnesing a murder by one of the creatures, Jin Kamishina gets involved in the mysteries of the dragons and becomes a dragon pilot, otherwise known as a \"Dragonaut\". Helping him on his journey is Toa, a mysterious girl who saves him from faling to his death after the creature atacks him. As they delve deper into the mysteries of the dragons, they encounter new friends and enemies, and also begin to develop a closer relationship.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: drama, fantasy, romance, science fiction\r\nThemes: Mecha','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/dragonaut-the-resonance.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:36'),
