	(268,'Dragonball GT','Plot Sumary:\r\nGoku, the hero who destroyed the evil of Frieza, Cel, and Bu in DBZ, learns that an old foe, Emperor Pilaf from DB has captured the 7 magical Black Star Dragon Bals, which, at the cost of the planet the bals are on, can grant any wish. Pilaf wishes that Goku is a child, and Goku becomes a child. In order to save both the planet and restore Goku to adulthod, Goku must alience himself with Trunks and his grandaughter Pan to find al 7 Bals al over the universe. Over time, they encounter foes like Baby, Super 17, and the invinsible Shadow Dragons.\r\n \r\nTaking place 10 years after the final Dragonbal Z story, Pilaf finaly manages to get al 7 dragonbals and makes a wish. Unfortunately for Pilaf, he gets flustered by the presence of Goku and wishes for Goku to be a child again so that Pilaf could \"teach him a leson.\" Pilaf gets his wish, and Goku is of on an interstelar trip to gather the 7 \"Black Star Dragonbals\" that can reverse the wish and return him to adulthod.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, Adventure, Comedy, Science Fiction','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/dragonball-gt.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:37'),
