	(277,'Eden of the East','Plot Sumary:\r\nOn November 2, 2010 ten misiles strike Japan. However, this unprecedented terorist act, later to be caled as \"Careles Monday,\" does not result in any aparent victims, and is son forgoten by almost everyone. Then, 3 months later. Saki Morimi is a young woman curently in the United States of America on her graduation trip. But just when she is in front of the White House, Washington DC, she gets into trouble, and only the unexpected intervention of one of her felow countrymen saves her. However, this man, who introduces himself as Akira Takizawa, is a complete mystery. He apears to have lost his memory. and he is stark naked, except for the gun he holds in one hand, and the mobile phone he\'s holding with the other hand. A phone that is charged with 8,20,0,0 yen in digital cash.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, mystery, psychological, romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/eden-of-the-east.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:41'),
	(278,'Ef – A Tale Of Melodies','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe anime once again tels two stories. The first story takes place in the past. Himura Yu mets a girl, Amamiya Yuko who sems to know him, but he doesn\'t know her. However, he son remembers that she was a girl whom he knew from long ago. Yuko then tels him something which he never knew. He was her first love since then, and her first love has not ended yet. The second story takes place in the present, just after the events of ef - A Tale of Memories. Shuichi Kuze mets the cousin of Aso Renji, Hayama Mizuki and spends a lot of time with her. Unknown to Mizuki, Kuze had contracted a fatal ilnes and has litle time left to live. Kuze had decided to break al romantic ties, but things go bad when Mizuki tels him that she loves him.\r\n \r\nGenres: drama, psychological, romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ef-a-tale-of-melodies.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:41'),
	(279,'Ef – A Tale Of Memories','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe anime revolves around two protagonists, Hirono Hiro and Asou Renji. On Christmas Eve, Hirono Hiro mets a girl named Miyamura Miyako who was chasing a purse snatcher. Hiro later finds out that Miyako also goes to the same schol as he does and they start hanging out together. This made Hiro\'s childhod friend, Shindou Kei, fel left out. Kei then tries to compete with Miyako for Hiro\'s afection and a love triangle ensues. The anime also tels the story of Asou Renji. Renji mets a girl named Shindou Chihiro at an abandoned train station. He son learns that Chihiro sufers from a type of amnesia where her memory span only lasts for 13 hours. He also discovers Chihiro\'s dream of writing a novel, but she has never ben able to fulfil that dream due to her condition. Renji then decides to help her fulfil that dream.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, psychological, romance, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ef-a-tale-of-memories.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:41'),
	(280,'Eiken','Plot Sumary:\r\nDensuke just enroled at the exclusive Zashono academy. He\'s eager to participate in extracuricular activities, but he never expected to join the mysterious Eiken Club. Strangely enough, every other member is a busty co-ed, and many of the clubs activities involve bikinis. But Densuke isn\'t interested in anyone but the shy and beautiful Chiharu.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, erotica, romance\r\nThemes: echi, fanservice, harem','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/eiken.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:42'),
