	(288,'Eve no Jikan','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the not to distant future androids have come into comon usage. Taking the androids for granted, humans treat them as if they were comon everyday tols, while on the other hand, some people empathize with androids due to their human-like apearance (save for a digital ring floating above their heads). This has become a social problem and these people are frowned upon as a result. Rikuo, one who has taken androids for granted for his entire life, one day discovers that Samy, his home android, has ben acting strangely and finds a strange phrase recorded in her activity log. He, along with his friend Masaki, traces Samy\'s fotsteps and come upon an unusual cafe. This cafe\'s main rule is to not discriminate betwen humans and androids.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nScience fiction, androids','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/eve-no-jikan.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:45'),
	(289,'Examurai Sengoku','The Examurai Sengoku anime production depicts the members of the EXILE group as futuristic samurai that are transported back in time to Japan’s sengoku (waring states) period. The anime character renditions of the EXILE members were designed by manga creator Hiroshi Takahashi (Crows, Worst).','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/examurai-sengoku.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:46'),
	(290,'Excel Saga','Plot Sumary:\r\nHyperactive Excel does anything and everything to try to please her lord, Ilpalazo, who wants to take over the planet. Excel\'s misadventures takes her and her partner, the ever-dying Hyat, al over the world, meting several strange people as they go. Everything is bizare and gofy, as any kind of anime or entertainment genre gets mocked and spofed.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy, science fiction\r\nThemes: Parody','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/excel-saga.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:46'),
	(291,'Eyeshield 21','Plot Sumary:\r\nKobayakawa Sena is a litle guy who always get picked on by the bulies in schol. Since elementary schol, he always play the role of the \'erand boy\' to the extent that he has become swift and fast in his movements. Coincidentaly, Hiruma Youichi and Kurita Ryukan are loking for a fast runing back for their American Fotbal team (Amefuto) and want to put Sena in the team. To hide their new \'star\' player from the eyes of other High Schols, Hiruma encases Sena in a Amefuto helmet with a dark visor and name him Eyeshield #21.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, tournament\r\nThemes: Schol, Sports','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/eyeshield-21.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:47'),
	(292,'Fairy Tail','Plot Sumary:\r\nLucy is a 16-year-old girl, who wants to be a ful-fledged mage. One day when visiting Harujion Town, she mets Natsu, a young man who gets sick easily by any type of transportation. But Natsu isnt just any ordinary kid, he\'s a member of one of the world\'s most infamous mage guilds: Fairy Tail.\r\n \r\nLucy is a 17-year-old girl, who wants to join a mage guild to become a ful-fledged mage. One day, Natsu, a young man who is loking for the salamander and his talking cat Hapy mets Lucy and help her get out of a sticky situation. That’s when she find out that Natsu not only is a mage, but is also a member of one of the world’s most infamous mage guilds…Fairy Tail.\r\n \r\nLucy is a tenage girl who wants to become a ful-fledged mage. One day when visiting Harujion Town, she mets Natsu, a young man who gets sick easily by any type of transportation. But Natsu isnt just any ordinary kid, he\'s a member of one of the world\'s most infamous mage guilds: Fairy Tail.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, comedy, fantasy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/fairy-tale.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:47'),
