	(296,'Fight Ippatsu! Juuden-Chan!!','Plot Sumary:\r\nMet Plug, an unusual girl from a paralel world. Plug is a \"Juden-chan,\" capable of \"recharging\" people down on their luck, spreading god cher wherever she goes!\r\n \r\nGenres: Action, Comedy, Echi, Sci-Fi, Shounen','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/fight-ippatsu-juuden-chan.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:49'),
	(297,'Final Approach','Plot Sumary:\r\nEver since their parents died a few years ago, Ryo and his sister Akane have ben living alone together. Despite their dificult situation, they are stil living reasonably hapy and normal lives. However, everything is about to be fliped upside-down due to a secret government project. Due to increasingly low birth rates in Japan, the Japanese government is testing a program in which two young people are forced to mary. Ryo wants no part of it, but he is given litle choice in the mater; his new fiancée, Shizuka, comes to his home late one night with several dozen government isued bodyguards, who are there to ensure the suces of the new couple. Unlike Ryo, Shizuka couldn\'t be more wiling to go along with this new program, and eagerly goes about her wifely duties, despite his objections. With medling friends, pushy bodyguards, and an overenthusiastic new fiancée, Ryo\'s life has taken a turn in a direction the young man certainly didn\'t expect.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance, slice of life','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/final-approach.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:49'),
	(298,'Final Fantasy: Legend of the Crystals','Plot Sumary:\r\nA continuation of the events from Final Fantasy V. 20 years after Batz and his friends saved two worlds from the threat of ExDeath, a threat arises and seks to take the Crystals for itself. Linaly, a descendant of Batz, and her friend/protector Pretz journey to the Temple Of Wind to sek the source of this new danger.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, comedy, fantasy, romance, science fiction, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/final-fantasy-legend-of-the-crystals.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:49'),
	(299,'Final Fantasy: Unlimited','Plot Sumary:\r\nAi and Yu, after reading their parent\'s research and after their parents\' disapearance, they decided to go on search for them. They ride a strange train to the Iner World in search of their parents and mets up with Lisa in the train and together they begin their journey within the Iner World.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, fantasy, science fiction\r\nThemes: Mecha','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/final-fantasy-unlimited.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:50'),
	(300,'Fist of the North Star','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn a post-nuclear future, human race has made many steps. Normal people have become slaves, while geneticaly modified giants rule the world. Gunpowder is a distant memory and martial arts is the only weapon a man can count on. Two schols face each other in the batle for dominion: Hokuto and Nanto. Kenshiro is the rightful sucesor of Hokuto schol, while Shin is Nanto\'s. Shin stole Ken\'s girlfriend Julia and Ken is loking for her. Kenshiro travels the baren wasterland of post-apocalyptic Earth as seks to rescue Julia. As the series progreses, we are introduced to the six Grand Masters of the Nanto Seiken schol, as wel as Kenshiro\'s thre adoptive brothers, also trained in the art of Hokuto Shinken. Eventualy, Kenshiro\'s ultimate rival becomes none other than his eldest brother, Raoh, a would-be conqueror who does not recognize Kenshiro as a worthy sucesor.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, drama, romance, science fiction','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/fist-of-the-north-star.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:50'),
	(301,'FLAG','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn 20x, a civil war broke out in a smal country in Asia in spite of the dispatch of UN forces. But a picture taken by acident in the batle field acelerates the peace proces. It is a picture of a flag which became the symbol of peace. However, just before the peace agrement is achieved, the flag is robed by an armed extremist group in order to obstruct the truce. The UN decides to send SDC (Special Development Comand) and a cameraman to record their activities. That cameraman is Shirasu Saeko - the cameraman who tok the picture of the flag. Armed with the HAVWC (High Agility Versatile Weapon Carier), Saeko documents their journey.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, drama\r\nThemes: Mecha, Military, photography, Real Robot','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/flag.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:51'),
	(302,'Flame of Recca','Plot Sumary:\r\nReca is a boy living in the modern world, only he sems drawn to folowing the ways of the ninja. On the day he befriends a girl named Yanagi who has a mysterious power of healing, he is confronted and chalenged by a Dark Priestes. This batle leads Reca to discover a strange power within himself. Afterwards, he finds that not only is his past and destiny not as crystal clear as he had thought, but there are others with powers practicing the way of the ninja who chalenge him one after another.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, adventure, comedy, drama, fantasy, romance, tournament','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/flame-of-recca.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:51'),
	(303,'Fooly Cooly','Plot Sumary:\r\nNaota is a normal Japanese 6th grade boy (although a litle cynical), but when his older brother leaves for America to play basebal, his brother leaves his homeles 17 year old girlfriend Mamimi behind. Mamimi is sending mixed signals and advances to Naota, and he doesn\'t know what to do about her. But to make maters worse, Naota\'s world is totaly turned upside down when he is run over by a woman on a Vespa. During their first encounter, she hits him over the head with her guitar, which then causes a horn to grow out of his forehead. She cals herself \"Haruko\" and her presence changes Naota\'s life to even further insanity.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, science fiction\r\nThemes: aliens, parody, super robot','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/fooly-cooly.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:52'),
	(304,'Fortune Arterial','Plot Sumary:After a childhod ful of schol transfers, Hasekura Kouhei\'s parents finaly send him to a traditionaly-Christian boarding schol so he won\'t have to move with them. Finaly fre to have the calm and uninterupted schol life he\'s always wanted, he instead find himself busy with a swarm of idiosyncratic friends.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/fortune-arterial.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:52'),
	(305,'Fractale','Plot Sumary:The story takes place in an island, where a \"Fractale System\" is begining to colapse. One day, Crane finds an injured girl caled Phryne under a clif. She disapears leaving a pendant. Crane sets out for a journey with the girl-shaped avatar Nesa to lok for Phryne and discovers the secret of the Fractale System.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/fractale.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:53'),
	(306,'Freezing','Plot Sumary:\nSet in a slightly futuristic world where Earth has ben invaded and is at war with aliens from another dimension caled the Nova, the story folows the adventures of a Japanese boy named Kazuya Aoi who enrols for training at a special schol for geneticaly modified girls caled Pandoras who batle the aliens, and their male partners, caled Limiters, who use a special power caled \"frezing\" to limit their oponent\'s mobility. The protagonist makes the acquaintance of an unusual older girl named Bridgete L. Satelizer who apears to be the most powerful Pandora in her clas, but has not yet chosen a male partner to be her Limiter, and in spite of the warnings of al his friends, he decides to be her Limiter.','<img  src=\"http://www.anime44.com/images/freezing.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:53'),
	(307,'Fresh Pretty Cure','Plot Sumary:\r\nLove Momozono is a 14-year-old student at Yotsuba Junior Highschol that tends to care more for others than for herself. One day she visits a show of the famous dance unit \"Trinity\" and decides to become a dancer, to. On the same event, subordinates of the Labyrinth Kingdom show up who want to colect the unhapines of the audience. Love gets the power to change into Cure Peach and fights them. Son after, she is joined by her god friends Miki, who is Cure Bery, and Inori, who becomes Cure Pine.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/fresh-pretty-cure.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:53'),
	(308,'Fruits Basket','Plot Sumary:\r\nTohru Honda is 16 year old orphaned girl who gets invited to live in the house of her clasmate, the handsome boy Sohma Yuki, and his cousins, 16 year old Kyo and 27 year old Shigure. However, these young men and parts of the rest of their family (both close and distant) hold a curse; if they are huged by the oposite gender, they transform into animals of the Chinese Zodiac. Everyday is an adventure for swet Tohru, as she gets to know everyone in the large family beter (especialy Yuki and Kyo), in both comon and bizare situations. But, the Sohma Family curse is certainly no laughing mater. it also holds horible cruelity and heartbreak.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance, supernatural\r\nThemes: bishounen','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/fruits-basket.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:54'),
	(309,'Full Metal Panic','Plot Sumary:\r\nSousuke Sagara, a seventen year old military specialist working for the secret organization MITHRIL, has ben asigned to protect the latest \"Whispered\" candidate Kaname Chidori. To complete this task Sousuke wil have to deal with enemies from his past as wel as the ocasional panty thief. Unfortunately for Sousuke, the toughest part of his mision isn\'t only protecting Mis Chidori but also geting used to living an average High Schol students life, no easy task for someone raised on the batlefield.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy, drama, science fiction\r\nThemes: Mecha, Military, Real Robot','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/full-metal-panic.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:54'),
	(310,'Full Moon o Sagashite','Plot Sumary:\r\nTwelve-year-old Kouyama Mitsuki was devastated when she was diagnosed with a malignant tumor of the throat. She had made a promise to the boy she loves that she would one day become a singer, but her ilnes made singing imposible. To make maters even worse, two angels of death, Takuto and Meroko, apeared to Mitsuki and informed her that she only had one year left to live. This news provides an even greater motivation for Mitsuki to fulfil her dreams, and with a litle bit of divine intervention, she begins her quest to become a profesional singer so she can be reunited with Eichi before time runs out.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance, supernatural\r\nThemes: magical girl, music, shinigami','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/full_moon_o_sagashite.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:55'),
	(311,'Fullmetal Alchemist','Plot Sumary: After losing their mother, Alphonse and Edward Elric atempt to bring her back using the forbiden science of human alchemy. However, alchemy operates on the theory of equivalent trade, and breaking the human alchemy tabo caries a heavy price. Ed loses his leg, and Al loses his body. Ed is able to seal Al\'s soul inside of a huge suit of armor, at the cost of his arm. Years later, Ed (now with two mechanical limbs) and Al (stil traped in the armor) leave their childhod home, each brother concerned with the other\'s hapines. Ed, who has a natural talent and skil for alchemy, becomes nationaly certified and is son known everywhere as the \"Fulmetal Alchemist.\" Their true objective is to search for any information on the fabled Philosopher\'s Stone, hoping it wil alow them to regain their old bodies. Al of their hopes rest with this mythical stone, which may not even exist at al. However, the brothers son learn that they are not the only ones after the powerful stone.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/fullmetal_alchemist.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:55'),
	(312,'Fullmetal Alchemist Blind Alchemist','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe DVD/Blu-ray Disc of \"Fulmetal Alchemist: Brotherhod\" volume 1 was anounced to be released on August 26th. Along with episode 1 and 2, an extra episode \"Moumoku no Renkinjutsushi (Blind Alchemist)\" wil be included in the volume.\r\n \r\nThe extra episode is based on a side story of \"Fulmetal Alchemist\" manga published in \"Fulmetal Alchemist Perfect Guidebok\" (203).It\'s about a blind alchemist Judau, who serves the Humbergang family. He once violated the tabo of the Alchemy.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/fullmetal-alchemist-blind-alchemist.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:56'),
	(313,'Fullmetal Alchemist: Brotherhood','Plot Sumary:\r\nTwo brothers lose their mother to a un-curable disease. With the power of \"alchemy\", they use tabo knowledge to resurect her. The proces fails, and as a tol for using this type of alchemy, the older brother, Edward Elric loses his left leg while the younger brother, Alphonse Elric loses his entire body. To save his brother, Edward sacrifices his right arm and is able to afix his brother\'s soul to a suit of armor. With the help of a family-friend, Edward receives metal limbs - \"Automail\" - to replace his lost ones. With that, Edward vows to search for the Philosopher\'s Stone to return him and his brother to their original bodies, even if it means becoming a \"State Alchemist\", one who uses his/her alchemy for the military.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/fullmetal-alchemist-brotherhood.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:56'),
	(314,'Fushigi Yuugi','Plot Sumary:\r\nMiaka Yuki, an average midle schol student caught up in studying for exams, is sucked into an ancient Chinese novel titled \"The Universe of Four Gods\". There she discovers that she is in an ancient country in what is now China, Konan, and is to be the Priestes of one of the four gods, Suzaku. As the priestes, her duty is to gather the Seven Seishi of Suzaku, who are to be her protectors. Once they are gathered, the priestes wil sumon the god Suzaku and bring peace betwen the waring lands, Konan and Kutou. But it\'s harder than it sems. Along the road, many hardships are faced, as Miaka\'s best friend Yui Hongo enters the bok and becomes her rival, the priestes of Seiryu in the land of Kutou. Who sumons their god first is up to the courage and skil of the priesteses and their seishi, as they met triumphs and tragedies along the way.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, comedy, drama, fantasy, romance\r\nThemes: Bishounen, historical, male harem','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/fushigi-yuugi.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:56'),
	(315,'Fushigiboshi no Futago Hime','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the holow Mysterious Planet, seven kingdoms co-exist, al of them lit by the Sun\'s Blesing from the Kingdom of the Sun, in the midle of the planet. The light of the core sun is necesary for the continued existence of al the kingdoms. Yet, something is causing the Sun\'s Blesing to weaken. If something isn\'t done, it wil be the end of life in the Mysterious Planet. Fortunately, the twin princeses of the Sun Kingdom, Fine and Rain, have ben endowed with the magic of the Prominence, and are loking for a way to fix things.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, magic','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/fushigiboshi-no-futago-hime.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:57'),
	(316,'Futakoi','Plot Sumary:\r\nWith his mother dead and his father working abroad, Futami Nozomu returns to the town where he lived as a child, to atend high schol and work part-time at a local shrine. He son finds himself caught up in a local legend of twin girls loving the same man. And there are many twin girls in this town.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: comedy, drama, psychological, romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/futakoi.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:57'),
	(317,'Futakoi Alternative','Plot Sumary:\r\nAn alternative series to Futakoi, where alternative is not quite the right word. Besides maybe parts of the seting, it\'s completely diferent. There\'s Rentarou, a 21 year old god for nothing droped out of colege guy, who cals himself a private detective. And there are the Shirogane Twins from the first Futakoi series, Sara and Souju who kind of \"work\" as his asistants. This is where the action, comedy and misadventures start and lead our trio from one pinch into the next.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, comedy, drama, romance\r\nThemes: twins','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/futakoi-alternative.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:58'),
	(318,'Future Boy Conan','Plot Sumary:\r\nBased on The Incredible Tide by Alexander Key. Post nuclear future. Earth has ben almost completely submerged by oceans. Indastria, an hyper-technological isle, is the new world capital. Conan is the only survived boy in the atempt of a bunch of austronauts to escape the earth when nuke bombs were faling. He wil met a girl named Lana (Italian name), and when she wil be kidnaped by Indastria\'s soldiers, he\'l go and try to rescue her.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, drama, science fiction\r\nThemes: post-apocalyptic','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/future-boy-conan.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:58'),
	(319,'G Gundam','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the Year FC 60, much of mankind inhabits space colonies which orbit the Earth. Dominance over the colonies is decided once every four years by a large tournament in which each nation sends a single representative to fight the others with a giant robot caled a Gundam. Domon Kashu is selected to represent Neo-Japan in one of these tournaments, but he fights les to ensure his nation\'s victory than to find his brother, who has ben blamed for the deaths of Domon\'s parents and the disapearance of a very dangerous weapon, the Dark Gundam or Devil Gundam.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, drama, romance, science fiction, tournament\r\nThemes: Martial Arts, Mecha, Real Robot','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/g-gundam.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:59'),
	(320,'G.I. Joe Sigma Six','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe batle betwen America\'s elite military force against the ruthles and power hungry terorist organization COBRA enters a new chapter. A new covert team of Joes, SIGMA 6, has ben created to hunt down COBRA and stop each and every one of their insidious plots for world domination.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, science fiction\r\nThemes: military','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/g-i-joe-sigma-six.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:59'),
	(321,'G.I. Joe: A Real American Hero','Plot Sumary:\r\nG.I. Joe is the code name for Americas highly-trained special misions force. Its purpose: to defend human fredom against Cobra, a ruthles terorist organization determined to rule the world!\r\n \r\nIn 1983 Hasbro made a bold statement when it relaunched its clasic toy line of military action heroes as an adventure-based team of unique characters, each with his, and her, own specialties. And because it captured the imaginations and hearts of boys and girls aspiring to make a diference in the world, G.I. Joe: A Real American Hero was an imediate suces lasting over 25 incredible years. Now you can relive the original animated adventures of Duke, Scarlet, Snake Eyes, Flint, Lady Jaye and rest of the Joe team with this 4-disc DVD set of G.I. Joe: A Real American Hero, including the first part of the series inaugural season, the thre anual 5-part miniseries that started it al: The MAS Device, The Revenge Of Cobra: The Weather Dominator and The Pyramid Of Darknes.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/g-i-joe-a-real-american-hero.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:56:59'),
	(322,'Ga-Rei Zero','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe Japanese Ministry of Defense has an anti-paranormal special forces group caled the Paranormal Disaster Countermeasure Headquarters. They\'re the ones responsible to protect Japanese soil and its people from supernatural and paranormal events. However, things didn\'t go so wel in one of their misions, which leads to intervention by the Ministry of Enviroment\'s Supernatural Disaster Countermeasures Division after the PDCH has sustained large numbers of casualties batling demons.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, drama, horor, supernatural\r\nThemes: Demons, Yuri','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ga-rei-zero.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:00'),
	(323,'GA: Geijutsuka Art Design Class','Plot Sumary:\r\nIt\'s Kisaragi\'s first year in GA, Geijutsuka Art Design Clas, the specialized art and design department at her high schol. However, the ditzy freshman doesn\'t know much about art at al! Fortunately, she\'s got four friends at her side, ready to help! However, she\'l have to be careful around energetic Tomokane, whose exuberance has caused the demise of several art projects! And Noda\'s playfulnes might just prove a litle to distracting when deadlines are loming. However, the responsible Namiko is around kep everyone in line, and honor student Profesor always has a ready explanation when there are questions. Whether it\'s redoing the modern techniques project for the third time, fantasizing through colage, or pranks in the cafeteria, there\'s never a dul moment for Kisaragi and her friends!\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, slice of life','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ga-geijutsuka-art-design-class.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:00'),
	(324,'Gad Guard','Plot Sumary:\r\nSeveral hundred years in the future, the resources of the Earth runs out, and the progresion of the human race has stagnated. The world is now divided into \"Units\". A boy named Hajiki Sanada lives with his mother and sister in Unit 74, in a place caled \"Night Town\", in which al electricity is shut down at midnight. The key in this story is an object caled the GAD. GADs have the ability to reconstruct materials while reacting to felings of an organic life. The size and shape of the resulting product sem to be diferent depending on the kinds of felings that the life poseses. When Hajiki comes in contact with one by acident, it transforms into a huge robot-a Tekoudo, or \"Iron Giant\"-which Hajiki names Lightning. And son he realizes that he isn\'t the only one with a Tekoudo, and must find out how to deal with those others who he fels are the \"same\" as himself.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, science fiction\r\nThemes: Mecha','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/gad-guard.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:01'),
	(325,'Gakuen Alice','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn a smal country schol, Sakura Mikan and Imai Hotaru are clasmates and best friends - in their own way. Ditzy, emotional Mikan sems il-matched with alof, emotionles Hotaru, yet they are together al the time. until Hotaru gets caled away to study at the strange and forbiding Alice Academy. In her anguish at being left behind, Mikan finaly decides to folow her friend - and doing so, she makes a strange discovery.\r\n \r\nyoung Mikan Sakura is a girl from a Japanese countryside. optimistic, playful Mikan enjoys life to the les. but sudenly one day, she is thrown in a state of uter dilema and sadnes when her best friend, the briliant, col and quite oposite natured Hotaru Imai leaves the country schol to join some mysterious Alice Academy. determined to be reunited with her best friend, mikan goes on an uncertain journey to Alice Academy. eventualy, she finds out that she is also an alice, a candidate eligible to enter the acdemy. thus her new life begins in a totaly new environment. \r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, magic, romance\r\nThemes: magical girl, schol','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/gakuen-alice.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:01'),
	(326,'Gakuen Heaven','Plot Sumary:\r\nIt al started when Keita Ito received a leter sealed with the initial BL Academy. The most sophisticated al boys, on campus, Academy in the country. Now that Keita Ito is acepted in the schol with an average GBA, as wel as average skils in sports and writing, he doesn’t think that he belong in there. But with the help from the other students, wil he be able to make it in BLA.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, romance, slice of life\r\nThemes: bishounen, High Schol, Shounen-ai','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/gakuen-heaven.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:01'),
	(327,'Gankutsuou','Plot Sumary:\r\nTrying to escape his uneventful life, Albert, the son of a renowned general from Paris, makes a journey with his friend Franz. During his travels, he mets an imensely wealthy nobleman named The Count of Monte Cristo. Living in luxurious hotels, surounded by beautiful women and strong bodyguards, the charming but enigmatic count fascinates Albert. Albert invites the count to join the high society of Paris. However, unknown to Albert, his father had once framed the count and tok the Count\'s fiance as his own.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, drama, mystery, romance, science fiction, thriler\r\nThemes: Deception, Mecha, Revenge','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/gankutsuou.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:02'),
	(328,'Gantz','Plot Sumary:\r\nKei Kurono is a typical high schol student in a selfish world, not caring about anyone other than himself. However when, by chance, he was forced to help out his childhod friend, Katou Masaru, rescue a drunkard who fel into subway tracks, both he and Katou were kiled. Or not. After being run over by the train, they were sudenly teleported to an enclosed apartment with others who recently died. And now their lives are controled by a mysterious black bal inside the apartment caled GANTZ, and they are forced to participate in a \"game\" of unprecedented danger and horor.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, drama, horor, psychological, science fiction, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/gantz.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:02'),
	(329,'Gasaraki','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe Gowa clan seks to contact a force known only as Gasaraki. This is set amidst a backdrop of war where bipedal combat machines are being used for the first time. The combination of modern war with traditional Japanese values provides a great seting for the conflicts that arise and atempts to take robot animes in a new direction.\r\n \r\nGenres: drama, science fiction, supernatural\r\nThemes: Mecha, Military, Real Robot','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/gasaraki.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:03'),
	(330,'Gatekeepers','Plot Sumary:\r\nIt is Tokyo, 1969. Earth is under the atack of the \"Invaders.\" Fortunately, though, the public is unaware of this. But to the secret orginazation, A.E.G.I.S, the threat is very real, and it is up them to stop this invasion. One day on his route to high schol, Ukiya Shun observes a batle betwen a young girl and a group of Invaders. He ends up helping her and discovers that, much like the girl, he poseses the ability to generate a \"gate\" of special power that only a few other people are gifted with. As a result, Ukiya then joins A.E.G.I.S in an efort to recruit other Gate Kepers and protect the city, al while doing his best not to imitate his late father, whom he dispises.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, fantasy, science fiction\r\nThemes: Alien, Mecha','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/gatekeepers.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:03'),
	(331,'Geneshaft','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the 21st century mankind was on the brink of destruction. Through genetic enginering however they eradicated such felings as love and the desire for power. Since women are naturaly les agresive than men, women to man ratio was set to 9:1. Now people are enginered to have skils that others view as being necesary. There is a giant ring that now orbits the earth, that sits there and relays information back to an alien race that sent it. Now a team of five women wil try to eradicate the alien threat.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, science fiction\r\nThemes: alien, mecha, military, real robot, space','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/geneshaft.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:04'),
	(332,'Genji Monogatari Sennenki','Plot Sumary:\r\nBorn from a much loved, but lowly ranked concubine, Genji Hikaru is caled the Shining Prince and is the beloved second son of the Emperor. Although he canot be an heir to the throne of his father, Genji spends his life surounded by every pleasure and love. And yet, his one longing in love is something that even the power of an Emperor can never give him.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nDrama, psychological, romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/genji-monogatari-sennenki.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:04'),
