	(334,'Get Backers','Plot Sumary:\r\nBan Mido and Ginji Amano are a recovery duo infamously known as \"GetBackers.\" Ban poseses two special powers: the \"Snake Bite\" (his hands have a griping power of 20kg) and the \"Evil Eye\" (anyone who loks into his eyes wil be locked into a powerful and nightmarish halucination). Ginji, on the other hand, has the ability to generate thousands of volts of electricity from his body. Together, they run a frelance busines of recovering anything lost or stolen from a client - and they claim a 10% suces rate at their job.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, drama, mystery, supernatural\r\nThemes: friendship, martial arts, supernatural abilities','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/get-backers.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:05'),
