	(336,'Ghost Hunt','Plot Sumary:\r\nTeling ghost stories is a favorite past time of Mai Taniyama and her friends-that is, until she mets 17 year-old Kazuya Shibuya, the man sent by Shibuya Psychic Research Center to investigate paranormal activity at a suposedly haunted schol. When Mai gets caught in a dangerous situation, she is rescued by Kazuya\'s asistant. Saving her lands the asistant incapacitated, and Kazuya demands that Mai become his asistant, instead.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, horor, mystery, psychological, supernatural\r\nThemes: ghosts, vampires','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ghost-hunt.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:06'),
