	(346,'Ginga Nagareboshi Gin','Plot Sumary:\r\nA giant demon bear named Akakabuto has taken over Futago pas. Shortly after, a silver, tiger-striped Akita pup named Gin is born and is trained as a bear-dog. Gin is brought to Riki (the leader of a large pack of dogs and Gin\'s father) to join the pack. Riki let\'s him join after proving his strenght and sends his platons to al parts of Japan to recruit strong males to fight Akakabuto. \r\nGin, the third generation of bear-dogs goes through many hardships for the purpose of stoping the terifying bear, Akakabuto.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, adventure, drama','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ginga-nagareboshi-gin.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:28'),
	(347,'Gintama','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe Amanto, vicious aliens from outer space, has taken over the country of Japan. It has supresed al the samurais by prohibiting the usage of samurai swords. Sakata Gintoki is one of the few remaining samurai. Along with Shimura…\r\n \r\nGintama is a rare case that is rated G for everyone. Every single episode in the series has unique storyline and actions. The story folows Gintoki as he asists victims of the the Amanto’s invasion by fighting with the shinsengumi and the aliens. Hope you enjoy the show as most of our stafs did.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, adventure, comedy, drama, fantasy, science fiction, Historical, Parody','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/gintama.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:29'),
	(348,'Girls Bravo','Plot Sumary:\r\nSmal for his age, Yukinari has ben bulied and abused by girls al his life. Now in high schol, he has developed a rare condition: whenever girls touch him, or even come close, he breaks out in hives. Imagine his surprise, when he is sudenly transported to the city of Seiren on a mystic world invisibly orbiting the Earth, and populated with vast numbers of women and very few men. Fortunately, he has a new friend, Miharu-chan, whose touch inexplicably doesn\'t afect him.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy, drama, fantasy, romance\r\nThemes: echi, paralel universe','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/girls-bravo.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:29'),
	(349,'Glass Fleet','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe People\'s Army led by Michel stands against Veti\'s newly founded empire. Upon seing how strong the Glas Batleship is, Michel tries to get Cleo, the captain of the Glas Batleship, to help People\'s Army overthrow Veti\'s empire. And together they fight against Veti\'s empire.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, science fiction','<img  src=\"http://i50.tinypic.com/1zluemx.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:30'),
