	(352,'Gokinjo Monogatari','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe protagonist, Kouda Mikako, is a student of \"Yaza Gaku\". Specialising in fashion design, Mikako dreams of becoming a fashion designer with her own brand. Living next to her is her childhod friend, Yamaguchi Tsutomu. Even though they have ben close since young, they share a platonic friendship. However, Tsutomu has ben gaining popularity after he was recruited as the vocalist for a band and somehow, Mikako begins to se him in a diferent light. This is a story about how youths cope with dreams, love and friendship.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance, slice of life','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/gokinjo-monogatari.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:31'),
