	(354,'Gokujou!! Mecha Mote Iinchou','Plot Sumary:\r\nA kind girl is the wel-known chairman. Everything goes easily for her, except for one problem, and that\'s the clas troubled-boy trio that can\'t sem to folow the rules. Now she must handle this rebelious group who can\'t sem to stay out of trouble.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/gokujou-mecha-mote-iinchou.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:32'),
	(355,'Gokusen','Plot Sumary:\r\nKumiko \"Yankumi\" Yamaguchi enters Shirokin Gakuen Private Schol to become a math teacher. She\'s asigned as the homerom teacher for clas 2-4, populated by a gang of delinquents. At first, the clas tries everything to ratle her cage, but to no avail. In a short period of time, Yankumi gains the respect of the clas. But what the schol doesn\'t know is that she\'s the heir to the Oedo Group, a powerful Yakuza clan. So while Yankumi strugles to excel in her carer as a teacher, she must also kep her Yakuza background a secret.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: comedy, slice of life\r\nThemes: delinquents, Schol, Yakuza','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/gokusen.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:32'),
	(356,'Golden Boy','Plot Sumary:\r\nKintarou Oe doesn\'t lok like it, but he is a genius who completed al his university courses and then quit before graduating. He becomes a wandering student, going from place to place on his bicycle, seking to learn what he can about life, the world, and women. He is wiling and able to do any job he has to prove himself. His travels take him to a variety of locations and a variety of women, each who learns to love the hardworking guy, but not before he can run of.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/golden-boy.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:33'),
	(357,'Golgo 13','Plot Sumary:\r\nDuke Togo, or as he is more widely known, \"Golgo 13\", is a M16 bearing asasin who wil take on any job for the right price. Anyone can hire him, including private citizens and world governments. If he\'s not beding women he\'s infiltrating a hostile country, waiting hours for the perfect shot in the most extreme conditions. Golgo 13 is just as adept in the urban jungle. Those who deal with him must make sure not to cros the Duke or they might find themselves the target of his rifle.\r\n \r\nGenres: action\r\nThemes: Military, Police','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/golgo-13.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:33'),
	(358,'Goshuushou-sama Ninomiya-kun','Plot Sumary:\r\nShungo is a normal high schol student living in a huge house. One day, his sister Ryoko send two siblings, Mayu and Mikihiro Tsukimura, to live with him so as to help Mayu overcome her problem—androphobia, by making Mayu and Shungo share the same rom and bed, and to even take baths together. To make things even worse, Reika Hojo, the student-council chair, somehow ends up becoming their maid.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: comedy, romance, supernatural\r\nThemes: Echi, fanservice, Sucubus','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/goshuushou-sama-ninomiya-kun.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:34'),
	(359,'Gosick','Plot Sumary:GOSICK takes place in 1924 in a smal, made-up European country of Sauvile. The story centers on Kazuya Kujo, the third son of a Japanese Imperial soldier, who is a transfer student to St. Marguerite Academy, where urban legends and horor stories are al the rage. There he mets Victorique, a mysterious yet beautiful and briliant girl who never comes to clas and spends her days reading the entire content of the library or solving mysteries that even detectives can\'t solve.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/gosick.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:34'),
	(360,'Gravion','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe year is now 2041 AD. A new enemy caled Zeravire sudenly apears in the solar system, destroying al military instalations it comes acros. However, a wealthy man named Klein Sandman is already aware of this planed invasion and had ben secretly preparing his army for batle. His trump card is Gravion, a giant robot that utilizes gravity as its source of energy. Meanwhile a young man named Eiji secretly enters Sandman\'s base in search for his mising sister. It is there that he mets another young man by the name of Toga. These two must now fight together with four other individuals aboard the super robot, Gravion to fend of the Zeravire threat.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, science fiction\r\nThemes: Mecha, Sentai','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/gravion.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:34');
