VALUES
	(361,'Gravitation','Plot Sumary:\r\nShuichi Shindou wants to make a famous band. He works on his band, hoping to get a chance in the public eye, with nothing on his mind but his musical ambitions. One night as Shuichi writes song lyrics, his paper blows away, and a stranger picks it up. The man is Yuki, a famous romance novelist who tels Shuichi that his writing skils are grade schol level. From that moment on, Shuichi is determined to find Yuki and have him explain his rudenes. he just doesn\'t realize that he\'s experienced love at first sight. When Shuichi finaly finds Yuki, it\'s a journey of obstacles, frightening experiences and haunting pasts trying to kep them apart. But, it\'s just the gravitation of fate and love that always puls these lovers back together everytime.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance\r\nThemes: Music, Shounen-ai, Yaoi','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/gravitation.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:35'),
	(362,'Great Teacher Onizuka','Plot Sumary:\r\nOnizuka is an ex-biker and gang leader who has one goal, to become the greatest teacher. He learns of the power and respect posible as an intern teacher, using his strength and conections to get his students to respect him. Now, graduated, he gets a job at a prestigious private schol to handle their \'problem clas\' that made the past few teachers quit. He must handle a diferent sort of trouble when the trouble makers include some of the smartest kids in Japan who prefer a more cerebral aproach to torturing their teacher. Onizuka must slowly win his students over and deal with their mistrust of teachers while handling the distrust of his felow teachers.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, comedy, drama, slice of life','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/great-teacher-onizuka.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:40'),
	(363,'Green Green','Plot Sumary:\r\nKanenone Academy was an al-boys high schol isolated from the world by mountains and hils. Yusuke Takasaki, the average 1th grader, led a normal life in the academy until the academy anounced atempting for co-ed, and high-schol girls were being transfered for the sumer semester.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, comedy, romance, slice of life\r\nThemes: Echi, mild nude scene\'s, Schol','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/green-green.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:41'),
	(364,'Grenadier','Plot Sumary:\r\nRushuna is a blonde and very beautiful Senshi (gun expert) that travels through the world with one purpose. This is to make the world a peaceful place by instead of fighting with weapons, taking away the people´s wil to fight by giving them a smile. Although she doesn´t want to fight, she is forced to and shows amazing gun skils. In this journey she mets Yajiro, a Mercenary that uses a sword to fight and joins her on her journey.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy\r\nThemes: girls with guns','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/grenadier.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:41'),
	(365,'Guilty Crown','Plot Sumary:After the outbreak of the unidentified virus \"Lost Christmas\" in 2029, Japan has ben under the control of a multi-nation organization caled GHQ. Ohma Shu is a 17 year old boy who has a psychic power in his right hand. He can use the power \"Ability of King\" to extract tols or weapons from his friends. He has ben avoiding making trouble for others but his life changes when he mets a girl Yuzuriha Inori, a member of a resistance guerila group caled \"Undertaker\", whose members pilot mecha weapons to fight against the government.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/guilty-crown.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:42'),
	(366,'Guin Saga','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe ancient kingdom of Paro has ben invaded by the armies of Mongaul, and its king and quen have ben slain. But the \"twin pearls of Paro,\" the princes Rinda and the prince Remus, escape using a strange device hiden in the palace. Lost in the Forest of Rod, they are rescued from Mongaul soldiers by a strange leopard-headed man named Guin, who has no memories except for the word \"Aura.\"\r\n \r\nGenres: fantasy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/guin-saga.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:42'),
	(367,'Gun x Sword','Plot Sumary:\r\nArmed with a metal sash that straightens into a sword, lanky swordsman Van is traveling through the desert, searching for the mysterious clawed man who kiled his bride. Along the way he picks up a felow traveler: Wendy, a young girl whose town he saves from bandits by sumoning a mecha with his sword. Wendy is searching for her mising older brother, whose engraved gun she caries on her back. In their mutual quest they run afoul of more bandits and vilains, a mysterious woman named Carmen9, and more mecha batles a la Wild West.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, adventure, drama, science fiction, giant weapons, girls with guns, harem, Mecha, revenge, space western','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/gun-x-sword.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:42'),
	(368,'Gunbuster','Plot Sumary:\r\nGunbuster is the story of Noriko Takaya, a young girl who is trying to walk in the fotsteps of her famous father, Admiral Yuzo Takaya. It chronicles Noriko\'s trials and tribulations as she strugles to become a pilot of the masive robot Gunbuster. With the help of Coach Ota and her friends Kazumi and Jung, Noriko conquers her fears and learns one of the most important lesons in life: Believing in one\'s self.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, adventure, comedy, drama, science fiction, Mecha, Military, space navy, super robot','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/gunbuster.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:43'),
	(369,'Gundam 00','Plot Sumary:\r\nIt is the year A.D. 2307. Fosil fuels on Earth have ben depleted entirely, with mankind turning to the next available power source: solar energy. During this time, 3 orbital elevators with solar power generation systems are built, each under control by the Union of Solar Energy and Fre Nations (formerly United States of America), the Human Reform League (Rusia, China and India) and the Advanced European Union. However, not al countries are able to enjoy the benefits of this system, leading to widespread resentment and war. Arising out of the conflict, a mysterious military organization known as Celestial Being apears, dedicated to end al warfare using Mobile Suits caled Gundam. This begins the stories of Gundam Meisters (pilots) Setsuna F. Seiei, Lockon Stratos, Alelujah Haptism and Tiera Erde as they are thrown into conflict betwen the 3 superpowers and the various other factions.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, drama, science fiction\r\nThemes: Mecha, Military, Real Robot, War','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/mobile-suit-gundam-00.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:43'),
	(370,'Gundam AGE','Plot Sumary:In A.G. 101 (the 101st year of the Advanced Generation calendar) a mysterious entity known only as \"UE\", or \"unknown enemy\", atacks and destroys the space colony Angel. This brutal atack becomes infamous as the \"The Day the Angel Fel\", and marks the begining of humanity\'s war for survival. The series begins in A.G. 108 when the UE atack the space colony Ovan, where Flit Asuno lives with his mother. Flit\'s mother is kiled by the UE, and in her belongings (in an object caled a \"AGE Device\") he discovers the blueprints for a powerful weapon from the past-the ancient mesiah named \"Gundam.\"\nFrom these blueprints, Flit spends the next several years studying enginering at an Earth Federation base on the Nora space colony and designing the AGE-1 Gundam AGE-1 Normal. Seven years later, in A.G. 15, Flit completes the Gundam AGE-1 Normal, just as the UE atack Nora. Flit and his lineage\'s batle piloting the AGE-1 to protect mankind is about to begin.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/mobile-suit-gundam-age.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:44'),
	(371,'Gundam Seed','Plot Sumary:\r\nHeliopolis, a so-caled neutral space colony was holding a top-secret weapons research facility, producing Gundams for the Earth Aliance. ZAFT, which is composed of Cordinators (geneticaly modified/upgraded humans), atacks Heliopolis, stealing 4 out of the Aliance\'s 5 Gundams. In the batlefield, civilian Kira Yamato stumbles upon the Strike, the last remaining Gundam of the aliance, and is forced to pilot it. In the midst of batle he encounters his best friend, Athrun Zala, as one of the hijackers of the 5 Gundams, who sides with ZAFT. Being a Cordinator, he is the only one who can pilot the Gundam. But Kira is not with ZAFT, even though they\'re his own kind, nor the Aliance. Since the Aliance is the only place he could turn to at the time, he sides with them. He pilots the Gundam to protect his friends, and to fight his best friend, which pains both of them. It\'s a war betwen individual beliefs.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, drama, science fiction, Mecha, Military, Real Robot, Space, Space Navy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/gundam_seed.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:44'),
	(372,'Gundam Seed Destiny','Plot Sumary:\r\nCosmic Era 73. Though the signing of a peace treaty brought the war betwen the Naturals and Cordinators to an aparent close, tensions fueled by the continued threat of Blue Cosmos continue to run high. During a conference betwen PLANT chairman Gilbert Dulindal and Orb representative Cagali Yula Atha concerning the threat of a new military arms race, an Aliance special forces team atacks the ZAFT base they\'re meting at and makes of with thre new Gundam mobile suits. Forced to pursue them, Shin Asuka of ZAFT and Athrun Zala of Orb set out aboard the new space batleship Minerva, and engage the retreating Aliance strike team in combat. But just as they catch up to the fleing ship, the crew of the Minerva receives word of an even greater catastrophe in the making, which wil undoubtedly re-ignite the brutal war betwen the Naturals & Cordinators al over again.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, drama, science fiction, Mecha, Military','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/gundam-seed-destiny.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:45'),
	(373,'Gundam Unicorn','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe year is U.C. 096. Thre years have pased since the end of the Second Neo Zeon War. It is said that the Vist Foundation manipulates the Earth Federation and Anaheim Electronics from behind the scenes. Hoping to create a new world, the Foundation atempts to hand over a certain secret to the Neo Zeon remnants known as the Sleves. This wil mean the opening of Laplace\'s Box, which holds a great secret tied to the origins of the Universal Century. The exchange betwen the Vist Foundation and the Sleves is to take place at the manufacturing colony Industrial 7. This is the home of the student Banagher Links, who rescues a girl he ses faling through the colony\'s zero gravity area. The girl gives her name as Audrey Burne and says she wants to prevent a war, spuring Banagher to step into the conflict surounding Laplace\'s Box?almost as if he is drawn in by his own blodline.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/gundam-unicorn.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:45'),
	(374,'Gundam Wing','Plot Sumary:\r\nIt is the year After Colony 195, and war betwen the Space Colonies and Earth has begun. To give the colonies an edge, they send 5 young soldiers, trained to perfection, to earth in the most powerful of Mobile Suits-Gundams. With their arival, the tide of the war changes as they batle against the Earth forces and the Colonies of their origin.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, drama, science fiction\r\nThemes: Mecha, Military, Real Robot, Space, War','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/gundam-wing.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:45'),
	(375,'Gundam X','Plot Sumary:\r\nWhen one space colony declared its independence from United Nations Earth, the devastating 7th Space War, an al-out war betwen Earth and space, resulted. The UNE responded to the Space Revolutionary Army with mobile suits, caled Gundams. However, the SRA forces played their trump card and droped hundreds of space colonies onto the Earth, plunging the planet into a seven-year-long nuclear winter. The UNE colapsed, but the SRA was unable to invade the Earth in the aftermath of the colony drop. Fiften years have pased. The year is now After War 015, and a New UNE has sprung up on Earth to restore order. In space, the colonial leaders have ben rebuilding their own forces as wel. By chance, fiften-year-old Garod Ran has discovered an old UNE mobile suit, the Gundam X, and now he uses it to help out the Vulture ship Freden in its strugle to kep the powers that be from repeating the mistakes of the past.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, drama, romance, science fiction\r\nThemes: Mecha, Real Robot','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/after-war-gundam-x.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:46'),
	(376,'Gundam ZZ','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe year is Universal Century 08. Directly after the end of the Gryps War, Haman Karn and her army of Zeon remnants on the asteroid Axis begin their quest of reviving the lost empire of the Zabi\'s, and proclaim themselves as the Neo-Zeon. With the Earth Federation as haples as ever, only the Anti-Earth Union Group (AEUG) is able opose the plans of Neo-Zeon. In ned of al the help it can get after being decimated in the previous war and losing many of its key members, the AEUG ship Argama enlists the aid of a young junk colector from the Side 1 colony of Shangri-La named Judau Ashta to pilot its newest mobile suit, the Double Zeta Gundam.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy, drama, science fiction\r\nThemes: Mecha, Military, Real Robot','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/mobile-suit-gundam-zz.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:46'),
	(377,'GunGrave','Plot Sumary:\r\nBrandon Heat, a silent and pasive man, is living a laid back life with his friends. He\'s got his eyes on Maria, but her uncle forbids their relationship. After the brutal murder of his friends and Maria\'s father, Brandon is on the run together with the only friend he has left; Hary McDowel. When he finds out custody over Maria has ben taken by Milenion, the largest mafia syndicate in town, he and Hary decide to join the syndicate. He goes through many hardships after joining the syndicate but he is wiling to risk everything as long as he can be close to Maria.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, drama, science fiction, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/gungrave.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:47'),
	(378,'Gunslinger Girl','Plot Sumary:\r\n\"Henrieta\" was an inocent litle girl when her entire family was masacred and she was left for dead. She was rescued by a privately-owned social welfare organization and given cybernetic components over her batered body. Brainwashed by the organization, she and four other girls now work as cold-bloded asasins, doing the dirty work for the Italian government.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, drama, science fiction\r\nThemes: girls with guns','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/gunslinger-girl.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:47'),
	(379,'Gunsmith Cats OVA','Plot Sumary:\r\nRaly Vincent knows her weapons wel, while her partner Mine May Hopkins loves to play with explosives. The pair run a gun-shop ilegaly and one day Bil Colins of the ATF, blackmails Raly and Minie May into working for the ATF. Litle do they know, that they are geting involved in a mision larger than they could imagine.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy\r\nThemes: bounty hunters, girls with guns, police','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/gunsmith-cats-ova.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:48'),
	(380,'Guyver: The Bioboosted Armor','Plot Sumary:\r\nSho Fukamachi, a normal tenager acidentaly found an alien object caled Unit and thus, changed his life forever. The Unit bonded with Sho, resulting a powerful fighting lifeform caled Guyver. With this great power, Sho batled the mysterious Chronos and it\'s Zoanoids, in order to protect his friends and his world. Unknown to Sho, the batle against Chronos wil lead to the discovery of the origins of human, their destiny, and the Creators.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, adventure, science fiction','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/guyver-the-bioboosted-armor.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:48'),
	(381,'H2 TV','Plot Sumary:\r\nHiro has two loves: basebal and porn, but due to an elbow injury, gives up basebal, chosing a schol with no basebal team. His childhod friend Hikari atends a diferent schol with basebal ace Hideo. The two of them wish that Hiro had not given up basebal. Hiro joins the socer team and mets Haruka, a very clumsy girl who is also the daughter of his father\'s bos. Haruka is the manager of the unoficial basebal club at Hiro\'s schol. When the socer team chalenges the basebal club to a game, with hopes of humiliating them, the basebal club nearly loses until Hiro, disgusted by the socer team\'s arogance, switches to the basebal club.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, romance, tournament\r\nThemes: basebal, Sports','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/h2.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:49'),
	(382,'H2O: Footprints in the Sand','Plot Sumary:\r\nTakuma Hirose, a blind young male high schol student, though the cause for his blindnes is undetermined. After his mother died an unexpected death, it left a dep emotional scar on him, which caused him to become very lonely and reserved. Due to this, Takuma move from the city out into a rural area and Takuma is enroled into a new high schol. At his new schol, he mets several new girls, though thre of whom he gets to know the most out of anyone else. They are, the firm and obstinate Hayami Kohinata, the kind and obliging Hinata Kagura, and the cherful and mysterious Otoha. As Takuma interacts with these girls, his medical condition gradualy begins to heal.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy, drama, psychological, romance, slice of life, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/h2o-footprints-in-the-sand.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:49'),
	(383,'Haibane Renmei','Plot Sumary:\r\nA dream of faling from the sky.and then birth. Raka is born from a large cocon into the Old Home, greted by a group of females with smal wings on their backs and shining halos above their heads. Son Raka’s own wings grow, a halo is placed on her head and she is told that she must work in the nearby town of Grie. She son realizes that the town and the entire world they live in are confined behind the Wal, a tal, impenetrable wal that none except the mysterious Toga are alowed to exit.\r\n \r\nRaka, a newly born Haibane (Angel) awakens into an unfamiliar world with only a strange dream of faling from the sky as her only memory. Alone and scared of who and what she is, she is cared for by felow Haibane as they try and search for the meaning of their existence as wel as what lies beyond their town\'s imprisoning wals.\r\n \r\nGenre:','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/haibane-renmei.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:57:49'),
	(384,'Hajime no Ippo','Plot Sumary:\r\nIpo, a timid highscholer, is one day saved from being beaten up by Takamura, a boxer. Enthraled by Takamura\'s skils Ipo begins to learn boxing, son finding love for the sport and a drive to chalenge the boxing world.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy, drama, tournament','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hajime-no-ippo.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:01'),
	(385,'Hakaba Kitarou','Plot Sumary:\r\nKitarou is a youkai boy born in a cemetery, and aside from his mostly-decayed father, the last living member of the Ghost tribe. He is mising his left eye, but his hair usualy covers the empty socket. He fights for peace betwen humans and youkai, which generaly involves protecting the former from the wiles of the later.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: horor, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hakaba-kitarou.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:01'),
	(386,'Hakuouki: Shinsengumi Kitan','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe protagonist, Yukimura Chizuru is the daughter of a doctor who works in Edo. The father leaves Edo to work as a volunter doctor and moves to Kyoto without his daughter. As time pases by, Chizuru starts worying about losing contact with her father, so she decides to go to Kyoto in search of him. On the way, Chizuru is atacked by few criminals and witneses a fight betwen an oni and the Shinsengumi. Taking her into custody and saving her, the Shinsengumi debate on what to do with Chizuru when they discover that she is the daughter of the doctor they are also loking for. So they decide to become Chizuru’s protectors and help her lok for her father. Lots of events hapen while she stays with the Shingensumi, as they discover mysterious secrets and also fight against the Bakumatsu group.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hakuouki-shinsengumi-kitan.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:02'),
	(387,'Hakushaku to Yousei','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe story is set in 19th century England and centers on a \"fairy doctor\" named Lydia. Her life takes a 180-degres turn when she mets a legendary blue knight count named Edgar and his crew. He hires her as an adviser during his quest to obtain a treasured sword that was suposed to be handed down to him by his family.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, magic, romance\r\nThemes: Historical','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hakushaku-to-yousei.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:02'),
	(388,'Halo: Legends','Plot Sumary:\r\nThis particular segment from Halo Legends apears to focus on the relationship betwen a squad of elite Orbital Drop Shock Tropers and the even more elite Spartan soldier that\'s paired up with them. Once the action picks up - contrary to what you probably expect from the Halo franchise at this point - there isn\'t realy a lot of gunplay; in fact, there are way more punches thrown than bulets fired. Sure, the games are al about shoting at brightly-colored aliens, but what Halo fan wouldn\'t want to se a Spartan take on a towering Brute in hand-to-hand combat?','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/halo-legends.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:02'),
	(389,'Hana Yori Dango','Plot Sumary:\r\nMakino Tsukushi: a girl who comes from a por family just wants to get through her 2 last years at Eitoku Gakuen, quietly. But once she makes herself known by standing up for her friend to the F4, the 4 most popular, powerful and rich boys at the schol. She gets the red card: F4\'s way of a \"Declaration of War\". But when she doesnt let herself be beaten by them and is starting to fal for one of the F4; Hanazawa Rui. She starts to se that there is more than mets the eye.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance, slice of life\r\nThemes: Schol','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hana-yori-dango.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:03'),
	(390,'Hanamaru Kindergarten','Plot Sumary:\r\nAnzu goes to a preschol with her friends, the shy Koume and the ecentric Hiragi. Together they try to atract atention from their caretaker Tsuchida. However, he is clearly more interested in the prety Yamamoto who supervises the clas next dor.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hanamaru-kindergarten.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:04'),
	(391,'Hanasakeru Seishounen','Plot Sumary:\r\nKajika Burnsworth is talked into a \"Mariage Game\" by her father, the mighty bos of the Burnsworth Company. She wil met thre men he has chosen and decide which one to mary. If she does, he wil tel her what her true destiny is.\r\n \r\nGenres: drama, romance\r\nThemes: bishounen, male harem, politics','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hanasakeru-seishounen.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:04'),
	(392,'Hanasaku Iroha','Plot Sumary:Ohana Matsumae is sent to live with her grandmother, who she has never met nor spoken to, at her Taisho-era (1920s) hot springs in. It\'s not a lifestyle that Ohana would have chosen, but she decidesnot to be discouraged and to make the most of her new circumstances.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hanasaku-iroha.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:05'),
	(393,'Hanaukyo Maid Team','Plot Sumary:\r\nAfter losing his mother, 12-year-old Taro journeys to Tokyo to live with his grandfather. But he gets the bigest surprise when he discovers that his grandfather\'s home is a huge mansion with hundreds of beautiful maids ready to serve him. Making maters worse (at least for Taro, but not for our viewing) is that not only does he inherit the Hanaukyo mansion, he gets the services of al of the maids 24 hours a day, 7 days a wek.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, romance\r\nThemes: Maids','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hanaukyo-maid-team.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:05'),
	(394,'Hanbun no Tsuki ga Noboru Sora','Plot Sumary:\r\nDuring the winter, Yuichi was hospitalized due to hepatitis. Randomly he would try to escape from the hospital but would get beat up by the nurse. One day, he hapened to met Rika, a girl of his age, in the next building. He was fascinated by her beauty, but she was very selfish girl. Although she led him by the nose, he began to be atracted by her. However, when Rika told him about her ilnes, he knew why she acted so selfish; she didn\'t have long to live.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance\r\nThemes: Tragedy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hanbun-no-tsuki-ga-noboru-sora.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:05'),
	(395,'Hand Maid May','Plot Sumary:\r\nSaotome Kazuya is a computer whiz. One day his friend Nanbara, threatens him with a computer virus. Trying to stop the virus, Kazuya ends up making a special order. May is a cyberdol that arives at his dor a few minutes later and she is 1/6th the size of a normal person, which makes for many awkward situations. Not to mention the fact Kazuya can\'t even aford to kep May. Cyberdyne is not satisfied with Kazuya\'s non-payments and wil do anything to retrieve CBD May.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, comedy, romance, science fiction\r\nThemes: Maids, Robot Girl','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hand-maid-may.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:25'),
	(396,'Hani Hani: Operation Sanctuary','Plot Sumary:\r\nNaoki Kuzumi, a junior in high schol, had lost his parents in an acident five years ago, and is living with his aunt, uncle, and cousin Matsuri. He always thought his life was ordinary, besides the fact that he can\'t remember what hapened in his youth. One suny day as he is taking a nap on a bench, a redheaded girl - Mikoto - literaly fals on him from the sky. For some reason, she thinks he\'s her younger brother. Naoki\'s time period is a temporal shelter for those in the future, when many are sufering from an incurable disease. When she heard her younger brother Yusuke had ben taken to Naoki\'s time, Mikoto herself had gone back in time.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance, science fiction','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hani-hani-operation-sanctuary.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:26'),
	(397,'Happiness!','Plot Sumary:\r\nKamizaka Haruhi having ben rescued when was young by a mage, longed to be a mage herself, so she enroled into a special schol that alows regular and magic clases into two diferent sections. Together with her rival/best friend, Hiragi Anri, they study together magic while she is searching for the boy that saved her years ago, to give him a Valentines\' chocolate.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, magic, romance\r\nThemes: crosdresing','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/happiness.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:26'),
	(398,'Happy Lesson','Plot Sumary:\r\nHitotose Chitose was always alone and untrusting of people but when 5 female teachers apear and started living together with him in his family\'s house as his mothers, things started to change and pick up, together with Hazuki-ne and Minazuki (his 2 sisters) everyday is a leson\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/happy-lesson.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:27'),
	(399,'Happy Seven','Plot Sumary:\r\nAmano Sakogami is a girl who has an unatural amount of bad luck. One day, she stumbles into the clubrom of the Beter Fortune Research Organization, which consists of a boy and seven other girls who secretly use the power of the luck deities to fight against the Magatsugami, monsters who can afect a person\'s luck & wel-being. Amano son becomes the club\'s manager, and joins the club in their fight against the Magatsugami and their controler, Kukitomoe.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, comedy, drama, fantasy, romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/happy-seven.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:27'),
	(400,'Happy World!','Plot Sumary:\r\nSOomura Takeshi is one unlucky felow. He has has this case of bad luck ever since he was litle. One day, while on his normal runs with bad luck, he mets an Angel named Ele, and he finds out that his father wished the curse of bad luck upon him. Takeshi has the opurtunity to pas on the curse, but acepts it to save a young girl. For his noble act, Ele becomes human and lives with Takeshi to protect him from the curse, which is something Takeshi isn\'t particularly hapy with.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: comedy, fantasy, romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/happy-world.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:28'),
	(401,'Hare + Guu','Plot Sumary:\r\nHale was a hapy boy living out his days in the jungle with his mother, but then one day Gu showed up and became a member of their household. Throughout the series he faces many hardships as he tries to kep Gu out of trouble in the jungle.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: comedy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hare-guu.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:28'),
	(402,'Hatenkou Yuugi','Plot Sumary:\r\nA young girl named Rahzel is boted out of her house one day by her father with the instructions to ’se the world.’ And so her journey begins, However, she won’t be doing it alone … for she befriends a stoic young man named Alzeido seking revenge for his father’s murder. Alzeido and Rahzel are like oil and water … but even stil, they fel strangely drawn to one another. This could be either the result of an underlying atraction — or their shared powers with magic. And so, the two reluctant alies travel from town to town, using their powers to help the helples, while discovering their own respective places in the world.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, comedy, drama, fantasy, mystery, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hatenkou-yuugi.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:29'),
	(403,'Hatsukoi Limited','Plot Sumary:\r\nA series of short stories depicting the complicated love lives of eight midle schol and high schol girls, their clasmates and relatives. These stories later intertwine to form a main story involving most of the cast.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, romance, slice of life\r\nThemes: Echi','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hatsukoi-limited.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:29'),
	(404,'Hayate No Gotoku','Plot Sumary:\r\nAbandoned by his parents and given a monumentaly large debt as a Christmas present, 16-year old Ayasaki Hayate is at the lowest point of his life. Desperately trying alter his haples fate, he decides to kidnap someone to hold for a ransom. Due to an il choice of words, the girl he tries to kidnap misunderstands the action as a confesion of love. His plan is totaly crushed when he gives his real name out. Realizing his wrongdoing, Hayate proceds to rescue the girl from the yakuza, who had instead kidnaped her. The girl, as a token of thanks, ofers Hayate a job as her butler. Hayate, overwhelmed by her kindnes, vows to protect her even at the cost of his life.\r\n \r\n16-year-old Hayate is realy down on his luck. His unemployed parents are god-for-nothings who waste the money they have on gambling. One day, his parents have racked up a huge gambling debt that they had to sel Hayate to the yakuza for the value of his organs. In a desperate atempt to avoid that fate, Hayate decides to become a “bad guy” and kidnap someone to be held for ransom, but his eforts to do so are mistaken as a confesion of love by the girl he targets.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy, romance, slice of life\r\nThemes: harem, Parody','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hayate-no-gotoku.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:29'),
	(405,'He is My Master','Plot Sumary:\r\nYoshitaka Nakabayashi, a 14-year-old milionaire who got this huge inheritance after his parents died in an acident, found himself neded to be taken care of and tried to hire live-in maids to do the job. Two runaway girls, Izumi Sawatari and her younger sister Mitsuki, stumped into Nakabayashi\'s mansion and got hired by Yoshitaka imediately, for Yoshitaka is not only a rich boy but also a pervert with uniform fetishes, who wants to be adresed as goshujin-sama (master). Having nowhere else to setle down along with Mitsuki\'s pet aligator Pochi, Izumi acepted the job reluctantly.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy, romance\r\nThemes: maids','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/he-is-my-master.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:30'),
	(406,'Heartcatch Precure!','Plot Sumary:\r\nTsubomi Hanasaki is a 2nd year midle schol student who loves flowers and plants. One day, she dreams of a mysterious flowering tre that wilted, causing the sprites to disapear. When she transfers to Myodou Academy[note 1], the sprites that she saw in that dream apeared before her. The sprites beged Tsubomi to become Prety Cure to protect the Great Tre, but she refuses. However, a suden atack from a mysterious enemy came, and the Heart Sed of her new clasmate, Erika Kurumi, is stolen. To save Erika\'s heart, she had no choice but to become a Prety Cure and fight.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/heartcatch-precure.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:30'),
	(407,'Heat Guy J','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the city of Judoh, Claire Leoneli has inherited leadership of the Mafia group \"Vampire\" folowing the death of his father. To kep Claire\'s and other criminal activities in check, the city\'s Bureau of Urban Safety has Special Services Division operative Daisuke Aurora and the super android codenamed \"J\" (whose identity is aparently kept in secrecy, as androids are baned in the city). With both of them around, crime now has litle rom to breathe in Judoh.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, science fiction\r\nThemes: Police','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/heat-guy-j.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:31'),
	(408,'Heaven and Earth','Plot Sumary:\r\nSouchirou Nagi and Bob Makihara are two delinquents who arive at Toudou Academy with the objective of ruling over the schol with their strength. But on their first day, they encountered the Jyukenbu, a martial arts group of the schol. Members of the group, Maya Natsume, her sister Aya, and Masataka Takayanagi easily overpowered Souchirou and Bob. And what\'s more, due to what was asumed to be their \"conections\" with the Jyukenbu, the two were atacked by members of the Enforcement Group, which overses the martial arts groups of the schol. Drawn into the personal conflicts betwen the Jyukenbu and the Enforcement Group, Souchirou and Bob have no choice but to join up with Maya Natsume\'s group and to hone their skils to become even stronger.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy, drama, supernatural\r\nThemes: Martial Arts, Schol','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/heaven-and-earth.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:31'),
	(409,'Heavy Gear','Plot Sumary:\r\nHeavy Gear begins on a distant, fictional planet caled Tera Nova around 4,0 Earth Standard Years from now (6132 AD). Tera Nova was once the crown jewel of the United Earth Government\'s colonies, however, an economic colapse forced the Teran government to abandon Tera Nova and al its other colonies centuries before the period depicted in the game seting, leaving Tera Nova in a dark age. Eventualy, City-States rose from the ashes and either through treaties or tyrany, united to form national unions caled Leagues. These Leagues would in turn aly (again either peacefuly or forcibly) to form the superpower blocs that dominated the temperate southern and northern hemispheres of the planet.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/heavy-gear.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:32'),
	(410,'Hell Teacher Nube','Plot Sumary:\r\nNube is a clumsy, easygoing, and very kind teacher, but he has a secret under his glove on the left hand. He has a monster hand, and he also has the ability to sense ghosts and evil spirits. So he protects his dear students from these evil spirits with his monster hand, proving to be very powerful.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy, horor, romance, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hell-teacher-nube.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:32'),
	(411,'Hellsing','Plot Sumary:\r\nHelsing folows the antiheroic vampire, Alucard, and a police girl-turned-vampire, Seras Victoria, two vampires employed by the vampire-extermination group of England, the Helsing Organization. Slowly but surely, through their active duty, they find a new bred of vampires begining to arise.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, Drama, Horor, Supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hellsing.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:32'),
	(412,'Hellsing Ultimate','Plot Sumary:\r\nVampires exist. It is the duty of Helsing, a secret organization sponsored by the British government, to hide that frightening fact and protect the blisfuly unaware populace. Along with its own personal army, Helsing has secret weapons. Alucard, an incredibly powerful vampire, has ben controled by Helsing for years. It is unclear how he fels about being a servant to the Helsing family, but he certainly enjoys his job as a vampire exterminator. Seras is a fledgling vampire and former police woman. Although reluctant to embrace her new self, she is a valued member of the organization. Integra Helsing, the curent leader, is usualy fuly capable of fulfiling her duty, but lately, vampire activity has ben on the rise. Unfortunately, the cause is more alarming than anything she could have imagined. A group long thought dead has ben ploting in secret since their aparent destruction over 50 years ago. Ploting to plunge England, and perhaps the entire world, into war.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, Drama, Horor, Supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hellsing-ultimate.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:33'),
	(413,'Hen Zemi','Plot Sumary:Nanako Matsutaka is an inocent university student who is participating in a sexual perversion seminar led by the deviant profesor Kenji Meshiya. She desperately tries to kep her morals as wel as her sanity while amidst the strange group of students in the study group.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/abnormal-physiology-seminar.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:33'),
	(414,'Hero Tales','Plot Sumary:\r\nSet in a time of chaos, seven heroes of the Stars, the Hokushintenkun, rise up to lead the people. Two of the seven, the Nitenshinson, the Hagun and the Tanrou, are never suposed to exist at the same time, but fate has decided otherwise. Taito, chosen as the Hagun, now must rise up to defeat the Tanrou, as the fate of the Stars destined it to be.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, fantasy\r\nThemes: Martial Arts','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hero-tales.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:34'),
	(415,'Heroic Age','Plot Sumary: Answering the cal of the \"Gold Race\", al the sentient races launch into space. The human race is the last to launch, and are thus known as the \"Iron Race\". Much time has pased since then, and humanity is threatened with extinction at the hands of the more dominant \"Silver Race\". In order to save her people, Princes Deianeira sets out on a journey to a galaxy far away, folowing the prophecies of the Gold Race handed down by the royal family. Then, she mets a boy named Age. Their encounter wil change the fate of the universe.\r\n	  	 Coment: This anime is one of the beter series I\'ve found in the action genre. The character design is great and their personalities are quite developed over the course of the series. The story is wonderful however the ending is quite open ended and can be interpreted in many diferent ways. Overal I\'d rate this series a 9/10.','<img src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/heroic-age.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"284\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:34'),
	(416,'Heroman','Plot Sumary:\r\nA colaboration betwen Studio Bones and Stan Le, the story centers on a boy named Joey who discovers a toy robot near the west coast of the United States. Joey has always wanted to become a hero. Unfortunately he’s just an orphan working part time to suport his grandma and himself. After he watches a toy comercial about a new robot action figure, Joey believes he’l gain strength if he obtains one. The only robot toy he can get his hands on is a broken one that was abandoned by a rich schol buly. Feling pity for the trashed action figure, Joey takes it home to repair it; litle did he know that once he repairs the toy, it’l make his hero dream become a reality.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/heroman.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:34'),
	(417,'Hetalia: Axis Powers','Plot Sumary:\r\nItaly, once home of the strongest empire in the world, has changed. This is the story of Italy, now a cowardly pasta-loving fol, and his friends (other personified countries of the world) as they live through strange moments in world history.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hetalia-axis-powers.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:35'),
	(418,'Hidamari Sketch','Plot Sumary:\r\nYuno has ben acepted to her dream schol: Yamabuki Arts High Schol. To atend the schol, Yuno moves and starts to live in a smal apartment building named the Hidamari Apartments located near the schol. Once there, she starts making new friends like her clasmate Miyako and the second year students, Hiro and Sae. Surounded by god friends, Yuno starts moving towards her dream of being an artist.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, slice of life\r\nThemes: Art','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hidamari-sketch.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:35'),
	(419,'Hidamari Sketch x Hoshimittsu','Plot Sumary:\r\nYuno has begun her new artist’s life in her new dream schol, Yamabuki High Schol. In front of the schol is an apartment complex caled Hidamari-so, where she moves in and mets clasmates, senior students, and other strange artists.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hidamari-sketch-x-hoshimittsu.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:36'),
	(420,'Hidan no Aria','Plot Sumary:The story takes place in Tokyo Butei High Schol, a special schol where armed detectives — \"Butei\" — are trained to use weapons. Kinji Toyama is a second-year-student who has a special ability, but he keps it a secret to maintain an ordinary, peaceful life. However, when he gets caught in a bombing on the way to schol, he encounters H. Aria Kanzaki, the most powerful S-Rank Butei student in Asault Studies.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/aria-the-scarlet-ammo.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:36'),
	(421,'Higepiyo','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe story of Higepiyo (literaly \"Mustache-Pep\") revolves around Hiyoko, a \"sureal\" bird that hapens to have a mustache. Hiyoko can talk with \"Piroshi\" — Hiroshi, the human boy who bought her at a night fair — and the two are tight friends. In fact, Hiyoko teaches Hiroshi how to win brawls in elementary schol, and she sometimes fights a bulying girl on Hiroshi\'s behalf. (Hiyoko is actualy an experimental test subject that escaped from a laboratory.)','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/higepiyo.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:37'),
	(422,'High School Girls','Plot Sumary:\r\nEriko, along with pals Yuma and Ayano, tests into an exclusive al-girls high schol. Her dream of atending a schol ful of beautiful, clean, and clasy role-model girls is son shatered, as the reality of an al-girl schol sets in. Rumor goes, with an absence boys in the schol, an atmosphere of laxnes sets in, slowly eroding the girls\' regard for culture and become a creature far scarier than boys.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/high-school-girls.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:37'),
	(423,'Highschool of the Dead','Plot Sumary:\r\nTakashi Komuro is a normal highschol boy, until an infection breaks out that turns people into zombie-like creatures. Along with his friends & the schol nurse, they fight their way out and continue their journey to find out what exactly has hapened to the world.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/highschool-of-the-dead.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:37'),
	(424,'Higurashi No Naku Koro Ni','Plot Sumary:\r\nAfter moving into the quiet town of Hinamizawa, Maebara Keichi spends his days blisfuly in schol often playing games with his local friends. However, apearances can be deceiving. One fateful day, Keichi stumbles upon news of a murder that had ocured in Hinamizawa. From this point on, horific events unfold in front of Keichi, as he son learns his close friends may not be al that they sem. Based on the amateur mystery game by 7th Expansion, the story is told in a series of diferent scenarios. \r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy, Mystery, Drama, Game, Horor, Psychological','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/higurashi-no-naku-koro-ni.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:38'),
	(425,'Hikaru No Go','Plot Sumary:\r\nHikaru Shindo is just a normal 12 year old boy, but one day he\'s rumaging through his Grandfather\'s things to se if he can find something to sel and puls out an old Go board. A ghostly aparation apears out of the board and tels Hikaru his sad story. His name is Sai Fujiwara, a man who was a Go instructor to the emperor of Japan a thousand years ago. However, because of bad sportsmanship of his oponent during a game, Sai was acused of cheating and banished from the city. With no livelihod or any other reason to live, Sai comited suicide by drowning himself. Now, he haunts a Go board, and wants to acomplish the perfect Go game, caled the \"Hand of God\" which he hopes to do through Hikaru. If Hikaru wil be able to do it or not (or even wants to) wil have to be sen.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, psychological, supernatural, tournament\r\nThemes: Games, Schol, Sports','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hikaru_no_go.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:38'),
	(426,'Hime Chen! Otogi Chikku Idol Lilpri','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe TV anime series Lilpri is adapted from Sega\'s trading card game Lilpri: Yubi Puru Hime Chen!, distributed via arcade game machines. The story centers on Ringo Yukimori, Reira Takashiro and Natsuki Sasahara - thre elementary schol girls who can change into idol princeses.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hime-chen-otogi-chikku-idol-lilpri.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:39'),
	(427,'Himitsu: The Revelation','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe story takes place five decades from now, when brain scaners have ben perfected to the point that the government can retrieve up to five years\' worth of memories from people\'s minds — even if they are dead. The investigators of the National Research Institute of Police Science\'s 9th Forensics Laboratory must weigh the ethical choices in the ultimate invasion of privacy as they delve into people\'s minds to solve crimes.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: mystery, psychological, science fiction','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/himitsu-the-revelation.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:39'),
