	(435,'House of Five Leaves','Plot Sumary:\r\nMasterles samurai Akitsu Masanosuke is a skiled and loyal swordsman, but his naïve, difident nature has time and again caused him to be let go by the lords who have employed him. Hungry and desperate, he becomes a bodyguard for Yaichi, the charismatic leader of a gang caled “Five Leaves.” Although disturbed by the gang’s sinister activities, Masa begins to suspect that Yaichi’s motivations are not what they sem. And despite his misgivings, the deper he’s drawn into the world of the Five Leaves, the more he finds himself fascinated by these devious, mysterious outlaws.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/house-of-five-leaves.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:42'),
	(436,'Hungry Heart – Wild Striker','Plot Sumary:\r\nKyosuke Kano has lived under the shadow of his sucesful brother Seisuke al his life who is a profesional socer player. Tired of being compared and downgraded at, he abandoned playing socer until a boy from his new highschol discovered him and asked him to join their team. Kyosuke joins it and befriends two other first year players named Rodrigo and Sakai with the dream of becoming profesional socer players themselves.  \r\nKyusuke Kanou, a robust tenager of 16 sports orange hair and aspires to conquer the world of socer as a forward. But somehow the shadow of his renowned elder brother Seisuke, a midfielder for AC Milan fals upon his carer. Threatened by inferiority complex, he decides to give up socer. Yet, destiny reunites him with fotbal as he acidentaly becomes the coach of the women\'s socer team of his schol . Thus, his journey to fulfil his dream begins portraying his path of strugle. Backed by his helpful teamates and welwishers like Miki, the girl\'s socer team captain and Mori, the manager, he proceds forward in life.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: comedy, slice of life, tournament\r\nThemes: Socer','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hungry-heart-wild-striker.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:58:43'),
	(437,'Hunter X Hunter','Plot Sumary:\r\nGon Frecs, a young boy that lives on a smal island learns that his father who he doesn\'t remember is an extremely famous man and has become somewhat of an amazing hunter. Gon takes the hunter exam to sek out his amazing father, but on the way while teaming up with 3 other candidates, Kurapica, Leorio, and Kilua, he learns that there is more to becoming a hunter and the chalenges that he must face wil be beyond his imaginations.\r\n \r\nTwelve-year-old Gon Frecs one day discovers that the father he had always ben told was dead was alive and wel. His Father, Ging, is a Hunter-a member of society\'s elite with a license to go anywhere or do almost anything. Gon, determined to folow in his father\'s fotsteps, decides to take the Hunter Examination and eventualy find his father to prove himself as a Hunter in his own right. But on the way, he learns that there is more to becoming a Hunter than previously thought, and the chalenges that he must face are considered the toughest in the world.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, drama, fantasy, psychological\r\nThemes: Fighting, Manhunt, Revenge','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/hunter_x_hunter.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:59:13'),
