	(439,'Huntik: Secrets & Seekers','Plot Sumary:\r\nHuntik is an action and adventure show about a group of sekers traveling around the globe in search of ancient amulets that can invoke diferent types of monsters.\r\n \r\nLong before our times, humanity fought against an evil of unimaginable power. The darknes was broken only by the Sekers, humans able to invoke legendary creatures -the Titans -into their own plane of existence. With the Titans executing their every order, the first Sekers the Casterwils fought against the dark forces of the underworld and against themselves. Centuries went by, and one by one, the Titans were hiden: some were buried folowing grueling batles, others merely forgoten as time pased. The magical and powerful creatures lie hiden and dormant in the most remote part of the earth, waiting to be awakened by a new and bold group of Sekers.\r\n ','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/huntik-secrets-and-seekers.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:58','2012-03-07 01:59:14'),
