	(480,'Kagihime Monogatari – Eikyuu Alice Rondo','Plot Sumary:\r\nAruto Kirihara lives with his doting sister Kiraha in a stylized German town. He is in love with Lewis Carol\'s Alice in Wonderland stories, and writes his own fanfiction involving the characters. One day, a girl resembling a character from his story, Arisu Arisugawa, apears in real life. She introduces Aruto to a secret world where girls do batle to obtain each other\'s pages locked inside themselves. The one who obtains al the pages can compile the Eternal Alice and have their wish granted. \r\nLewis Carol wrote two volumes about the adventures of Alice in Wonderland, but there\'s a rumor of a mystical third volume. In order to compile the last bok, magical buny-girl wariors do batle with eachother, striping the defeated of pages locked inside them.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, drama, magic, romance\r\nThemes: fanservice, incest, Magical girl, yuri','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kagihime-monogatari-eikyuu-alice-rondo.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 01:59:31'),
