	(495,'Kamisama Dolls','Plot Sumary:Kyouhei, after moving away to Tokyo from his old town to get away from the events that hapened, is on a goukon with his friends, including his old neighbor, Shiba. After drinking for a whole night, he and Shiba discover a dead, blody, body in the elevator. He is told by his younger sister, Utao with her Kamisama Dol, that Aki, an old friend, and his Dol, are the culprits responsible.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kamisama-dolls.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 01:59:58'),
	(496,'Kamisama Kazoku','Plot Sumary:\r\nSamatarou is not just an average high-schol boy, the truth is that he is the son of a god, his mother is a godes and his sisters are candidates to become godeses. They are living in the human world, because they want their boy learn about the human customs and the habits of the creatures that they are protecting, so that in this way Samatarou wil become a beter god. Tenko is a angel asigned to lok after Samatarou. She\'s born the same day, same year as Samatarou and have ben close friends ever since. Life sems normal but things start to change with the apearance of a transfer student named Kumiko. Samatarou fals in love with her and from now on, things wil be a lot more diferent for him. His decision of making her fal in love with him without using his powers wil put him in trouble.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: comedy, drama, fantasy, romance\r\nThemes: Gods','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kamisama-kazoku.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 01:59:59'),
	(497,'Kampfer','Plot Sumary:\r\nSenou Natsuru is your normal, everyday high schol student. However he´s ben chosen to be a Kampfer, who´s objective consists on fighting other Kampfer with either guns, swords or magic, however, there´s catch; first you can´t chose if you´re a Kampfer or not, and second, you must have the body of a girl to use your powers.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy, romance\r\nThemes: ER> gender switch harem echi, gender switch harem echi','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kampfer.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 01:59:59'),
	(498,'Kanamemo','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe story centers on Kana Nakamichi, a midle-schol girl who had already lost her parents and just recently lost her only remaining relative, her grandmother. As a result, she ends up living and working at a newspaper delivery ofice. Everyone else living at the ofice are al charming, self-asertive bish?jo. The manga folows Kana’s daily life in the fast-paced yet joyous environment.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kanamemo.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 01:59:59'),
	(499,'Kannagi','Plot Sumary:\r\nAn art student named Jin Mikuriya carves a statue from the wod of the Kanagi tre only to have the statue come to life in the form of a godes, who has now taken over the statue. He and \"Nagi\" work together to destroy the impurities that are gathering in the town.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy, magic, romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kannagi.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:00'),
	(500,'Kannazuki no Miko','Plot Sumary:\r\nPlot Sumary: The highborn Himemiya Chikane is col and alof, the perfect young lady of god breding. Kurusegawa Himeko is devoted to her, and secretly her friend. Their lives are undisturbed in their schol, until an ancient evil sudenly rears its head. To combat it, Chikane and Himeko must take on the roles of shrine maidens of the Mon and Sun. \r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, drama, magic, psychological, romance, supernatural\r\nThemes: Mecha, yuri','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kannazuki-no-miko.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:00'),
	(501,'Kanokon','Plot Sumary:\r\nKanokon\'s story revolves around Kouta Oyamada, a young first-year high schol student who moves from the country to the city and thus transfers to Kunpo High Schol. On his first day at his new schol, a beautiful second-year female student named Chizuru Minamoto asks him to met her alone in the music rom. When he arives, she reveals that she is in fact a fox deity and from that day on the two hang out together. Nozomu is a first year female student at Kouta\'s schol, she is in fact a wolf deity and in love with Kouta, and a rival of Chizuru for Kouta\'s afections.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, romance, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kanokon.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:01'),
	(502,'Kanokon Manatsu no Daishanikusai','Plot Sumary:\r\n Kanokon\'s story revolves around Kouta Okayama, a young first-year high schol student who moves from the country to the city and thus transfers to Kunpo High Schol. On his first day at his new schol, a beautiful second-year female student named Chizuru Minamoto asks him to met her alone in the music rom. When he arives, she reveals that she is in fact a fox deity and from that day on the two hang out together. Nozomu is a first year female student at Kouta\'s schol, she is in fact a wolf deity and in love with Kouta, and a rival of Chizuru for Kouta\'s afections.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, romance, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kanokon-manatsu-no-daishanikusai.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:01'),
	(503,'Kanon 2002','Plot Sumary:\r\nChanging schols is something Yuchi is acustomed to, due to his parent’s profesion, and with their recent venture to Africa, he is returning to his aunt’s home after 7 years. The time that has pased since his last visit has faded his memories of the people he knew, and the ties that bonded them to him, including his cousin Nayuki. Slowly those people, coincidently al being girls, find their way back to him. However, time has pased and things have hapened in their own lives that sets the tone for the series. Secrets that are coming to surface, and memories that are returning to not only Yuichi, but to those surounding him.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kanon-2002.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:01'),
	(504,'Kanon 2006','Plot Sumary:\r\nYuichi Aizawa returns to this city after seven years. In his childhod, he often visited it, but something hapend in the past which caused him to block out his memories of the events of seven years ago. On the day after he gets setled in, he mets a girl carying a backpack with wings on it. Her name is Tsukimiya Ayu and he begins to recal the memories he had lost.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, psychological, romance, supernatural\r\nThemes: moe','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kanon-2006.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:02'),
	(505,'Karas (OVA)','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe old Karas is dead, kiled by an evil ex-Karas who now named himself Ekou. He started a series of murders against humanity by making his loyal youkai drain the body fluids from humans. Otoha ,a young man who just woke from a coma, is chosen to be the new Karas. Him and his trainer, Yurine, start the fight against the evil forces of darknes that are triyng to conquer the city of Shijuku.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, fantasy, science fiction','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/karas-ova.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:02'),
	(506,'Kare Kano','Plot Sumary:\r\nYukino Miyazawa is realy, realy vain, and loves to hear people praise her. She\'s always ben the best at everything, and always tries to lok perfect. But when Yukino goes to high schol, she\'s finaly upstaged-by Souichiro Arima, who scores beter on the entrance exams and instantly snatches the atention of the clas. By acident, Arima finds out that Yukino is just pretending, and this starts of a series of events that lead to Yukino and Arima faling in love. They then have to cope with a lot of obstacles in their relationship.\r\n \r\nYukino Miyazawa, the Quen of Vanity, is the \'perfect student\' - smart, prety, athletic and has an overal nice personality. What everyone in her schol didn\'t know was that behind the perfect facade lies a diferent person. She is always the best in anything - but an obstacle comes her way. The obstacle\'s name is Souichirou Arima. Souichirou Arima is chosen as the representative of the freshmen, not Miyazawa. Thus, she strives hard to defeat him in al aspects. But a day comes when her most-hated enemy comes to find out her secret. From treating Arima as an enemy, friendship blosoms. Son love comes. Kare Kano is a story that revolves al around the pangs and beauty of first love\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy, drama, romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kare-kano.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:03'),
	(507,'Karin','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the 21st century, a family of vampires setled down on the grounds of Japan and lived a modest life whilst sucking on the blod of humans discretly. However, the eldest daughter of the family, Karin Maka, has an embarasing secret which canot be revealed to anyone. Even though she is a vampire, she does not lack blod like her family members. Instead, she overproduces blod to the extent that she transfuses the exces into her victims, hence increasing their blod levels. Despite her troubling body characteristic, she atends schol like any other high schol student, that is until a new transfer student, Kenta Usui, enters her life.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: comedy, horor, psychological, romance, supernatural\r\nThemes: Parody, Vampire','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/karin.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:03'),
	(508,'Kasimasi – Girl Meets Girl','Plot Sumary:\r\nHazumu was a shy boy who enjoyed gardening, colecting herbs, and long walks in the mountains. One day he finaly worked up the courage to confes his love to Yasuna, but she rejected him. Feling dejected, he wandered up Mt. Kashimayama to the place where they first met to reconsider his felings. After geting lost, he wished upon a shoting star which turned out to actualy be a crashing alien spaceship. Although he was hit by the faling ship, Hazumu survived the crash thanks to some body reconstruction by the aliens, only they got it a litle wrong. Now that he is a she, Hazumu stumbles head-first back into his social life and relationships only to find that the entire landscape has changed.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance, science fiction\r\nThemes: aliens, gender switch, love triangle, yuri','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kasimasi-girl-meets-girl.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:31'),
	(509,'Katanagatari','Plot Sumary:\r\nThis story teakes place in the Edo era where Yasuri Shichika is the seventh head of the Kyotou schol of Japanese sword martial arts living in Fushou Island with his sister Nanami. With the order from a female samurai general Togame, he sets out for a trip to colect the twelve treasured swords created by a legendary swordsmith Shikizaki Kiki.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/katanagatari.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:31'),
	(510,'Katekyo Hitman Reborn','Plot Sumary:\r\nTsuna is a haples youth with low test scores and lower self estem. His mother hires a tutor to help Tsuna out, but it comes as a surprise to the both of them when the tutor is a baby named Reborn, claiming to be from the Mafia. Reborn informs Tsuna that he\'s the next heir to the Vongola family mafia family and tries to help Tsuna reach the goal. Reborn poseses the Dying Wil bulet, which kils a person and brings them back to life to fulfil the last regret they had, and even works to get Tsuna some henchmen to make him a true mafia bos-in-training.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, comedy, supernatural, Mafia','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kateikyoushi_hitman_reborn.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:32'),
	(511,'Kaze no Stigma','Plot Sumary:\r\nAyano is the heir to the house of Kanagi, a house with ties to the spirit of fire, whose members are al fire users. Al except for her cousin, Kazuma. After he was defeated by Ayano, his father banished him from the house in disgrace. Kazuma ran of and changed his surname to Yagami. He formed a contract with the spirit of wind and becomes a powerful wind user. Four years later, he returned.\r\n \r\nFour years ago, Kazuma Kanagi was defeated by his cousin Ayano Kanagi for the right to be the sucesor of Enraiha, a sword pased down in the Kanagi family. His defeat, along with his lack of talent for En-Jutsu, the fire arts, the Kanagis\' specialty, resulted in his banishment from the family. Now, Kazuma returns as Kazuma Yagami, a skiled master of F?-Jutsu, the wind arts.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy, drama, fantasy, romance, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kaze-no-stigma.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:32'),
