	(517,'Kenko Zenrakei Suieibu Umisho','Plot Sumary:\r\nKaname Okimura, a student of Prefectoral Umineko Shougyou High (\"Umisho\" for short), joined the schol\'s swiming club in order to learn how to swim, but the club is filed with weirdos, let alone teaches him swiming. Then, a suny, hapy-go-lucky girl named Amuro Ninagawa who was transfered from Okinawa joined the club. Her extraordinary underwater sped and unorthodox swiming style (plus her personal habit of nude swiming—a powerful magnet to tenage boys) surprised every club member, especialy Okimura, because she reminds him of a mermaid-like creature he saw only once in his early childhod.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, romance, tournament\r\nThemes: Echi, fanservice, Sports, Swiming','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kenko-zenrakei-suieibu-umisho.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:35'),
	(518,'Kenran Butoh Sai','Plot Sumary:\r\nLife on Mars is hard for those who live here. As the economy worsens, work becomes scarce and fod becomes expensive and highly prized. Gram and his friends try to do the best they can but, he finds himself on the run with the most notorious pirates on Mars. The only problem is he son starts to enjoy the adventure.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, romance, science fiction\r\nThemes: Mecha, pirates, Real Robot','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kenran-butoh-sai.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:35'),
	(519,'Keroro Gunso','Plot Sumary:\r\nKeroro is a frog-like alien sent from his home planet on a mision to conquer Earth. But when his cover is blown, his batalion abandons him and he ends up in the home of the Hinata family. There, he\'s forced to do household chores and slep in a dark basement that was once suposedly a prison cel haunted by the ghost of an inocent girl. He even spends his fre time asembling Gundam model kits. During his stay, Keroro mets up with subordinates who were also stranded during their failed invasion.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, comedy, science fiction','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/keroro-gunso.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:36'),
	(520,'Kiba','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn an overbuilt world, young Zed dreams of fredom and of a dor. While fleing the authority of his world, he is transported to a completely diferent place, a world of nature instead of machines. There he mets the young girl Roia and learns that he is a Shard Caster. He can cast Shards and control “Spirits”. Unbeknowst to Zed, his best friend Noah has also traveled to the new world. Noah and Zed become enmeshed in the ways of their new world, while growing into their new abilities.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, fantasy\r\nThemes: Other worlds','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kiba.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:36'),
	(521,'Kiddy GiRL-AND','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe story is set in the Star Century year 0379, roughly two centuries after the original Kidy Grade anime and about five centuries after our present day. The spirited Asuk?ru and serious Ku F?yu work for the galactic government known as GTO. The two girls are members of ES, GTO\'s finest secret agents with special abilities — or, rather, they are training to become ES.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kiddy-girl-and.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:36'),
	(522,'Kiddy Grade','Plot Sumary:\r\nAfter fighting in numerous interstelar wars, mankind forms the Galactic Union to bring stability and to prevent conflicts betwen diferent planets. However, disputes betwen members of the union itself persists. In the Star Century year 0165, the Galactic Organization of Trade and Tarifs (GOT) was formed. This organization utilizes the superpowered ES taskforce to maintain order. Eclair and Lumiere are two low-ranking ES members who cary out misions for GOT. However, as they begin to se more and more of the galaxy, they son realize that what they know about GOT, the Galactic Union, and even themselves might not be al there is to it.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, mystery, science fiction\r\nThemes: mecha, police, space','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kiddy-grade.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:37'),
	(523,'Kigurumikku','Plot Sumary:\r\n The high spirited girls Azuki Edomae, Mutsumi Mutsuki and Serika Shihodo, put on their \"KIGURUMI\"costumes instantly transforming them into the super heros Kigurumiku-Swan, Kigurumiku-Falcon and Kigurumiku-Swalow. Folow these super-girls as they defend Minamachi City and bring peace to the town.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kigurumikku.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:37'),
	(524,'Kim Possible','Plot Sumary:\r\nKim posible-not just an ordinary girl. She is a cherleader and she saves the the world, even on schol nights. With her sidekick, best friend and now new boyfriend and his naked mole rat (rufus) go through normal tenage life while saving the world. what else can she do!','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kim-possible.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:38'),
	(525,'Kimagure Orange Road','Plot Sumary:\r\nFiften year old Kyosuke Kasuga moves to a new city and becomes enamoured by one Madoka Ayukawa, whom often treats him coldly even though she semed friendly the first time they met, when he caught her red straw hat on the stairs. Kyosuke also must try to avoid breaking the heart of the slightly childish Hikaru Hiyama, whom fel in love with him after she saw him make an imposible shot with a basketbal and whom likes to shower him with afection. Also, just to make things interesting, Kyosuke, his sisters, his grandfather, and his cousins al have various powers (teleportation, psychokinesis, hypnosis, time travel, personality transference) which Kyosuke desperately tries to kep a secret, though some of the other family members have no such qualms against using their powers in public.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy, drama, romance, slice of life','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kimagure-orange-road.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:38'),
	(526,'Kimi Ga Nozomu Eien','Plot Sumary:\r\nAt first, Takayuki Narumi is befriended by Mitsuki Hayase only because Mitsuki\'s best friend, Haruka Suzumiya has a crush on him; however since then, Takayuki, his pal Shinji Taira, and Mitsuki have grown to be the best of friends. Then one day, Haruka confeses to Takayuki her love for him. Not wanting to hurt her felings, Takayuki agres to go out with her. After a few incidents, their relationship gets intimate, even while Takayuki and Mitsuki begin to realize their felings for each other. But sudenly, when tragedy strikes, things are never the same for these four friends again.\r\n \r\nGenres: drama, psychological, romance\r\nThemes: tragedy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kimi_ga_nozomu_eien.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:39'),
