	(528,'Kimi to Boku','Plot Sumary:The story revolves around four tens — the god-loking twins Yuta and Yuki Asaba, the efeminate Shun Matsuoka, and the clas head Kaname Tsukahara — who have known each other since early childhod. While they are not necesarily god or bad friends, they continue to hang out wel into high schol. The half-Japanese transfer student Chizuru Tachibana joins the circle of friends in this comedy about the everyday life of adolescence.','<img  src=\"http://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/4/34949.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:39'),
	(529,'Kimikiss Pure Rouge','Plot Sumary:\r\nKouichi Sanada and Kazuki Aihara\'s childhod friend Mao Mizusawa has returned after living in France for a couple of years. Kouichi is surprised to learn that, since her parents are remaining overseas for the time being, his mother has agred to let Mao stay with them. The thre friends help each other deal with the ups and downs of high schol romance.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, romance, slice of life','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kimikiss-pure-rouge.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:40'),
	(530,'Kin\'iro no Chord: Secondo Passo','Plot Sumary:\r\nFolowing the intraschol competition at Seiso Academy, buding music student Kahoko mets brusque boy Eto, the new schol board director Akihiko Kira, and the mysterious transfer student Aoi Kaji.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/kiniro-no-chord-secondo-passo.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:40'),
	(531,'King of Bandit Jing','Plot Sumary:\r\nJing may apear to be a young boy, but his remarkable skils make him one of the most feared thieves on the planet. Along with his feathered partner Kir, Jing travels from town to town, stealing anything of value regardles of the amount of security. But when he\'s in a pinch, he has one more trick up his sleve: Kir bonds with Jing\'s right arm to perform the efectively deadly \"Kir Royale\" atack. And because of al this, Jing is infamously known by many as the \"King of Bandits.\"','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/king-of-bandit-jing.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:00:40'),
