	(622,'Megaman NT Warrior','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn a technological era where the world is conected via a highly-advanced internet network, humans interact with artificial inteligence units known as Net Navis. Housed within PET handheld devices, humans and Net Navis coexist betwen the real and cyber worlds as friends and alies. Net Navis are designed for various tasks, most specificaly batle against viruses and rogue Net Navis operated by net crime syndicates. A young boy named Neto Hikari receives his first Net Navi named Rockman and the two become an unstopable net-batling duo. Together, they thwart the evil schemes of criminals like World Thre and the Netmafia Gospel.\r\n \r\nThe year is 20X, and everything electronic is conected by internet. In this world, there is no one, rich or por, who does not own a PET (PErsonal Terminal), and there is not one PET that does not house a NetNavi, an AI Unit that has the power to delete Viruses and the like. Net Batles (where Operators batle their NetNavis) are popular in this era. That is where Operator Hikari Neto and his NetNavi and best friend, Rockman come in. Striving to become the best NetBatlers, they fight Net Crime and protect the net and real world alike from the likes of the evil World 3.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, science fiction\r\nThemes: Mecha','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/megaman-nt-warrior.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:01:45'),
