	(644,'Monochrome Factor','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe story revolves around high schol student Akira Nikaido, a typical slacker living a normal life. That is, until he mets the mysterious Shirogane, a man who sudenly apears and tels him to met him at the schol that night. Though he is skeptical, he goes anyway, and subsequently gets atacked by a shadow monster. Shirogane convinces him that the balance betwen the human world and the shadow world has ben distorted, and that Akira must become a \"shin\", which is a creature of the shadow world, in order to help restore the balance.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy, fantasy\r\nThemes: Shounen-ai','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/monochrome-factor.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:02:11'),
	(645,'Monster','Plot Sumary:\r\nKenzou Tenma, a Japanese brain surgeon in Germany, had it al: incredible skil at his work, a rich and beautiful fiance, and a promising carer at his hospital. However, after becoming disenchanted by hospital politics, he chose to save the life of a young boy who got shot in the head over the life of the mayor. As a result he lost the suport of the hospital director, as wel as his position in the hospital and his fiance. A short time later, the hospital director and the doctors that replaced him were murdered, and once again he was catapulted back onto the top. But as the chief suspect of the murders, Tenma did not get a easy life. As a mater of fact, it sems that the boy he saved was much more than he had apeared to be. Now to clear his name and to corect his past mistake, Tenma must get to the botom of these and other murders, and investigate the truth of the Monster who is behind al of this.\r\n \r\nGenres: drama, horor, mystery, psychological, thriler\r\nThemes: Crime, Historical, Police','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/monster.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:02:11'),
	(646,'Monster Rancher','Plot Sumary:\r\nGenki is a boy who loves playing video games. One day he\'s zaped into the world of Monster Rancher and mets the girl Holy and the monsters Mochi, Suezo, Golem, Tiger and Hare. Together, they are searching for a way to revive the Phoenix, which is the only monster capable of stoping the evil Mo.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, fantasy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/monster-rancher.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:02:12'),
	(647,'Moribito – Guardian of the Spirit','Plot Sumary:\r\nBalsa the spearwoman is a wandering warior, who takes on the task of saving lives, in atonement for a past sin. On her journey, she hapens to save a prince, and is tasked with becoming his bodyguard. And he is going to ned one, for his own father, the emperor, wants him dead. \r\nBalsa, the spear wielder and bodyguard, is visiting the New Yogo Empire. She is hired to protect the Second Prince, Chagum, who is endangered because he is posesed by a being despised by his father, the Emperor, who ordered his asasination. The two go on a perilous adventure for the survival of the prince. Throughout the story, Balsa\'s past wil come to light and they wil uncover mysteries about Chagum\'s condition while developing a family-like relationship with each other and others.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, drama, fantasy\r\nThemes: female bodyguard, historical','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/moribito-guardian-of-the-spirit.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:02:12'),
	(648,'Morita-san wa Mukuchi','Plot Sumary:“Morita-san wa Mukuchi” is about Morita Mayu, a highschol girl who rarely speaks. The reason behind it is not because she doesn’t like to talk nor because she has nothing to say. The reason she rarely speaks is due to the fact she thinks to much before speaking, thus losing the timing to speak altogether .','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/morita-san-wa-mukuchi.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:02:13'),
