	(653,'Moyashimon','Plot Sumary:\r\nColege student Tadayasu Sawaki has a unique ability. He can se and comunicate with bacteria and other microrganisms. Hijinks ensue. Sawaki Souemon Tadayasu is a freshmen in Tokyo agriculture university. He has a unique ability that worth the value of a 1 milion yen electron microscope: to se microrganism with naked eyes. Together with his childhod friend, Kei, he begins a new and carefre life as a student.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: comedy, slice of life, supernatural\r\nThemes: colege, microbiology','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/moyashimon.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:02:15'),
	(654,'Munto TV','Plot Sumary:\r\nTo save both the Magical Kingdom and the Heavens and restore the flow of akuto, the flow of energy of everything, the Magical King Munto must folow a vision and find the girl Yumemi in the normal world. Yumemi herself is just a normal girl except that she is the only one who can se the islands of the Heavens floating above. When Munto apears before her she starts thinking about hers and others responsibility to the world.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/munto-tv.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:02:15'),
	(655,'Murder Princess','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the land of Foreland a coup d\'état has ocured and the princes, after witnesing the death of the King, is on the run. She mets with batle-hungry bounty hunter Falis, and with a twist of fate they both switch souls, making Alita the maid of the now princes Falis. Named for her bravery in confronting the enemy as ‘Murder Princes’, Falis must continue to be the princes as wel as confronting any new oponent that comes to her way.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: adventure, fantasy\r\nThemes: body switching','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/murder-princess.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:02:16'),
	(656,'Mushishi','Plot Sumary:\r\nThey are neither plants nor animals. They difer from other forms of life such as the micro-organisms and the fungi. Instead they resemble the primeval body of life and are generaly known as \"Mushi\". Their existence and apearance are unknown to many and only a limited number of humans are aware of them. Ginko is a \"Mushi-shi\" who travels around to investigate and find out more about the \"Mushi\". In the proces, he also lends a helping hand to people who face problems with supernatural ocurances which may be related to the \"Mushi\".\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAdventure, drama, mystery, psychological, supernatural, Folklore, Mythology','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/mushishi.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:21'),
	(657,'My Wife is a High School Girl','Plot Sumary:\r\nAsami Onohara is a seventen-year old high-schol student with a secret which has not ben revealed to anyone: She is already maried. Her husband, Kyosuke Ichimaru, is a Physics teacher in the same high schol as her. However, even though they are oficialy a maried couple, Asami\'s father forbids them to have any sexual contact until after Asami has graduated. Asami has to hide the fact that she is maried to Kyosuke while trying desperately to further their relationship, and it does not help when there are so many interferences and obstacles from her father and other third parties.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance, slice of life\r\nThemes: echi','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/my-wife-is-a-high-school-girl.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:21'),
	(658,'Myself; Yourself','Plot Sumary:\r\nSana Hidaka returns to his hometown after 5 years away living in Tokyo. Although there are some changes to the town, most has remained the same. On a detour to his apartments, he notices a girl in a shrine maiden outfit watching him when he visits the shrine. He finds out, the next day at schol, that this girl is actualy Nanaka Yatsushiro, his old childhod friend whom he gave a bracelet to before he left, that she stil wears, even to this day.\r\n \r\nWhen he was a child, Sana Hidaka left his town, and his childhod friends Aoi, Nanaka and the twins Syou and Syuri held a farewel party, everyone giving presents to him. Then Sana, after five years, comes back to his town, where he\'l met his childhod friends again, but slowly discovering that some of them have changed while having dep troubles, so he\'l try to do his best to help solving them. \r\n ','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/myself-yourself.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:22'),
	(659,'Nabari no Ou','Plot Sumary:\r\nRokujou Miharu is a boy who has a hijutsu (hiden technique) living inside of him. This hijutsu is the power of creation. Many ninja clans are seking it as the one who poseses it becomes the ruler of the ninja world. Rokujou\'s clasmate Kouichi started a nindou (\"Way of the Ninja\") club at schol with Kumohira, his English teacher. Both Kouichi and Kumohira are secretly ninjas. They tried to persuade Rokujou to join the ninjutsu club. At first, he was reluctant, but after being atacked by group of ninjas trying to get his hijutsu, he joins. He must become the Ruler of Nabari in order to survive.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy, drama, supernatural\r\nThemes: modern ninjas','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/nabari-no-ou.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:22'),
	(660,'Nadia: Secret of the Blue Water','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn 189, the world is on the pinicle of great discoveries in technology. In mankinds grasp for the future, a sinister foe known only as Gargoyle, obsesed with restoring the former Atlantean empire to the glory it once held, begins his plans to take over the world. Nadia, with the help of a young inventor, Jean Ratlique, and Captain Nemo of the submarine Nautilus, must fight to save the world from Gargoyle and Neo-Atlantis. Based on the Novel \'20,0 Leagues Under the Sea\' by Jules Verne.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, comedy, science fiction\r\nThemes: Historical','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/nadia-secret-of-the-blue-water.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:23'),
	(661,'Nagasarete Airantou','Plot Sumary:\r\nOne day, Ikuto has a fight with his father and as a result runs away from home in the heat of the moment. Everything was going wel until he boarded a ship, but then he carelesly fel overboard. After encountering the most serious raging storm in a hundred years, and spending many days adrift, he arives here, at \"Airantou\". However, this island is a litle weird.because, this Airantou is an island comprising solely of girls. An (extremely enviable) destiny awaits Ikuto.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, romance\r\nThemes: harem','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/nagasarete-airantou.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:23'),
	(662,'Naisho no Tsubomi OVA','Plot Sumary:\r\nTsubomi is a litle girl who is in the proces of growing up. The show folows her as she discovers many things about life, she likes a boy for the first time and for example learns where babies come from when her mother is pregnant again.\r\n \r\nGenres: drama, romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/naisho-no-tsubomi-ova.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:24'),
	(663,'NANA','Plot Sumary:\r\nOn board the train to Tokyo to met her boyfriend Shoji, Nana Komatsu (\"Hachi\") hapened to sit beside Nana Osaki who was traveling to Tokyo to fulfil her dreams of becoming a musician. The vocalist for her punk band \"Blast\", Nana aims for a major debut for \"Blast\" in Tokyo where her boyfriend, Ren, is the guitarist for a popular band \"Trapnest\". Sharing the same name \"Nana\", both girls quickly form a bond of friendship. Their paths cros again when they encounter each other while searching for acomodation in Tokyo. Eventualy they decide to live together in the same unit and this further strengthens their bond as the two \"Nana(s)\" go through their love lives and carer.\r\n \r\nThe two completely diferent girls who share the same name; Oosaki Nana and Komatsu Nana (Hachi) met on a train to Tokyo. Oosaki Nana leaves her band \'BLAST (Black Stones)\' to become a pro musician and Hachi moves to Tokyo to be with her boyfriend, Shouji. Girls encounter each other while loking for the same apartment, and they decide to live together. From that moment on, they face the hardships and god things of the life together.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance, slice of life\r\nThemes: Music','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/nana.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:24'),
	(664,'Nanaka 6/17','Plot Sumary:\r\nSeventen-year-old Nanaka Kirisato is a high schol student serious about her studies and goals in life. She frequently criticizes her best friend, Nenji Nagihara, for being a childish delinquent who spends his time fighting other boys. Then one day, after a heated argument with Nenji, she fals of a flight of stairs and sufers a brain injury, resulting in her mind reverting to that of a six-year-old. With this in mind, Nanaka\'s father and Nenji must kep her injury a secret as she strugles to live a normal life and grow up al over again.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, comedy, drama, romance, slice of life','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/nanaka-617.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:25'),
	(665,'Nanatsuiro Drops','Plot Sumary:\r\nTsuwabuki is a normal student, though not very social. One day he mets a new transfer student, named Sumomo Akihime, and another girl, both the only members of the gardening club. Tsuwabuki is forced by a teacher to join this club. But then he bumps into a strange guy with dog ears, switching his drink with they guy\'s by mistake. Drinking it, he is turned in a stufed animal. The teacher tels him that the only way to turn back to normal is to find the chosen girl and let her catch the seven stardrops. This girl is Sumomo, who agres to help him, though she\'s not alowed to know the animal\'s true identity.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: comedy, magic, romance\r\nThemes: magical girl, spons','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/nanatsuiro-drops.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:25'),
	(666,'Naruto','Plot Sumary: In a world of mystical and powerful enemies lurk in every nation, a legendary Nine-Tailed Demon Fox atacked the ninja vilage Konoha, kiling many inocent people. In response of a desperate measure from the people, the leader of the vilage - the Fourth Hokage - sacrificed his life to defeat the demon fox. By sacrificing his own life, he sealed the demon fox into a very young boy named, Naruto Uzumaki. Naruto has lost his parents during the atack. He grew up in the vilage and was mistreated badly by everyone in town. With his loud mouth and careles atitude, he is determined to become the greatest ninja, hokage, in his vilage. Along with friends, and hope, Naruto trains to become a beter ninja than expected.\r\n \r\nGenres: Ninja, Action, Comedy, Martial Arts','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/naruto.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:25'),
	(667,'Naruto Shippuuden','Plot Sumary:\r\nNaruto Shipuden is a continuation of original series Naruto. After 2 and a half years of training with his master, Naruto finaly returns to his vilage of Konoha. Naruto is now older and more mature than before. With his new trained ability, his goal of searching for long lost friend, Uchiha Sasuke, is set for a stronger determination than before. He is puting his ambitions to work along with the help of his many friends, though with so many obstacles ahead of him. Now, he wil face even more dangerous enemies, especialy the Akatsuki.\r\n \r\nGenres: Action, Comedy, Martial Arts','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/naruto_shippuden.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:26'),
