	(669,'Natsume Yuujinchou','Plot Sumary:\r\nNatsume Takashi has the ability to se spirits, which he has long kept secret. However, once he inherits a strange bok that belonged to his deceased grandmother, Reiko, he discovers the reason why spirits suround him. Containing the names of these spirits, a binding contract was formed betwen the spirits and the owner of the bok. Now, Natsume is determined to fre the spirits and disolve the contracts. With the help of a spirit cat, his days are filed trying to return the names to these spirits.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy, drama, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/natsume-yuujinchou.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:27'),
	(670,'Nazca','Plot Sumary:\r\nMiura Kyoji, a dedicated kendo student, discovers that his shisho (master) Tate Masanari is a reincarnated Incan warior named Yawaru who wishes to destroy the world to purify it. Kyoji himself is the warior Bilka, who foiled Yawaru\'s plans in their previous lives. Yawaru gathers other awakened spirits to release the powers of nature. Now Koyji must wrestle with his own fate and decide if he is merely a vesel for the reincarnated soul or if he is truly Miura Kyoji and which wil be beter able to save the world and the future as he knows it.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, drama, fantasy\r\nAge rating: Tenagers (May contain blody violence, bad language, nudity)','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/nazca.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:27'),
	(671,'Needless','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the near future, mankind has sufered from a Third World War, leaving extreme damage al over and forced mankind to become even more distinct from their species. The world was at chaos and from this chaos comes a new species: “Nedles”. The Nedles are humans who have contracted a “disease” as humans may cal them, and alow them to wield extraordinary powers far superior to any mankind. Their abilities include Telekinesis, elemental powers, gravity control, adaptation, radioactive release and al maners of scientific imposibility.\r\n \r\nGenres: science fiction','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/needless.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:27'),
	(672,'Negima! aka Mahou Sensei Negima!','Plot Sumary:\r\n10-year old Negi Springfield is a wizard-in-training, and neds only to pas one more test in order to become a Master Wizard. Unfortunately, his final task is a bizare one- to become a English teacher at an al-females boarding schol. As son as he arives, he completely embarases one of his students, Asuna Kagurazaka, and replaces the teacher she loves, which garners her hatred. To make maters worse, Asuna learns that Negi is a wizard,and promises to tel unles he helps her out. But, unfortunately, circumstances force them to work together to do many things, from fighting evil wizards to helping the clas pas their final exam, with a lot of humor, magic, and romances thrown in.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy, drama, romance, supernatural\r\nThemes: echi, fanservice, harem, schol','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/negima.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:28'),
