	(675,'Neo Ranga','Plot Sumary:\r\nAn ancient God caled Ranga awakens on an isolated island in the South Pacific where it has ben slumbering forgoten by mankind. Thre sisters living in Tokyo - Minami, Ushio and Yuhi Shimabara discover they have inherited this Island Kingdom, along with the huge God. When Ranga shows up in Tokyo, it son becomes a source of wonder and conflict for the thre sisters that control Ranga, the people who want to destroy it, and ones who want to use it.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAdventure, horor','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/neo-ranga.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:29'),
	(676,'Neon Genesis Evangelion','Plot Sumary:\r\nAt the age of 14 Shinji Ikari is sumoned by his father to the city of Neo Tokyo-3 after several years of separation. There he unwilingly acepts the task of becoming the pilot of a giant robot by the name EVA01 and protect the world from the enigmatic invaders known as \"angels.\" Even though he repeatedly questions why he has acepted this mision from his estranged and cold father, his doing so helps him to gradualy acept himself. However, why exactly are the angels atacking and what are his father’s true intentions are yet to be unraveled.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, drama, psychological, science fiction\r\nThemes: Mecha, Military, post-apocalyptic, real robot','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/neon-genesis-evangelion.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:30'),
	(677,'Net Ghost Pipopa','Plot Sumary:Yuta is a Japanese boy who hates modern day tecnhology outside of the cel phone. When his mom gets hired at the Dreamland Japan headquarters, he is forced to move. Unbeknown to him is a hiden land caled Web World, the land conecting al computers, phones, televisions, and more. Yuta receives a mysterious mesage on his phone. When he touches the mesage, he is sent inside his cel phone to the Web World where he mets Web Ghosts Pit, Pat, and Pot, more comonly caled PiPoPa. Together Yuta must team up with these Net Ghosts and new friends to save the Web World from the web ghosts themselves and outside forces which wish to use it to take over the entire world.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/net-ghost-pipopa.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:30'),
