	(680,'Night Wizard','Plot Sumary:\r\nNight Wizard. A term given to those whose mision is to protect the world from impending darknes. Renji Hiragi is one such Night Wizard, who is constantly caled on misions, even though al he wants is to be able to go to schol and graduate. However, his latest order was to protect Elis Shiho, who is a new transfer student at his academy. Being draged into the Astronomy Club by Renji\'s childhod friend, Kureha Akabane on her first day at schol, Elis son realises that she to, has the power to become a night wizard, after posesing one of seven secret Jewels, the Jewel of Kindnes. Along with Renji and Kureha, Elis now begins her fight and her new life, as a Night Wizard\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, comedy, drama, fantasy, psychological','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/night-wizard.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:31'),
	(681,'Nightwalker','Plot Sumary:\r\nShido Tatsuhiko is not only a private eye . . . he is also a vampire with no real memory of his past.Joined by Yayoi Matsunaga,a female goverment agent,Riho Yamazaki,an orphaned tenage girl working as his girl friday and Guni,a litle gren imp,Shido must face demonic creatures known as Nightbred.Meanwhile,Cain,the vampire who made him what he is now,is seking him . .\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, horor, mystery, supernatural\r\nThemes: demons, police, vampires','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/nightwalker.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:32'),
	(682,'Nijuu Mensou no Musume','Plot Sumary:\r\nChiko, who had ben leading a lonely life because of her parents death. Together with the Phantom Thief Nij?-Mens? (20-Faces), she sets out on a journey into the real world. She gradualy changes as she encounters new friends and places. But strange events start hapening revolving around the mystery of \"Legacy of the 20-Faces\". So Chiko has to move forward, regardles on how checkered her life wil become.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: adventure, drama, mystery\r\nThemes: detective, thief','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/nijuu-mensou-no-musume.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:32'),
	(683,'Ninja Nonsense','Plot Sumary:\r\nShinobu is a naive ninja-in-training. In order to test her ninja abilites, she must steal the panties of al the high schol girls. The first house she stops at is the abode of one Kaede Shiranui, who hapens to catch Shinobu in the act. Kaeda is the voice of reason and the two girls become quick friends, despite a round yelow bal-thing who claims to be a ninja master and tries to get in the way of their friendship.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy\r\nThemes: ninja, yuri','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ninja-nonsense.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:33'),
	(684,'Ninja Scroll','Plot Sumary:\r\nFourten years after defeating the imortal warior Himuro Genma and thwarting the Shogun of the Dark\'s evil plans, Kibagami Jubei continues to roam al over Japan as a masterles swordsman. During his journey, he mets Shigure, a priestes who has never sen the world outside her vilage. But when a group of demons destroys the vilage and kils everyone, Jubei becomes a prime target after acquiring the Dragon Jewel - a stone with an unknown origin. Meanwhile, Shigure - along with the monk Dakuan and a young thief named Tsubute - travels to the vilage of Yagyu. And with two demon clans now hunting down Shigure, Dakuan must once again acquire the services of Jubei to protect the Priestes of Light.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, horor, supernatural\r\nThemes: ninja','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ninja-scroll.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:33'),
	(685,'Ninku','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the war, a group of wariors caled Ninku fought against the Imperial Army and almost anihilated it. But in the end, the Ninku lost and got shatered. After the war, the imperial army established themselves as the defender of the people with the help of propaganda. They also managed to get the people to think the Ninku were the vilains and had started the war. Fusuke loks like a child but he is the former captain of the first Ninku division. His mother was taken during the war and after the Ninku were defeated, he goes on a journey to find her. On his journey he mets Aicho and Touji, both also former Ninku captains, and together they fight against the imperial army that tries to kil the last remaining Ninkus. \r\nThe ninku is a clan of extinct ninjas who comand esoteric and powerful techniques, hence a lot of other groups are constantly trying to steal their techniques to take over the country. Their primary target is Fusuke, a weird loking kid but one of the most powerful Ninku ninja. Fusuke, together with other Ninku ninja with diferent specialties must fight those threat that caused the downfal of the Ninku clan.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ninku.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:34'),
	(686,'No. 6','Plot Sumary:The TV anime series No. 6 is created by studio Bones, based on a sci-fi light novel series authored by Atsuko Asano. The story is set in a future model city in 2013, caled \"No. 6\". Raised as a top-ranking elite since the age of 2, a boy named Shion lives in an exclusive area of the city. On the night of his 12th birthday, he rescues a boy who cals himself \"Nezumi\" (\"Rat\"). Nezumi ran away from the city\'s Special Security Area. From that moment on, Shion\'s life is changed forever.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/no.-6.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:04:34'),
