	(718,'Panty and Stocking with Garterbelt','Plot Sumary:A company of ghosts has moved into Daten City, taking advantage of human gred. Two angels, Panty and Stocking, are sent from heaven to exterminate them - but in reality they got kicked out for bad behavior.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/panty-and-stocking-with-garterbelt.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:05:00'),
	(719,'Paradise Kiss','Plot Sumary:\r\nYukari is a typical high-schol student who listens to her parents and atends schol everyday. As she starts to question her way of life, she encounters a group of fashion design students who has a clothing label known as \"Paradise Kis\". The group neds to find a model to showcase their designs in an up-coming fashion show and decides to pick Yukari instead. Initialy, Yukari was reluctant to be asociated with this semingly ecentric group, but eventualy, she realizes that they are realy nice people. Furthermore, their pasion and enthusiasm to folow their ideals and dreams make Yukari realise that she has not ben enjoying her life and this motivated her to pursue her own dreams.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nDrama, Romance, Fashion','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/paradise-kiss.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:05:00'),
	(720,'Paranoia Agent','Plot Sumary:\r\nAn elementary schol kid dubed with the title \"shounen bat\" or \"lil sluger\" has ben going around atacking people with his bent, golden bat. Now, two detectives are investigating so they can stop this kid from making any more atacks, but they wil find out son enough. that this case is much more than they expected.\r\n \r\nGenres: drama, horor, mystery, psychological, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/paranoia-agent.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:05:01'),
	(721,'Patalliro Saiyuki','Plot Sumary:\r\nRealy wierd monkey Son Goku & his master Genjou Sanzou-Houshi lok for Budha\'s Scriptures. Along the way, they encounter various people and have interesting adventures.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, fantasy\r\nThemes: Bishounen, Shounen-Ai','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/patalliro-saiyuki.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:05:01'),
	(722,'Patlabor The Mobile Police','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the future, advanced robotics has created heavy robots (\"labors\") for use in a variety of functions: construction, fire-fighting, military, and more. However, though the robots are only machines, their operators are also only human - and humans sometimes turn to crime. Since a heavy labor unit can be a dangerous weapon, the police of the future are set to fight fire with fire, using advanced patrol labor units, \"patlabors\". This is the story of the Second Special Vehicles Division, a motley crew of patlabor policemen and -women doing their best to fight crime and live a normal life.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy, science fiction\r\nThemes: Mecha, Police, Real Robot','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/patlabor-the-mobile-police.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:05:02'),
	(723,'Peacemaker Kurogane','Plot Sumary:\r\nTetsunosuke Ichimura has always ben upset about his short stature. After he ses his parents being murdered by a Choushu asasin right in front of him, he vows with al his heart to become strong enough to take revenge on their kiler. It is now 1864, the first year of Genji. Tetsunosuke, now 15, heads to the headquarters of the Shinsengumi with his older brother Tatsunosuke, loking to join the historical group to fulfil his dreams of geting stronger. Litle does he realize what he is about to experience by doing so, for in order to join this army, one must forego his humanity and become a demon.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, drama, supernatural\r\nThemes: Historical, Samurai','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/peacemaker-kurogane.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:05:02'),
	(724,'Peach Girl','Plot Sumary:\r\nPeach Girl is about an average high schol girl, Momo Adachi, who everyone thinks is a beach buny / slut because of her taned skin. The actual reason she is so taned is because she was on the swim team and tans very easily. She likes a boy, Toji, who she heard only likes non-taned girls. This causes her to question who she is and have low self estem. She spends a lot of time trying to remake herself into the girl she believes he wants. However, she has a friend, Sae, who likes to go behind Momo\'s back and make her life terible, mostly by trying to take Toji away from her. Al the while there\'s another boy, Kairi, who is in love with Momo.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance\r\nThemes: Schol, Tenagers','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/peach-girl.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:05:02'),
	(725,'Penguin Girl','Plot Sumary:\r\nSakura Nankyoku is a total otaku. Due to a fluke, she gets elected as her clas\' Student Council President. Everything takes of from there into a series of crazy misadventures revolving around Sakura, her family, and her clasmates.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, slice of life','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/penguin-girl.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:05:03'),
	(726,'Persona Trinity Soul','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe stage is Ayanagi City, a city near the Japan Sea. It is a futuristic city that was built to cary out the recovery from the calamity caused by the \"Apathy Syndrome\" ten years previous. High schol student Shin Kanzato with his litle brother Jun, met with their elder brother Ry?, who is the chief of the Ayanagi City Police, again after ten years. At that time, a series of strange incidents hapen in Ayanagi City such as the crew of a submarine that sudenly disapears while in their submarine, or a spiritles symptom which disturbs the world after ten years, or the case of the inside out corpse where a student tok on a cruel apearance. Ry? tracks down the organization behind the string of incidents, and having become involved in the incidents, Shin awakens the \"Persona\".\r\n \r\nGenres: action, drama, mystery, psychological, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/persona-trinity-soul.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:05:03'),
	(727,'Petshop of Horrors','Plot Sumary:\r\nCount D, a quite interesting pet shop owner from an area caled Chinatown, sels rare and hard to come by pets to people longing for something special, but with each sale comes a contract. If the rules of the contract are folowed, everything goes fine, but if someone should break the rules of the contract, the pet shop canot be held responsible for anything unfortunate that might hapen. Leon Orcot, a homicide detective, has linked many od and unexplainable deaths together; they al were customers of Count D\'s pet shop, and he intends to find out why.\r\n \r\nGenres: horor, mystery, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/petshop-of-horrors.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:05:17'),
	(728,'Phantom Memory Kurau','Plot Sumary:\r\nIt is the year 210, and on the colonised Mon, a project is under way to explore new aspects of energy. Amami Kurau is the daughter of the chief scientist on the project, and on her 12th birthday, she acompanies her father to the lab to observe the experiments. Then something goes awry, and Kurau is struck by twin bolts of light. In the aftermath, her father is dismayed to find that his daughter is no longer his daughter. Rather, her body is now home to two energy entities with fantastic powers.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, drama, psychological, science fiction\r\nThemes: aliens psychic powers, mecha','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/phantom-memory-kurau.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:05:18'),
	(729,'Phantom the Animation','Plot Sumary:\r\nZwei was an ordinary person, until one day, while walking the strets a night, he witnesed a brutal asasination. He managed to avoid the sniper, a young girl named Ein, but was son captured, and had the memories of his former life erased. He is spared death only by acepting a condition : to train to become an asasin alongside Ein. Now he must find a way to fre himself from this shady world and reclaim his life once again.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, drama','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/phantom-the-animation.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:05:18');
