	(752,'Popotan','Plot Sumary:\r\nSisters Ai, Mai, Mi, and their housekeper android Mea inhabit in a mysterious house that transports them through time and space. Folowing leads obtained from dandelions (or \"popotan\"), the sisters atempt to locate a certain someone believed to hold the answers to their questions. Their peculiar method of transport, however, does not come without its own set of painful drawbacks.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, supernatural\r\nThemes: echi, fanservice','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/popotan.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:05:37'),
	(753,'Potemayo','Plot Sumary:\r\nSunao Moriyama finds a strange but cute creature in his refrigerator that he names Potemayo. Potemayo starts folowing him everywhere, usualy riding on top of his head. His discovery becomes the center of atention in his clas at schol. Son after, a similar creature apears, and is named Guchuko by one of Sunao\'s clasmates. However, Guchuko doesn\'t sem to be as god-natured as Potemayo.\r\n \r\nSunao Moriyama is a junior high schol student living life with (and without) his constantly-traveling father. Things change when he encounters a strange, childish creature that came from his refrigerator. With the help of his newfound friend, Potemayo, Sunao learns that life is about more than just schol.\r\n ','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/potemayo.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:05:37'),
	(754,'Pretear','Plot Sumary:\r\nHimeno Awayuki was a normal sixten-year old girl until her father maried a woman who hapens to be rich. Since then, she has ben perceived as an outcast by both her new stepsisters and her clasmates. Later Himeno finds out from seven men caled the Leafe Knights that she is something caled Pretear, a girl who has the power to merge with and control the nature of the elemental-oriented powers from the Leafe Knights and stop an evil being caled the Princes of Disaster.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, magic, romance\r\nThemes: bishounen, Magical girl, male harem','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/pretear.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:05:37'),
	(755,'Pretty Cure','Plot Sumary:\r\nNagisa Misumi and Honoka Yukishiro couldn\'t be more diferent. Nagisa is sporty and Honoka bokish, and while they atend the same schol, they have very litle in comon - until one day, a shower of shoting stars brings two very unlikely visitors into their lives: Mipuru and Mepuru, refuges from the Garden of Light, which has ben conquered by Darknes. Endowed with new and startling powers, Nagisa and Honoka become Cure Black and Cure White, magical defenders of the light - together, they are Prety Cure.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, comedy, magic\r\nThemes: Magical Girl','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/pretty-cure.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:05:38'),
	(756,'Pretty Cure Max Heart','Plot Sumary:\r\nShortly after the fal of the Wicked King, the Quen of the Garden of Light lost her memory and came to Earth, in the form of a 12-year-old girl named Hikari Kujou. Now, she-with the help of Nagisa and Honoka, endowed with new costumes and powers-must find the 12 Heartiels, which hold the key to restoring the Quen\'s lost memories. For together once again, they are Prety Cure.\r\n \r\nGenres: magic','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/pretty-cure-max-heart.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:05:38'),
