	(776,'Raimuiro Senkitan','Plot Sumary:\r\nAround the the 37th year of the Meiji Era (1904) in the midst of the Ruso-Japanese war, the smal Japanese army, in ned of asistance, uses its special flying (thanks to a benevolent demon) ship, the Amanohara, to atack Rusia\'s major base at Port Arthur (Lushun). Umakai Shintaro, a Rusian diplomat originaly from Japan, defects and goes to Saporo to teach at a girls academy. However, that girls academy is not typical - it is on board the Amanohara, and the five girls Shintaro teaches are known as the Raimu Unit - girls with the ability to sumon powerful beings to fight for them. Shintaro eventualy becomes their teacher and general in batle, and so the six embark on a weird and excesively erotic journey, as Shintaro helps the girls overcome their weakneses, become stronger for the final stand at Lushun, and also understand the motives of the \"Rusian Spiritual Corps\" that asist the oponent, which, unfortunately, has one member whom Shintaro knew wel.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, comedy, supernatural\r\nThemes: Historical, Mecha','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/raimuiro-senkitan.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:06:46'),
