	(779,'Ranma 1/2','Plot Sumary:Ranma 1/2 revolves around a 16-year old boy named Ranma Saotome who was trained from early childhod in martial arts. As a result of an acident during a training journey, he is cursed to become a girl when splashed with cold water, but hot water wil change him back into a boy. Don\'t let the animation discourage you it was made a long time ago so let it slide. This show is very fun to watch and the first anime I ever finished that was over 10 episodes. I highly recomend this for those who want to se something while waiting for another show. Ranma 1/2 is very random and echi.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ranma-12.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:06:47'),
	(780,'Rave Master','Plot Sumary:\r\nHaru Glory is a boy who lives with his sister, Catleya, in Garage Island. After fishing out a. thing caled Plue, he mets Shiba who entrusted him with Rave Stone or more known as Holy Bring. From there on, he embarks on a quest leaving his sister at Garage Island like his father who went to find Rave 15 years ago. He mets Elie, a girl who loves to gamble but has lost her memory. They met up with Musica at Punk Stret. They have to eliminate Demon Card using Rave and is helped by Elie\'s uncontrolable Ethelion and Musica\'s ability of controling silver as a Silver-Claimer. Unfortunately, they had to colect 4 more Raves in order to eliminate the mother of al dark brings, Sinclair. Together, they find out their past including Haru and Musica who both do not know their parents very wel. They also find out the conection betwen Ethelion and Rave.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, fantasy, romance\r\nThemes: Huge Swords','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/rave-master.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:06:48'),
