	(782,'Real Drive','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe Real Drive is a \"neo-futuristic science-fiction suspense\" story is set in A.D. 2061, when a new, more secure information network caled the Material Network (or \"Metal\") has taken over human society. However, aberations begin to crop up as individuals chafe against the rigid system, and so-caled \"cyber divers\" are dispatched to investigate these incidents. The the main cast consists; the cyber driver Mari, an \"intuitive girl\" named Minamo, the team\'s head Eichir?, the combat expert S?ta, and the android Horon.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: drama, mystery, science fiction\r\nThemes: cyberpunk, diving, environment','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/real-drive.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:01:59','2012-03-07 02:06:48'),
