	(824,'Salaryman Kintaro','Plot Sumary:\r\nYajima Kintaro used to be the charismatic leader of a biker gang. Then he retired to have a family. With his wife dead in childbirth, and al alone with a baby boy, Kintaro now embarks upon a new adventure - as the strangest salaryman in al of Japan.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy, drama','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/salaryman-kintaro.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:15'),
	(825,'Samurai 7','Plot Sumary:\r\nA smal vilage is being persecuted by robers who return every harvest to seize the vilage\'s crops. Faced with starvation, the vilagers send out a mision to find and recruit some samurai to defend them. With no pay to ofer except rice, and knowing ful wel that only down-on-their-luck samurai would even consider acepting such an deal, the vilagers can only hope that their saviours wil apear before the rice is ready for harvest.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, adventure, fantasy, science fiction','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/samurai-7.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:15'),
	(826,'Samurai Champloo','Plot Sumary:\r\nMugen is a fierce animal-like warior with a unique Bboying (break-dance) inspired fighting style. Jin has a more traditional style but don’t think of this as a weaknes because his skils are amazing. The two contrasting samurai wariors are far from friends, yet their separate paths sem to cros anyways. Mugen is wandering aimlesly through the city when he stumbles upon a teahouse where he mets Jin and Fu (A ditzy waitres, but don‘t think she doesn‘t have anything hiden up her sleves). Fu convinces them both to come with her in search of a mysterious samurai that smels like sunflowers and their journey begins. This modernized hip-hop tale breaks the bariers of the comon, historical, samurai anime.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, adventure, comedy, drama','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/samurai_champloo.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:16'),
	(827,'Samurai Deeper Kyo','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the year 160, during the batle of Sekigahara, wariors Kyoshiro Mibu and \"Demon Eyes\" Kyo - the legendary slayer of a thousand men - engaged in fierce combat. Both men disapeared when a meteor crashed in the batlegrounds. Four years later, Kyoshiro is spoted on a rural highway, acting as a traveling medicine salesman. He is captured by the female bounty hunter Yuya Shina when she discovers that dep inside him is the dormant personality of \"Demon Eyes\" Kyo himself.\r\n ','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/samurai-deeper-kyo.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:16'),
	(828,'Samurai Jack','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe plots of individual episodes range from dark and epic to light-hearted and comic, but typicaly folow Jack in his singular quest to find a method of traveling back in time. Many of the batle scenes in the series are reminiscent of samurai films, and since Jack\'s robotic enemies \"bled\" oil or electricity and monsters/aliens bled slime or go, the series is able to exhibit the action of these films while avoiding censorship for violence.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/samurai-jack.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:17'),
	(829,'Samurai Pizza Cats','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe seting is a Japanese loking vilage named `Litle Tokyo\' where the Piza Cats run a piza fastfod busines. Litle Tokyo is populated by al kinds of animals. The oficial governor of the town is the Emperor, but since he has gone bananas a council takes care of the wel-being of the vilage. One of the members of this council is caled Seymour \"Big\" Chese, who secretly wishes to take over control of the vilage. The piza take away restaurant is merely a cover for their true job. Whenever evil is afot, the Piza Cats are launched towards the danger from the gun-lokalike clock tower that emerges from the top of their restaurant.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy, science fiction\r\nThemes: mecha','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/samurai-pizza-cats.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:17'),
	(830,'Samurai X: Trust & Betrayal OVA','Plot Sumary:\r\nTaken by slavers when he was a child, Himura Kenshin is rescued only when an encounter with bandits kils of everyone but him. He is found by a master of the Divine Justice Schol of Swordmanship, a schol so deadly that to train in it, means death for either the master or student, there can only be one master. Taken by the master, Kenshin is trained in this schol, only to leave before finishing so that he may join the Meiji restoration and help prevent further tragedies like his own. Thus is born the Batousai, the greatest strength of the Ishin Patriots, a boy of 15 who kils for the sake of building a new, beter world. One night, he comes acros a mysterious woman, Tomoe. He must hide with her when the revolution stumbles. They mary for apearances, but son fal in love. Tomoe has another reason to be with Kenshin, one she regrets but canot stop. Revenge must be satisfied, and only blod can do that.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, drama, psychological, romance\r\nThemes: Historical, samurai','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/samurai-x-trust-betrayal-ova.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:18'),
	(831,'Sasameki Koto','Plot Sumary:\r\nSasameki Koto is the story of Murasame Sumika, an inteligent and athleticaly gifted girl who just hapens to be in love with her best friend, Kazama Ushio. Unable to confes her felings, Sumika can only stay by her side and watch over her. After al, the bigest obstacle to her love is something that she can\'t change. It has nothing to do with the fact they\'re both girls; Sumika just isn\'t Kazama\'s type!\r\n \r\nKazama is only into cute girls and Sumika\'s col personality just doesn\'t fit the bil. Much to her friend\'s dismay, Kazama is always eager to share news about her latest crush. With the duo\'s knack for atracting trouble, it loks like Sumika\'s trials have only just begun.\r\n \r\nGenres: psychological, romance\r\nThemes: yuri','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/sasameki-koto.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:18'),
	(832,'Save Me! Lollipop aka Mamotte! Lollipop','Plot Sumary:\r\nNina,thinking it was a loly, swalows the Crystal Pearl. But the colection of the Crystal Pearl was a test for the magicians. To retrieve the crystal, a special medicine has to be made so now Zero and Ichi, the magicians, have to protect her from others while waiting for the medicine to be completed.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/save-me-lollipop-aka-mamotte-lollipop.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:18'),
	(833,'Sayonara Zetsubou Sensei','Plot Sumary:\r\nItoshiki Nozomu is the world\'s most negative person. To his way of thinking, there is no hope or meaning in this existence. Even the thre kanji of his name become the two-kanji word zetsubou, \"despair\", when compresed. What an ironic twist of fate, then, that he becomes teacher to a clas containing his precise oposite, the invincibly positive-minded Fura Kafuka.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, slice of life\r\nThemes: harem, parody, schol, suicide','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/sayonara-zetsubou-sensei.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:19'),
	(834,'School Days','Plot Sumary:\r\nMakoto Ito rides the train to and from schol every day. However, at the begining of his second term, he fals in love with a beautiful girl that also rides the train. Unfortunately, she barely knows of his existence. Her name is Kotonoha Katsura, and though they atend the same schol, they are not in the same clas. In an atempt to catch her eye, Makoto enlists the aid of a close female friend of his: Sekai Saionji. She helps him, despite the fact that she-unbeknownst to Makoto-is in love with him. Thus the thre are bound in a love triangle of life changing proportions.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, horor, psychological, romance, slice of life\r\nThemes: echi, Echi (nudity), Harem, Schol','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/school-days.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:19'),
