	(836,'Scrapped Princess','Plot Sumary:\r\nPacifica Casul is the most feared and hated person by the folowers of the God Mauser. Known as the Scraped Princes, she is the poison that wil destroy the world. To avoid being kiled by the zealots of Mauser, Pacifica and her adoptive brother and sister leave the vilage of Manhurin. Her brother, Shanon, is an expert with the sword while Racquel is proficient with magic. At every step of the way, however, someone is constantly trying to kil Pacifica, hoping to somehow avert the catastrophe that is suposed to befal the world on her 16th birthday.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAdventure, comedy, drama, fantasy, science fiction, Historical','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/scrapped-princess.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:20'),
