	(842,'Sekirei','>Plot Sumary:\r\nMinato Sahashi is extremely inteligent, yet due to his inability to cope under presure has failed the colege entrance exam twice. As a result he has ben branded an idiot and loser by many. One day after talking to his yet again disapointed mother he comes into contact with a girl named Musubi who was under atack. The girl runs but takes him with her and son finds that Minato, while unknown to him, is an Ashikabi, one of the mysterious set of masters that have the genetic trait that can become partners with some of the 108 cute girls, buxom women, and bish?nen caled \"Sekirei\". The reason for the partnership alows the Sekirei to use al their power to win in the competition held by the mysterious MBI corporation.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, comedy, magic, romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/sekirei.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:23'),
