	(845,'Senjou no Valkyria','Plot Sumary:\r\nWhen Imperial forces atack the smal border town of Bruhl, Welkin Gunther, son of late General Belgen Gunther, is forced to fight for his life alongside Town Watch captain Alicia Melchiot. Along with Welkin\'s adopted sister Isara, the thre escape to Galia\'s capital and subsequently join the country\'s militia forces. As members of the newly-formed Squad 7, they must work to repel the invading Imperial forces and discover the true purpose of the invasion itself.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, drama','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/senjou-no-valkyria.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:24'),
	(846,'Senko no Night Raid','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe story is set in Shanghai in 1931, when the Imperial Japanese Army has ben dispatched to mainland China due to the relatively recent First Sino-Japanese War, Ruso-Japanese War, and World War I. In this cosmopolitan city of intrigue, there is a special military spy organization caled “Sakurai Kikan” that has since ben buried in history.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/senko-no-night-raid.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:25'),
	(847,'Serial Experiments Lain','Plot Sumary:\r\nLain Iwakura apears to be an ordinary girl, with almost no experience with computers. Yet the suden suicide of a scholmate, and a number of strange ocurences, conspire to pul Lain into the world of the Wired, where she gradualy learns that nothing is what it sems to be. not even Lain herself.\r\n \r\nGenres: drama, mystery, psychological, science fiction, supernatural\r\nThemes: cyberpunk, networking, self-identification, wired','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/serial-experiments-lain.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:25'),
