	(850,'Shakugan no Shana','Plot Sumary:\r\nSakai Yuji, a high schol student who expected his normal life to last forever, is dead. When he was on his way home he witnesed a shocking view as the world sudenly froze: people were engulfed by blue flames and a monster resembling a large dol swalowed them. Just as the monster prepared to consume Yuji, a sword-wielding girl in black atire with flaming red eyes and hair that burns like embers saved him from the monster. The girl caled herself a \"Flame Haze\" who hunts the \"Guze no Tomogara\", creatures from another world. As Yuji noticed a blue flame in his chest, she caled him a \"Torch\", a temporary replacement, saying that the \"real\" Yuji\'s existence had already ended. Unfazed, Yuji befriended the strange girl, named her \"Shana\", and joined her fight against Tomogara and other Flame Hazes.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, comedy, drama, fantasy, romance, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/shakugan-no-shana.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:26'),
	(851,'Shaman King','Plot Sumary:\r\nAsakura Yoh is a shaman, a person who comunicates with ghosts. He enters the Shaman Fight, for whoever wins the tournament gets to comune with the Great Spirit, God . . . that and his fiance Ana wants to be the wife of the Shaman King. Helping him are his friends Manta, Horo Horo, Ryu, and his samurai ghost partner, Amidamaru.\r\n \r\nOnce every 50 years, there\'s an event caled the Shaman Fight, and whoever wins becomes the Shaman King and can use the most powerful spirits ever. Asakura Yoh comes to Tokyo to train and become the Shaman King. Acompanied by many friends, he defeats many enemies along and the way, and gets more friends.\r\n \r\nYoh is a young shaman, one who can se and comunicate with spirits. Shaman\'s also have another power,the ability to unify with spirits and use the spirit\'s fighting skils. Yoh is training to become the Shaman King, strongest among al Shamans, a title won by wining the Grand Tournament that takes place every 50 years. Helping him are his best friend Morty, a short kid who can also se ghosts, Amidamaru, an old samurai and his spirit partner, and his fiance Ana, a spirit meduim and his trainer. However, another Shaman family is trying to kep Yoh out of the tournament. Along the way he mets a bunch of other misfit ghosts and wanabe Shamans.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, drama, supernatural, tournament','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/shaman-king.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:27'),
	(852,'Shamanic Princess','Plot Sumary:\r\nFrom the Guardian World, home of mages, Tiara has ben sent on a mision: recover the stolen Throne of Yord, the most powerful magic artifact of al. But Tiara finds herself in a dilema - the Throne has ben taken by her former lover, and there is more to the situation than mets the eye. \r\n \r\nGenres: action, magic, romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/shamanic-princess.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:27'),
	(853,'Shangri-La','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe story of a young woman fighting for her survival in a real \"urban jungle.\" Only 18 years old, Kuniko Hojo finds herself at the heart of the batle for humanity\'s future when she discovers that the government which rules Atlas intends to continue marginalising the les-privileged mases outside the tower - by force, if necesary.\r\n \r\nGenres: science fiction','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/shangri-la.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:28'),
	(854,'Shattered Angels','Plot Sumary:\r\nKu Shiratori often fantasizes and dreams of her \"prince\", and longs to met him as her ordinary schol life in the schol-city of Academia proceds. One day, a young man, Kyoshiro Ayanokoji, transfers to her clas, and strangely enough, bears a striking resemblence to the prince of her dreams. Ku is elated, but son after things start to not go her way, as she son finds out that Kyoshiro is diferent from how she imagined him to be. However, after Kyoshiro saves her after she gets caught in the midle of a fight involving mechanical creatures and magic she has never witnesed before, she begins to apreciate him once again, and thus, a beautiful relationship betwen two young people comences.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, drama, fantasy, romance\r\nThemes: Bishoujo, Bishounen, Mecha, yuri','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/shattered-angels.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:28'),
	(855,'Shigofumi: Letters from the Departed','Plot Sumary:\r\nFumika and Kanaka are mail cariers- but not the typical kind. For one, Kanaka is a talking staf and for two, Fumika delivers shigofumi: leters from the dead adresed to the living. These leters are a final, true, comunication derived from hate, hope, and love. The story unfolds folowing this pair and their uncomon job as wel as Fumika\'s unique \'situation\'.\r\n \r\nGenres: drama, psychological, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/shigofumi-letters-from-the-departed.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:28'),
	(856,'Shigurui: Death Frenzy','Plot Sumary:\r\nAt the begining of the Edo Era, when people enjoyed a time of peace, Lord Tokugawa Tadanaga holds a fighting tournament. In the past, matches were fought with woden swords. This time, real swords wil be used. One-armed Fujiki Genosuke and blind Irako Seigen wil fight each other in this match. Both are disciples of Iwamoto Kogan, who is known as Japan\'s greatest swordsman. Each of them are determined to prove himself the sucesor of Iwamoto\'s schol. However, there can only be one champion. So begins a story of intertwining fates, conflict, and strange destinies.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: drama\r\nThemes: Historical','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/shigurui-death-frenzy.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:29'),
