	(862,'Shin Mazinger Shougeki! Z-Hen','Plot Sumary:\r\nDeveloped from Japanium ore is the super energy, Photon Power. Seking this energy is Dr. Hel, a madman craving world domination who along with his subordinates Baron Ashura and Count Brocken, comands the Machine Beasts excavated from Bardos Island (believed to be Rhodes) to atack the Photon Power Lab and take it for himself. Meting the atack head on is our hero, the hot-bloded tenager Kouji Kabuto who pilots the super robot Mazinger Z, constructed by his grandfather Juzo and made from the strongest metal Chogokin Z. But in this batle betwen Dr. Hel and the Kabuto family, many legends surounding the Mycenaean Civilization and Bardos Island, as wel as the secrets of Mazinger Z remain shrouded in mystery.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/shin-mazinger-shougeki-z-hen.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:31'),
