	(895,'Soul Eater','Plot Sumary:\r\nSet in the Shinigami technical schol for weapon meisters, the series revolves around 3 groups of each a weapon meister and a human weapon. Trying to make the later a \"Death Scythe\" and thus fit for use by the Shinigami, they must colect the souls of 9 evil humans and 1 witch.\r\n \r\nSoul Eater is an anime that centers around meisters and their weapons and their mision to colect 9 evil souls and 1 witch soul. Upon doing that the meister\'s weapons wil become a Deathscythe, which is the highest title for a weapon. Maka, Soul Eater, Black Star, Tsubaki, Death the Kid, and Paty and Liz Thompson are the characters Soul Eater revolves around. Besides taking the time to gather souls these students of Shibusen defend Death City from some of the most powerful of creatures while stil atending schol and trying to become stronger.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, adventure, comedy, supernatural, human weapons, Shinigami','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/soul-eater.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:49'),
	(896,'Soul Hunter','Plot Sumary:\r\nThousands of years ago, it was a time of witchcraft and dark magic. An evil sorceres has bewitched the emperor of the mighty dynasty and he has become a mindles pupet. The country is in shambles and evil spirits lurk everywhere. The human world is on the verge of uter destruction. A bold mision is planed by the Confederation of the Imortal Masters. They send a young master wizard to hung down the vilains and evil warlocks in the devastated lands.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, fantasy, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/soul-hunter.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:50'),
	(897,'Soul Link','Plot Sumary:\r\nAizawa Ryota was in the 3rd grade of the preparatory course of Central Military Academy. AD 2045, he went to a space station, Aries, for the training with his clasmates including Nagase Saka and Nitak Kazuhiko. However, the station was atacked by a terorist group, Halarax. *Sarara*\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, comedy, drama, romance, science fiction\r\nThemes: Military','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/soul-link.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:50'),
	(898,'Sousei no Aquarion','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn a distant future, humanity once again is facing the threat of the \"Shadow Angels\". Mystical creatures who returned after 12.0 years of absence. They atack human cities and kidnap their inhabitants in order to drain their \"prana\" (vital energy). To fight against them, youngsters with special powers from around the world were gathered and trained to pilot the \"vector machines\", thre ancient ships that together form mankind\'s ultimate weapon, \"Aquarion\". The story revolves mainly around Apolo, a tenager rumored as the rencarnation of Apolonius, a falen angel who fought against his own kind to protect mankind. Few believe it could be true, but the fact is that dispite his untamed and reckles nature, he proved to be an invaluable aset in the batle against the Shadow Angels.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance, science fiction\r\nThemes: Mecha','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/sousei-no-aquarion.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:51'),
	(899,'Souten Kouro','Plot Sumary:\r\nSouten Kouro’s story is based losely on the events taking place in Thre Kingdoms period of China during the life of the last Chancelor of the Eastern Han Dynasty, Cao Cao (15 – March 15, 20), who also serves as the main character.\r\n \r\nThe Thre Kingdoms period has ben a popular theme in Japanese manga for decades, but Souten Kouro difers greatly from most of the others on several points. One significant diference is its highly positive portrayal of its main character, Cao Cao, who is traditionaly the antagonist in not only Japanese manga, but also most novel versions of the Thre Kingdoms period, including the original 14th century version, Romance of the Thre Kingdoms by Luo Guanzhong. Another significant diference from others is that the storyline primarily uses the original historical acount of the era, Records of Thre Kingdoms by Chen Shou, as a reference rather than the aforementioned Romance of the Thre Kingdoms novel. By this, the traditional hero of Romance of the Thre Kingdoms, Liu Bei, takes on relatively les importance within the story and is portrayed in a les positive light. Yet, several aspects of the story are in fact based on the novel version, including the employment of its original characters such as Diao Chan, as wel as anachronistic weapons such as Guan Yu’s Gren Dragon Crescent Blade and Zhang Fei’s Viper Blade.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nDrama, historical','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/souten-kouro.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:51'),
	(900,'Souten no Ken','Plot Sumary:\r\nKasumi Kenshiro, also known as Yan Wang or the King of Death, is a Tokyo profesor and the 62nd sucesor to the deadly asasin art known as Hokuto Shinken. He leaves his teaching job and travels to Shanghai after geting word that his old Qing Bang Triad friend, Pan Guang-Lin, and his friend\'s sister and Kasumi\'s love interest, Pan Yu-Ling, are in trouble. While in Shanghai, he encounters and fights the thre families of Hokuto: Hokuto Sonkaken, Hokuto Soukaken, and Hokuto Ryukaken. He does al this while revolting against the corupt Hong Hua Triads to restore honor and power to the Qing Bang. \r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, adventure, Historical, Military','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/souten-no-ken.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:52'),
	(901,'Space Pirate Captain Harlock','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe year is 297. Mankind has become complacent and stagnant. Al work is done by machines, while humans spend al their time on entertainment. But when a mysterious invader from the stars catches Earth unawares, only the legendary space pirate Captain Harlock and the crew of the Arcadia have the wil to stand against them.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, drama, horor, science fiction\r\nThemes: aliens, pirates, space, war','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/space-pirate-captain-harlock.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:53'),
	(902,'Spawn','Plot Sumary:\r\nKen Kurosawa is a clever hitman and karate fighter from Los Angeles. His one and only reason to fight is to take care of his sick litle sister, Mariko. But then Ken is murdered with a bomb-car. His last wish is to be with his sister in her birthday and take care of her forever. Seven years later, Ken is back on Earth, but now as a Helspawn. Now, he most survive using his new powers from Hel against the new threats surounding him, his old friendships and his litle sister Mariko, who is now turning into a famous actres.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, drama, horor, mystery, supernatural\r\nThemes: Demons, Police','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/spawn.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:53'),
	(903,'Special A','Plot Sumary:\r\nHikari Hanazono, the main character, has always ben second to Kei Takishima. While Hikari considers Kei a rival and somewhat of a friend, Kei loves Hikari. Everyone knows this, but she is to dense to notice. Their wrestling loving fathers first introduced them to one another when they were 6 years old. Asuming that she was the best in wrestling, young Hikari chalenged Kei to a wrestling match only to be thoroughly defeated by him. Ever since that fateful incident, Hikari swore to beat Kei in schol grades, a sporting event - anything. To do this she has enroled in the same schol as Kei since elementary. Now she atends Hakusenkan, an ultra elite schol, that costs her carpenter father a lot of money. Hikari and Kei are the top two students in the schol, with Kei holding firmly to that number one position.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy, drama, romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/special-a.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:54'),
	(904,'Spice and Wolf','Plot Sumary:\r\nKraft Lawrence, a 25 year old pedler traveling from town to town seling and buying various things to make a living during a period much like Europe in the Midle Ages. One night when stoped at the town of Pasroe, he finds in his wagon a 250 year old pagan wolf deity girl named Holo. She apears to be that of a 15 year old girl, except for a wolf tail and ears. She introduces herself as the town\'s godes of harvest who has kept it blesed with god harvests of wheat for many years. Despite having the responsibility to watch over the town, she wants to go back to her homeland in the north caled Yoitsu, she believes the people have already forsaken her anyway and that she has kept her promise to maintain the god harvests. She manages to bargain her way out of the vilage by making a deal with Lawrence to take her with him. As they travel, her wisdom helps increase his profits, but at the same time, her true nature draws unwanted atention from the church.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAdventure, drama, fantasy, romance, supernatural, economics, trading','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/spice-and-wolf.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:54'),
	(905,'Spider Riders','Plot Sumary:\r\nWhile on a hiking trip with friends, 1-year old Hunter is sucked into the fantastic subteranean world of Arachnia, where the insects have become the dominant – and giant – species. Hunter is welcomed by an elite warior team, The Spider Riders, with whom he must fight to defeat the evil Invectid, and ultimately, find his way home.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, fantasy\r\nThemes: spiders','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/spider-riders.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:54'),
