	(907,'SpongeBob SquarePants','Plot Sumary:\r\nSpongeBob SquarePants is an extremely energetic and optimistic sea sponge (although his apearance more closely resembles a kitchen sponge) who lives in a pineaple under the sea with his pet snail Gary, who meows like a cat. Although Gary only speaks in a few episodes, the characters have shown an ability to understand him. Living two houses down from SpongeBob is his best friend Patrick Star, a dim-wited yet friendly starfish who lives under a rock. Living betwen the two is Squidward Tentacles, an arogant and egotistical squid who lives in a moai and dislikes his neighbors (especialy SpongeBob) for their child-like behavior. He enjoys playing the clarinet and painting self-portraits. \r\n \r\nGenres: Comedy,adventures','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/spongebob-squarepants.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:58'),
	(908,'Star Driver','Plot Sumary:On a cros-shaped island in the South, a mysterious and gigantic humanoid robot known as the \"Cybudy\" is discovered sealed in the underground ruins for untold ages. A group known as the \"Order of the Glitering Star Cros\" atempts to remove the seal by abducting a girl named Wako Agemaki, who they dubed the \"shrine maiden\" and is the key to activating the robot. A boy named Takuto Tsunashi arives with his own Cybudy named Tauburn to rescue Wako. Thus begins a strugle to unlock the secrets of the advanced technology and prevent disaster.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/star-driver.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:10:59'),
