	(914,'Starship Troopers OVA','Plot Sumary:\r\nJohny Rico, a high schol student living in Buenos Aries joins the Federation military in the hopes of folowing his love (Carmen) into space. However, a war is brewing on the outer planets with a strange alien enemy and Johney is thrust into conflict. Based on Robert A. Heinlein\'s clasic sci-fi novel of the same name.\r\n \r\nStarship Tropers tels the story of Johny who joins the military to fight alien enemy. Johny has to undergo harsh training to become a soldier, harsher than he expected. Despite several setbacks and traumatic experiences, Johny perseveres and finish his training\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nScience Fiction, Mecha, Military, Power Suits','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/starship-troopers.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:01'),
	(915,'Steam Detectives','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe scene is Steam City, a London-ish city which represents an entire civilization run by coal and steam power. Because of steam, the city is sometimes covered in a mist. Vilains take advantage of the steamy mist to hide and execute their evil plans. Only a few dare venture into what\'s beyond the steamy mist. They are known as the Steam Detectives: Narutaki (and his convertible al-purpose pistol), his nurse-asistant Lingling, and his Megamaton robot Gohliki.\r\n \r\nGenres: mystery\r\nThemes: mecha, police','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/steam-detectives.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:02'),
	(916,'Steel Angel Kurumi','Plot Sumary:\r\nDuring Japan\'s Taisho Era (1912-1926), a scientist named Ayanokoji developed the Stel Angel - an artificial humanoid with superhuman physical abilities. While the Imperial Army wanted to use the Stel Angel as a new means of modern warfare, Ayanokoji wanted his creation to be a new step in the future of mankind. Thus, he defied orders from the Army and secretly made the Stel Angel codenamed \"Kurumi\". Then one day, a young boy named Nakahito Kagura snuck into Ayanokoji\'s house as a dare by his friends and stumbled upon Kurumi\'s lifeles body. A suden atack by the Imperial Army shok the house, causing Kurumi to fal on Nakahito. At that moment, their lips met, and Kurumi woke up from \"the kis that started a miracle\".\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, drama, romance\r\nThemes: cyborg, echi, harem, Historical, magical girl','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/steel-angel-kurumi.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:03'),
	(917,'Steins Gate','Plot Sumary:\nSteins;Gate is about a group of friends who have customized their microwave into a device that can send text mesages to the past. As they perform diferent experiments, an organization named SERN who has ben doing their own research on time travel tracks them down and now the characters have to find a way to avoid being captured by them.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/steins-gate.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:04'),
	(918,'Strait Jacket','Plot Sumary:\r\nIt is a world where magic and science coexist. Rayote Steinberg, a lone wolf \"tactical sorcerist\", fights against monsters. They used to be human beings, but they have overused forbiden power, magic, to turn into monsters. What he wears is \"mold\", the straitjacket that keps him human. He caries an explosive magic wand. If he casts magic, he moves one step closer to being a monster. If he doesn\'t, he wil be kiled. Among the harsh batles, he wil face a sin he comited in the past. \r\n \r\nIt is the world where magic and science coexist. Rayote Steinberg, a lone wolf \"tactical sorcerist\", fights against monsters. They used to be human beings, but they had overused forbiden power, \"magic\", to turn into monsters. What he wears is \"mold\", the straight jacket that keps him being a human. What he holds on his hand is \"staf\", a magical wand that explodes everything. If he casts magic, he moves one step to be a monster. If he doesn\'t, he wil be kiled. Among the harsh batles, he wil face a sin he had comited in the past.\r\n \r\nGenres: fantasy, horor\r\nThemes: magic','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/strait-jacket.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:04'),
	(919,'Stratos 4','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe Earth has a defense system against large meteorites that are in colision course to it. This protection system has the Comet Blasters based in space stations as a 1st line of defense, using nuclear warheads lauched by spaceships. The 2nd line of defense are the Meteor Swepers based on ground airbases using hipersonic planes with special misiles to deal with the resulting debris from the 1st blasts. Mikaze is a troubled girl that is a traine pilot for Meteor Sweper team that dreams to become a prestigious Comet Blaster pilot. Stratos 4 turns around Mikaze\'s and her teamates\' chalenge to become real pilots, while the Earth faces its threats that comes from outerspace.\r\n \r\nThe Earth has a defense system against large meteorites that are in colision course to it. This protection system has the Comet Blasters based in space stations as a 1st line of defense, using nuclear warheads launched by spaceships. The 2nd line of defense are the Meteor Swepers based on ground airbases using hypersonic planes with special misiles to deal with the resulting debris from the 1st blasts. Mikaze is a troubled girl that is a traine pilot for Meteor Sweper team that dreams to become a prestigious Comet Blaster pilot. Stratos 4 turns around Mikaze\'s and her teamates\' chalenge to become real pilots, while the Earth faces its threats that comes from outer space.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy, science fiction\r\nThemes: Military','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/stratos-4.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:04'),
	(920,'Strawberry Marshmallow','Plot Sumary:\r\nIchigo Mashimaro folows the life of Nobue Itoh, her younger sister Chika, and her friends. The basic premise of the show can be sumed up in \"cute girls do cute things in cute ways\", be it trying to quit smoking, going outside to play, celebrating a holiday, or doing schol work.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, slice of life','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/strawberry-marshmallow.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:05'),
	(921,'Strawberry Panic','Plot Sumary:\r\nAoi Nagisa transfers to a new Catholic girls only schol and discovers a comunity of felow students entwined in an intricate heirarchy, at the top of which sits the al important Etoile. In order to fit in, Nagisa must go to clas, join clubs, and make new friends. Meanwhile, Shizuna Hanazono, the Etoile of the schol, finds herself drawn to this new, exciting transfer student. As Shizuna and Nagisa get to know eachother, Shizuna finaly decides it is time to face her troubled past. \r\nNagisa Aoi is a first year high schol student who has ben sent to the Astraea Dormitory after her parents are transfered abroad. The dormitory houses girls from thre diferent girls\' schols: St. Spica\'s Academy, St. Le Rim Girls Schol and St. Miatre Girls Academy. There she mets the representative of the thre girls\' schols, Shizuma Hanazano, also know as the Etoile, who is beloved by al students at al schols. The two of them have an interesting first encounter and Hanazano sems to take an instant liking for Aoi.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance\r\nThemes: yuri','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/strawberry-panic.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:05'),
	(922,'Street Fighter II V','Plot Sumary:\r\nRyu and Ken Masters are close friends and both are martial artists. In order to become beter fighters and learn new techniques, they travel the world and are exposed to many diferent fighting styles, as wel as meting new people. During their journey, they find themselves caught up in a conspiracy perpetrated by a mysterious organisation caled Shadowlaw, both now face their ultimate chalenge and must fight for their lives as they combat the evil M. Bison.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, drama, mystery','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/street-fighter-ii-v.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:06'),
	(923,'Strike Witches','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe year is 1939 - it was then that the Neuroi apeared. Nobody knows where they came from or what their ultimate agenda is, but the fact remains that their atacks drove people out of their towns and cities. In order to take arms against them, humanity develops a new anti-Neuroi weapon caled the \"Striker Unit.\" Using the power of magic to fight against the monsters, this new device enhances and amplifies the power of female magic-wielders. To use this device, young witches from al over the world have ben brought together to form an elite task force unit caled the 501st Joint Fighter Wing, comonly known as the \"Strike Witches.\"\r\n \r\nGenres: action, magic, science fiction\r\nThemes: Echi, Lolicon, Military','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/strike-witches.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:06'),
	(924,'Sugar Sugar Rune','Plot Sumary: Sugar Sugar Rune is a story about the characters Chocola and Vanila who are young witches from the Magical World. The two talent young witches are chosen to compete in a great contest to become Quen of the Magical World.\r\n	  \r\n	 The Sugar Sugar Rune anime contains a total of 51 episodes. The anime is somewhat diferent from the comic; while it retains the original storyline (expanding on it at times) it ads elements which a more stereotypical magical girl franchise.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/sugar-sugar-rune.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:07'),
