	(926,'Sukisho','Plot Sumary:\r\nAfter faling out of a 4th story window, Hashiba Sora has lost his memory. He returns to his schol to find a new romate in his dormitory. Sora gradualy begins to fal in love with his new male romate, while trying to put together pieces of his past.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance, slice of life\r\nThemes: shounen-ai, yaoi','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/sukisho.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:07'),
	(927,'Summer (OVA)','Plot Sumary:\r\nTakumi Kaizu is a boy that doesn\'t have any particular interest in girls. During a schol trip, his friend Osamu asks him whether or not he has a girl that he likes. From that point on, Takumi slowly becomes interested in the oposite sex, through the girls that he is acquainted with in his daily life. As the last sumer of his high schol life begins, Takumi begins to search for the one girl that he can cal his girlfriend, while watching Osamu\'s desperate and relentles search for a girlfriend as wel.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/_summer-ova.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:08'),
	(928,'Sumomomo Momomo','Plot Sumary:\r\nMomoko Kuzuryu is a martial-arts crazed tenage girl who has grown up in the mountains with her father, a legendary fighter. However, one day her father tels her that because she is a girl, she wil never be able to master the family\'s ultimate technique. The only thing for her to do is go mary the strongest warior, and produce the strongest ofspring. Her unlikely fiance is the handsome but weak Koushi Inuzuka, the son of her father\'s best friend and rival. Their mariage was agred upon by their fathers before they were born. However, Koushi has no interest in martial arts; in fact, he is a coward who frezes whenever he ses violence. Instead, he wants to become a prosecutor, so that no criminal can escape capital punishment. Despite Koushi\'s adamant refusal to mary her and his subsequent displays of cowardice, Momoko fals in love with him and swears to remain in his house and train with his father in order to become the strongest fiance ever.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy, romance\r\nThemes: echi, martial arts','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/sumomomo-momomo.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:08'),
	(929,'Super Gals','Plot Sumary:\r\nRan Kotobuki is wel-known as the #1 gal in Shibuya, and she lives to shop, eat, and have as much fun as posible. But she\'s not al faux nails and para para; in the midst of al of her gofing of, she protects Shibuya from al maner of undesirable people, and she often devotes herself to helping both friends and strangers out of trouble, big and smal. Of course, she\'d rather be eating fre fod and scoring god deals on clothes, but geting someone out of a big pinch can be just as fun for her. Because of this, she\'s widely respected by the denizens of Shibuya, and although she may lok (and even act) a bit shalow, she\'s got a big heart and a sense of justice that could put her Police Chief father to shame. But she\'s not interested in that line of work, much to her family\'s dismay. Al she wants is to hang out with her best friends Miyu and Aya, and continue spending her days as Shibuya\'s #1 gal.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, slice of life','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/super-gals.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:09'),
