	(932,'Super Robot Wars Taisen OG: The Inspector','Plot Sumary:Six months after the conclusion of the L5 Campaign and the DC War, the crews of the PT cariers, Hagane and Hiryu Custom have gone their separate ways. They are not far apart for long, however, as the remnants of the DC son begin to push against the Federation Forces with newly acquired resources. A mysterious organization, the Shadow Miror, has begun to arm them with weapons and robots that should not exist. Compounding maters, inter-dimensional entities known as Einsts begin to apear around the World and sem to share a psychic conection with ATX pilots, Kyosuke Nanbu and Excelen Browning. Even worse, aliens caling themselves, The Inspectors, have arived from outer space with plans to retake the White Star and finish the job the Aerogators could not. As this new, four sided war begins, Lamia Loveles, a Shadow Miror operative sent to spy on the Federation Forces must chose betwen her orders and her new found friends among the Hagane and Hiryu crews.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/super-robot-wars-taisen-og-the-inspector.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:10'),
	(933,'Suteki Tantei Labyrinth','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn a forgoten town known as the old capital of Tokyo, strange and mysterious crimes are progresively ocuring. These supernatural ocurances are beyond comprehension and bring fear and teror to the people. Only one person is not intimidated by the evil underlying these ocurances and is wiling to chalenge them: Hyuga Mayuki, a young boy detective who holds a special insight power that alows him to uncover the real truth behind these ocurances.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, mystery, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/suteki-tantei-labyrinth.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:10'),
	(934,'Suzuka','Plot Sumary:\r\nYamato Akitsuki travels to Tokyo alone to study in one of the high schols located within the area. He lives in with his aunt who operates a public bath solely for the ladies in the local district and begins his normal high-schol life. One day, he chances upon a girl in schol and is imediately mesmerised by her beauty. He is shocked when he realise later that the girl, Suzuka, is actualy living next dor to him. From then on, Yamato\'s ordinary life begins to change litle by litle.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance, slice of life\r\nThemes: Sports','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/suzuka.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:11'),
	(935,'Switch OVA','Plot Sumary:\r\nTwo newbies at the Narcotic Control Department in Japan, Hal and Kai, strugle against: drug dealers, gangs, murderers, psychopaths, mysterious organizations, and mad people in general. The gentle and caring one of the group, Kai, who has problems of his own, has the tendancy of turning into a lethal kiling machine in certain scenarios. The way he acts changes like that of a \"switch\". As the two do their job, answers of what is behind Kai\'s strange behavior and who exactly he is, is revealed.\r\n \r\nGenre: Action','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/switch-ova.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:11'),
	(936,'Tactical Roar','Plot Sumary: In the near future the world\'s climate shifted creating in the Western Pacific a perpetual super cyclone: the Grand Roar that alterted the earth, floding most countries. Shiping and navigation became important to nations and folowed by the specter of ocean pirates thus necesisating companies to hire escort cruisers to safeguard their investments. Hyousuke Nagimiya is a system enginer that was comisioned to upgrade the Pascal Magi maned by an entire crew of women with its captain, Misaki Nanaha. Together the crew strives to prove themselves to their detractors that they are no mere \'Alice Brand\'. Yet as they go about their mision a larger global conspiracy sems to be working behind the scenes to take advantage of this new world order.\r\n	  \r\n	 Genres: Comedy, Romance, Science Fiction','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/tactical-roar.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:12'),
