	(939,'Tales of Eternia','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn order to prevent the catastrophe caled the Grand Fal, Rid Hershel and his companions Farah, Kel and Meredy have obtained the thre Greater Spirits (\"Craymels\" in the game version) of Inferia. En route to Mount Farlos, Rid is kidnaped by the bounty hunter Marone Blucarno, and the party is compeled to head to Belcarnu, an archipelago far from the major cities of Inferia. A series of adventures forces them to remain on the islands, where a more imediate threat to Inferia sleps.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, fantasy, romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/tales-of-eternia.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:16'),
	(940,'Tales of Phantasia','Plot Sumary:\r\nCles Alvein, a young swordsman from the town of Totus, along with his friend Mint Adnade, a healer with the talent of Mana, are sent back in time to defeat Dhaos, a sorcerer imprisoned by their parents decades ago. Along with the help of the archer Chester Barklight, the sumoner Klarth F. Lester and the half-elf Arche Klaine, they sek to right the wrongs of Dhaos and return peace to the land. Based on the 195 Super Famicom Game by NAMCO, \"Tales of Phantasia.\"\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, fantasy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/tales-of-phantasia.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:17'),
	(941,'Tales of Symphonia','Plot Sumary:\r\nBased on the same-name Game Cube and Play Station game, \"Tales of Symphonia\". Two worlds exist, both unaware of the existance of the other. In order for one world to flourish, the other wil have to perish. On the perishing world, a Chosen one is send on a journey to restore that world\'s mana by awakening the Spirits and becoming an angel. Colete Brunel, the Chosen of Sylvarant, sets out on her journey acompanied by her best friends Lloyd Irving and Genis Sage. As they travel further they met more friends and even more enemies, while they learn more and more about the truth behind the World Regeneration.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, fantasy, psychological, romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/tales-of-symphonia.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:17'),
