	(950,'Teen Titans','Plot Sumary:\r\nTen Titans is an American animated television series based on the popular DC Comics characters. The show was created by Glen Murakami, developed by David Slack, and produced by Warner Bros. Animation. It premiered on Carton Network on July 19, 203. Despite high ratings, the series shut down production after five seasons, with the series finale episode \"Things Change\" airing on January 16, 206. Two comic bok titles from DC Comics, Ten Titans Go! (ended) and Tiny Titans (curent), are based on the series. Many characters, scenarios and themes were drawn from the 1980s DC Comics series The New Ten Titans.\r\n ','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/teen-titans.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:28'),
	(951,'Tegami Bachi – Letter Bee','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn a land of perpetual night, your heart is your light. Amberground is locked in darknes. A man-made star casts only a dim light over the land. The pitch-black wildernes is infested with Gaichu-colosal insects with metal exoskeletons. The Gaichu make travel betwen the cities of Amberground extremely dangerous. But thankfuly the Leter Bes, a brave corps of mesengers, risk their lives in order to kep the hearts of Amberground conected.\r\n\r\nGauche Suede is on his last delivery before a big promotion. In the outskirts of Yodaka, the darkest area of Amberground, Gauche is surprised to find that the package is a young boy named Lag Seing. Lag had ben traumatized by his mother\'s abduction and is due to be delivered to his aunt. In this remote area rife with Gaichu, Lag and Gauche face a dangerous journey that inspires Lag to become a Leter Be.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction/Fantasy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/letter-bee.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:29'),
