	(961,'Texhnolyze','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn a man-made underground society, descendants of a banished generation vie for control of the crumbling city of Lux. Ichise, an orphan turned prize fighter, loses a leg and an arm to satisfy an enraged fight promoter. On the brink of death he is taken in by a young woman doctor and used as a guinea pig for the next evolution of Texhnolyze. With his new limbs, Ichise is taken under the wing of Oonishi, a powerful leader of Organ, an organization with some hold on Lux. As Ichise is drawn deper into a war for teritorial control of the city, he learns of his posible future from the young girl prophet Ran, who guides him from the shadows in his darkest times. With the explosion of the warfare, Ichise must uncover the truth about Lux and fight for his survival as he realizes his destiny.\r\n \r\nGenres: drama, psychological, science fiction\r\nThemes: crime organizations, cyborg, post-apocalyptic','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/texhnolyze.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:34'),
	(962,'The Big O','Plot Sumary:\r\nParadigm City is a place without a past. 40 years ago, something hapened that wiped the memories of everyone in it. Unfortunately, the people of Paradigm City were very busy before then, making Megadueses(giant robots) and monsters. People who were born after the memory wipe are gaining/recovering memories of the past and using them to build newer threats. Roger Smith keps Paradigm City safe with the help of The Big O (a faithful giant robot), his butler Norman and the android Dorothy, Roger keps Paradigm City safe. As problems mount and more memories surface, Roger\'s past and Paradigm\'s future begin to become suspect.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, mystery, psychological, science fiction\r\nThemes: Mecha, Noir','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/the-big-o.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:35'),
	(963,'The Boondocks','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe Bondocks is a social satire of American culture and race relations (or stereotypes in the world), revolving around the lives of the Freman family – ten-year-old Huey, his younger brother, eight-year-old Riley, and their grandfather, Robert. The Bondocks takes place in the same place and time frame as its comic counterpart. The Freman family, having recently moved from the South Side of Chicago to the peaceful, fictional suburb of Wodcrest, Ilinois (compare Crestwod) find diferent ways to cope with this acute change in seting as wel as the drasticaly diferent suburban cultures and lifestyles to which they are exposed. The perspective ofered by this mixture of cultures, lifestyles, and races provides for much of the comedy in this series.\r\n \r\nGenres: Animated comedy, Black sitcom, Action, Satirical, Dark comedy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/the-boondocks.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:35'),
	(964,'The Daughter of 20 Faces','Plot Sumary:\r\nChiko, who had ben leading a lonely life because of her parents death. Together with the Phantom Thief Nij?-Mens? (20-Faces), she sets out on a journey into the real world. She gradualy changes as she encounters new friends and places. But strange events start hapening revolving around the mystery of \"Legacy of the 20-Faces\". So Chiko has to move forward, regardles on how checkered her life wil become.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAdventure, drama, mystery, detective, thief','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/the-daughter-of-20-faces.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:36'),
	(965,'The Epic of Zektbach OVA','Plot Sumary:The story begins when the kingdom of Noiglado sudenly invades the smal country of Azuelgat and brings it to the brink of destruction. General Adnowel leads Noiglado\'s trops against Azuelgat\'s final, remaining line of defense: the fortres Doroah, led by a skiled female warior named Shamshir.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/the-epic-of-zektbach.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:36'),
	(966,'The Familiar of Zero','Plot Sumary:\r\nMet Louise, a buding magician. The students at the Tristein Academy cal her \"Zero Louise\", due to her curent record of zero suceses with magic. In fact, her magic tends to go spectacularly wrong. Now, as an important test of her aptitude for magic, she must sumon a familiar to be her servant. At this critical moment, she sumons up al her magic and wishes for a familiar that is \"devoted, beautiful and powerful\", and gets. Hiraga Saito, an ordinary Japanese boy. It\'s dificult to say who is more surprised and dismayed, but the rules don\'t alow for second atempts. Louise is stuck with her strange familiar, and he with her.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAdventure, comedy, magic, romance, Magical girl','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/the-familiar-of-zero.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:37'),
	(967,'The Galaxy Railways','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the future, the planets are conected with a masive galactic railway system. The pasengers of the railways are protected by two forces, the Space Panzer Grenadiers (SPG) and the Space Defense Force (SDF). This is the story of Manabu Yuki, a new member of the Sirius Platon within the SDF. He and his new crewmates meld together as a team through their dealings with escaped criminals, meteors, hostile aliens, a time vortex, ghosts and terorists before defending mankind from its greatest peril yet.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, drama, science fiction\r\nThemes: military, space','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/the-galaxy-railways.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:37'),
