	(969,'The Irresponsible Captain Tylor','Plot Sumary:\r\nJusty Tylor has no training, no skil, no initiative, or leadership qualities; in fact, he has nothing going for him except one crucial thing: dumb luck. This is his only saving grace, and it saves him from imposible ods, time and again. By sher acident, he rescues the General\'s beloved grandaughters; for which, the General is extremely grateful, and as such, makes this inept recruit a ful Captain, but gives him comand of the lowliest ship in the flet, the Soyokaze. This ship has a crew of misfits and mutiners, so the General is not at al woried about Tylor making maters worse. He has kiled two birds with one stone: he has given this inept freloader a \'reward\' for saving the grandaughters, and also put a captain in comand of a ship and crew he would just as wel se engulfed by a black hole. Thus, Tylor begins an adventure that takes him from the lowest and highest positions of authority, from which he somehow manages to make things turn out for the best. \r\n \r\nJusty Ueki Tylor thought a carer in the United Planets Space Force would give him an easy life: enlist, get a desk job, spend the rest of his life in quiet, boring comfort. No soner does he take the qualifying exam than war breaks out with the Ralgon Empire, and circumstances quickly conspire to land this volunter of the stret in comand of the cruiser \"Soyokaze.\" Now Tylor faces two uphil batles - against the Ralgon flet that wants to kil him, and against his own crew, who expect him to conform to some standard of military discipline. But as the war rages, Tylor\'s easy-going ways might have a beter chance of converting his crew than vice-versa.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, science fiction\r\nThemes: Military','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/the-irresponsible-captain-tylor.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:38'),
	(970,'The Law of Ueki','Plot Sumary:\r\nKousuke Ueki, a student of the Hinokuni Junior High Schol, is picked by a God Candidate, Koba-sen, to participate in a competition where people batle out to become God and only the strongest wil prevail. Embodied with the ability to turn garbage into tres, Kousuke wil be joining in the batle against other junior high schol students in this selection. This sets the premise for the earth-friendly batle where the students wil pit their powers against the rest.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, drama, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/the-law-of-ueki.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:38'),
	(971,'The Legend of Koizumi','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe story is a fictionalized version of Japan\'s 89th prime minister, Junichirou Koizumi. In this political parody, Koizumi plays a special form of \"mahjong diplomacy\" against foreign adversaries such as George W. Bush, Kim Jong-il, Vladimir Putin, Margaret Thatcher, and others.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/the-legend-of-koizumi.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:39'),
	(972,'The Legend of the Legendary Heroes','Plot Sumary:\r\nRaina Lute is a lazy student of Roland Empire Royal Magician\'s schol. One day, Roland Empire goes to war against a neighboring country Estabole, and he lost his clasmates in the batle. After the war, Lute sets out for a journey to search the relics of a \"Legendary Hero\" at Emperor Zion Astar\'s comand. And he finds out a deadly curse spreading the continent.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/the-legend-of-the-legendary-heroes.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:39'),
	(973,'The Legend of Zelda','Plot Sumary:\r\nEach episode of Zelda folowed the adventures of the hero Link and the royal Princes Zelda as they defended the kingdom of Hyrule from an evil wizard named Ganon. Most episodes consisted of Ganon (or his minions) either atempting to capture the Triforce of Wisdom from Zelda, kidnap Zelda herself, or use another method to conquer Hyrule. Link and Zelda are in some episodes asisted and acompanied by a fairy-princes, Sprite.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/the-legend-of-zelda.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:40'),
	(974,'The Melancholy of Haruhi Suzumiya','Plot Sumary:\r\nOn the first day of high schol a beautiful girl named Haruhi Suzumiya introduces herself as having \"no interest in ordinary humans\". She asks for any aliens, time travelers, sliders or espers to join her. Watching her weird behaviour is Kyon who sits in front of Haruhi and is the only person who talks to her. When Kyon coments about Haruhi\'s joining every club in schol and then quiting he unwitingly gives Haruhi an idea to start her own after schol club. Thereafter Kyon and several others find themselves draged, literaly, into the Save our world by Overloading it with fun Suzumiya Haruhi\'s Brigade (the S.O.S. Brigade for short).\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy, mystery, psychological, science fiction, slice of life, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/the-melancholy-of-haruhi-suzumiya.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:40'),
	(975,'The Sacred Blacksmith','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe story takes place after an abominable war that foisted a \"devil\'s contract\" upon a land. Cecily Campbel, a former noble\'s daughter who joined a knighthod, encounters a man who dispatches some hodlums with one swep of a mysterious sword. The man poseses the power of the same \"devil\'s contract\" that has become tabo, now that peace has ben restored. Cecily has ben searching for a blacksmith who can repair an old sword she inherited from her father, and that mysterious young man hapens to be blacksmith named Luke. This encounter launches their adventures together.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/the-sacred-blacksmith.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:11:40'),
	(977,'The Skull Man','Plot Sumary:\r\nSet in an alternate history of Japan, frelance photographer Minagami Hayato returns to his hometown of Ootomo to investigate rumors of a man wearing a skul mask comiting murders there. Once in the city, he discovers conections betwen the victims and a local pharmaceutical company, a new religious sect, and strange half human, half animal creatures. Along with a young photographer, he decides to find out who the Skul Man realy is.\r\n \r\nGenres: horor, mystery, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/the-skull-man.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:33'),
	(978,'The Smurfs','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe Smurfs are kind, litle, blue creatures that live somewhere dep in the Forest. They live in mushroms and even have their own language. Their bigest enemy is Gargamel, the wizard who lives together with his cat Azraël nearby in the Forest. Gargamal\'s only goal in life is to catch and eat The Smurfs. But The Smurfs aren\'t gona let that hapen anytime son!','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/the-smurfs.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:34'),
	(979,'The Twelve Kingdoms','Plot Sumary:\r\nYoko Nakajima, an unhapy high schol student, is one day sudenly faced with a strange man who swears alegiance to her. After a batle with demon-like beasts, he then takes her to another world along with two of her clasmates. There, her apearance has changed and she can understand the language even though her clasmates canot. But their status as \"Kaikyaku\" (people who come from Earth) makes them hunted fugitives, so they wander the land of the 12 countries, simply trying to survive and to figure out the reason why they were brought to this world.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAdventure, drama, fantasy, psychological','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/the_twelve_kingdoms.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:34'),
	(980,'The World God Only Knows','Plot Sumary:Keima Katsuragi is an avid galge gamer known at his schol as \"Otamega\" (a derogatory term combining the words Otaku and Megane) and on the internet a \"The Capturing God.\" One day he receives an e-mail ofering him a contract to \"capture\" girls. He acepts thinking it\'s a chalenge and a demon from Hel named Else apears. She asks for his help in capturing runaway spirits that are hiding in \"real\" girls. He refuses stating he only like the girls from the game and she tels him that if he refuses then both of their heads wil be cut of.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/the-world-only-god-knows.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:34'),
	(981,'The World of Narue','Plot Sumary:\r\nIizuka Kazuto is a 14 year old boy who mets a somewhat weird but cute and charming girl named Narue Nanase who claims she is an Alien. The show is about the trials and tribulations of the young couple as they get to know each other.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, romance, science fiction\r\nThemes: aliens','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/the-world-of-narue.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:35'),
	(982,'They Are My Noble Masters','Plot Sumary:\r\nDue to family troubles, Ren Uesugi and his sister, Mihato, leave their home. They end up moving to the city but find themselves with a lack of money. Somehow they are able to find work in the form of the Kuonji family\'s mansion, being employed as servants to the thre sisters of the Kuonji family: Shinra, Miyu, and Yume. Being a servant also asociates Ren with the mansion\'s aditional servants and the Kuonji sisters\' friends.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance\r\nThemes: echi, harem, hot girls, Yuri','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/they-are-my-noble-masters.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:35'),
	(983,'This Ugly Yet Beautiful World','Plot Sumary:\r\nHigh schol student Takeru Takemoto works part time as a (motor)bike courier. During one of his deliveries, he saw a mysterious light pasing him and fel into a forest. What he had found was a beautiful girl coming out from a glowing cocon, caling herself “Hikari.” While Takeru was quite embarased because of Hikari’s nudity, a strange monster sudenly showed up and imediately atacked the two. Both Takeru and Hikari demonstrated the power of their other selves before Takeru had a clue of what’s going on.\r\n \r\nRyou and Takeru are typical high schol students. That is, until Takeru finds an alien caling herself Hikari. Takeru’s life is sudenly filed with aliens and monsters and a drunken robot and he’s just trying to kep everyone safe while he figures out what the hel is going on.\r\nTakeru is a typical high schol student until he saves Hikari, an alien girl with no memory of her past. Comiting himself to take care of her, Takeru’s life is sudenly filed with aliens and monsters.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, comedy, drama, romance, science fiction','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/this-ugly-yet-beautiful-world.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:36'),
	(984,'Tide-Line Blue','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe catastrophe, \"Hamer of Eden\", resulted in the los of six bilion lives and the floding of 90% of the land. The New United Nations were formed to pursue peace on the ruined lands 14 years later. Kel is a boy living in a town caled Yabitsu, an area which prospered due to the energy from the nuclear generator brought by the catastrophe. His next kin, Aoi, is the secretary general of the New United Nations. She views the catastrophe as an oportunity to create a new world in which nations can help one another overcome diferences in races and religions. However, her eforts to realise that vision fail because of the unwilingnes of the nations to change. Gould, a military oficer, fels that the only way to make an order is through the military. Using Ulyses, a nuclear submarine, along with his crew, including Kel\'s brother Tean, Gould caries out a coup to declare war against the New United Nations in his atack on Yabitsu.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, adventure, drama, Military, post-apocalyptic','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/tide-line-blue.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:45'),
	(985,'Tiger & Bunny','Plot Sumary:Schternbilt City is home to people caled \"Next,\" who use their special abilities to protect the people as superheroes. These heroes solve cases and save lives so they can wear sponsor logos or acquire \"hero points.\" Their activities are documented on the popular program \"Hero TV,\" which picks the \"King of Heroes\" in a yearly ranking. The veteran hero Wild Tiger has always prefered to work alone, but now he\'s ben asigned the rokie Barnaby Broks Jr., who has a diferent perspective on being a superhero.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/tiger-bunny.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:46'),
	(986,'Time of Eve','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the not to distant future androids have come into comon usage. Taking the androids for granted, humans treat them as if they were comon everyday tols, while on the other hand, some people empathize with androids due to their human-like apearance (save for a digital ring floating above their heads). This has become a social problem and these people are frowned upon as a result. Rikuo, one who has taken androids for granted for his entire life, one day discovers that Samy, his home android, has ben acting strangely and finds a strange phrase recorded in her activity log. He, along with his friend Masaki, traces Samy\'s fotsteps and come upon an unusual cafe. This cafe\'s main rule is to not discriminate betwen humans and androids.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nScience fiction, androids','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/time-of-eve.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:46'),
	(987,'To Aru Kagaku No Railgun','Plot Sumary:\r\n“The story is set in a world where supernatural powers exist through science, and magic exists through religion. University City. 2.3 milion inhabitants. 80% of the students are active in the ‘Brain Development Program’ and out of those only 7 are Level 5s. Met the civilian protagonist Mikoto and her friend Kuroko, maintainers of peace and order at the University district, as members of the ‘Judgement’.”','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/to-aru-kagaku-no-railgun.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:47'),
	(988,'To Aru Majutsu no Index','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn a world where science clarifies supernatural powers. In a huge colege that has power development in its curiculum. To a resident high schol student, Kamijou Touma, a pure white sister apears. She cals herself \"Index\" and says that sorcerers are chasing her. Thus, Kamijou Touma enters the world of the ocult.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, comedy, drama, fantasy, science fiction','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/to-aru-majutsu-no-index.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:47'),
	(989,'To Heart','Plot Sumary:\r\nAdapted from a dating sim game of the same name. Hiroyuki Fujita and Akari Kamigishi are friends since childhod. With both of them are in the same clas in high schol, their love towards each other begin to acumulate, slowly but day by day. However there are many cute girls around.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, romance, slice of life\r\nThemes: schol','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/to-heart.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:47'),
	(990,'To Love-Ru','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe story is about Yuki Rito, a high-schol boy who canot confes to the girl of his dreams, Sairenji Haruna. One day when coming home and sulking in the bath-tub a mysterious, nude girl, apears out of nowhere. Her name is Lala and she comes from the planet Deviluke, where she is the heir to the throne. Her father wants her to return to her home planet so she can mary one of the husband candidates, but she decides that she wants to mary Rito in order to stay on Earth.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/to-love-ru.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:48'),
	(991,'Togainu no Chi Bloody Curs','Plot Sumary:Several years after the end of a war, the city of Toshima has falen into decay and ben taken over by the crime syndicate Viscio. There, the head of the syndicate, Il Rey, has convened the batle game \"Igura.\" Meanwhile, Akira, falsely acused of a crime, has made a deal to earn his pardon: go to Toshima, defeat Il Rey, and destroy the syndicate.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/togainu-no-chi.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:48'),
	(992,'Tokimeki Memorial Only Love','Plot Sumary:\r\nAoba Riku has just transfered to a new high schol because of his father\'s job, and things aren\'t quite what he expected. The headmaster\'s secretary controls the schol while espousing the virtues of academic fredom, the teachers are even stranger than normal teachers, and half the student body is walking around with animal ears on. On his very first day, Riku is unfortunate enough to find himself at the center of the student council\'s latest event, which has him runing for his life. Al this on top of the normal high schol rigour of popularity contests, crushes, and homework makes it unsure whether Riku wil be able to survive this new schol.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/tokimeki-memorial-only-love.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:49'),
	(993,'Tokko','Plot Sumary:\r\nShindou Ranmaru has just graduated from police academy and asigned to Toki: Special Mobile Investigation Force. On the day of his graduation, he mets the half-naked girl he has ben seing in his dreams, Rokujo Sakura. It turns out she works for a secret group within Toki, known as Toko: Special Public Safety Task Force. Shindou ends up joining Toko to avenge his parents’ death, and solve the mystery mas murder of residents in his hometown of Machida. Botomles pits start to apear around Japan, and mysterious creatures emerge from them, linked to the mas murder of humans. Al this to do with something caled “The Box of Dirge”…\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy, horor, mystery, psychological, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/tokko.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:49'),
	(994,'Tokyo Magnitude 8.0','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe premise of the project is the 70% or higher posibility that a magnitude 7.0 earthquake wil ocur in Tokyo in the next 30 years. The anime wil depict what would hapen if an 8.0 earthquake tok place. The story wil center on Mirai, a midle schol freshman girl who goes to Tokyo’s artificial Odaiba Island for a robot exhibition with her brother Yutaka at the start of sumer vacation. A powerful tremor emanates from an ocean trench, the famed Tokyo Tower and Rainbow Bridge crumble and fal, and the landscape of Tokyo changes in an instant. With the help of a motorcycle delivery woman named Mari who they met on Odaiba, Mirai and Yutaka strive to head back to their Setagaya home in western Tokyo.\r\n \r\nGenres: drama\r\nThemes: disaster','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/tokyo-magnitude-80.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:50'),
	(995,'Tokyo Majin','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the night of Tokyo, mysterious deaths involving the \'Reborn Dead\' ocur. Mysterious transfer student, Tatsuma Hiyu, and delinquent student, Kyouichi Houraiji, fight these undead every night. They, along with the rest of their group, son realize that a greater threat, that involves even more powerful demons, is near.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, drama, horor, psychological, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/tokyo-majin.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:50'),
	(996,'Tokyo Majin Gakuen Kenpucho Tou: Dainimaku','Plot Sumary:\r\nThis is the sequel of Tokyo Majin, only this time in the begining the brave fighters have to fight against a dark asasination organisation made for kiling. The organisation is known as the \'Dancing Swords\' they gather up people with god fighting skils and awaken power just like Hiyu\'s and everyones in order to asasinate others only making those who live above the law doing evil as their targets. Hiyu, Aoi, Kyoichi, Sakurai and Daigo are atacked by these fighters from the organisation and have to fight against them.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, horor, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/tokyo-majin-gakuen-kenpucho-tou-dainimaku.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:50'),
	(997,'Tokyo Mew Mew','Plot Sumary:\r\nMomomia Ichigo, is your average twelve year old girl that is until one eventful date. her crush masoya ayoama asks her to atend an endangered species exhibit and after a series of events she gets hit by a ray that turns her into a cat. now her and four other girls must band together to fight of the chimera and alien who are invading their planet.\r\n \r\nOn her first date with the cutest boy in schol, Ichigo is zaped by a mysterious ray that scrambles her DNA with that of the endangered Iriomote wildcat. The next day, Ichigo discovers that she has developed the agility (and ocasionaly the ears and tail) of a cat, as wel as the power to transform into a pink-haired superheroine, Mew Ichigo. She and four other girls, each endowed with the genes of a diferent \"Red Data\" animal, have ben selected for the top-secret Mew Project, which aims to protect the Earth from an alien menace known as Dep Blue.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, comedy, magic, romance, science fiction, slice of life, supernatural\r\nThemes: Aliens, Magical Girl, Sentai, Superhero','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/tokyo-mew-mew.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:51'),
	(998,'Tokyo Tribe 2','Plot Sumary:\r\nThis is the other side of Tokyo, a Tokyo of a diferent color. There, various tribes are living. The SARU from Japan\'s Musashino, WU-RONZE of Bukuro, and HANDS of Shindyuku. Young men living in the city.the public of modern times builds a home out of coruption, these young men of the sordid side of life, a side caled \"reality,\" are depicted here.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, drama\r\nThemes: yakuza','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/tokyo-tribe-2.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:51'),
	(999,'Tokyo Underground','Plot Sumary:\r\nUnder the capital city of Tokyo, Japan, there exists a large, vast, and unknown world known as Underground. There, people known as Elemental Users exist; people who have the ability to control the elements: Fire, Water, Lightning, Magnetism, Freze, etc. Met Rumina Asagi and his best friend Ginosuke Isuzu, two average high schol freshmen who reside in Tokyo. When they mets Gravity User, Chelsea Rorec, and the Miko of Life, Ruri Sarasa, their whole life changes into one big adventure.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, romance, science fiction\r\nThemes: superpowers','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/tokyo-underground.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:52'),
	(1000,'Tom And Jerry','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe Tom and Jery series is very popular due to its violent and comedic fight betwen a comon pair of enemies, the comon house cat and mouse. The plots of each short usualy center on Tom\'s numerous atempts to capture Jery and the mayhem and destruction that ensues. Since Tom rarely atempts to eat Jery and because the pair actualy sem to get along in some carton shorts, it is unclear why Tom chases Jery so much. Some reasons given may include normal feline/murine enmity, duty acording to his owner, Jery\'s atempt at ruining a task that Tom is entrusted with, Jery eating Tom\'s master\'s fod which Tom has ben entrusted with safeguarding, revenge, Jery saving other potential prey (such as ducks, canaries, or goldfish) from being eaten by Tom, competition with another cat, and Jery ruining Tom\'s atempts to seduce feline feme fatales of which Jery does either out of disgust or jealousy, among other reasons.\r\n \r\nTom rarely suceds in catching Jery, mainly because of Jery\'s clevernes, cuning abilities, and luck. Interestingly enough, many of the title cards show Tom and Jery smiling at each other which sems to depict a love-hate relationship rather than the extreme anoyance each displays towards the other in each carton. There are also several instances within the cartons where they display genuine friendship (\"Springtime for Thomas\") and concern for each other\'s wel-being (such as in \"Jery and the Lion\" where Jery in one instance tricks Tom into thinking he has shot Jery, and Tom comes runing with the first aid kit).\r\n \r\nThe short episodes are famous for some of the most violent gags ever devised in theatrical animation: Jery slicing Tom in half, shuting his head in a window or a dor, Tom using everything from axes, pistols, explosives, traps and poison to try to murder Jery, Jery stufing Tom\'s tail in a wafle iron and a mangle, kicking him into a refrigerator, pluging his tail into an electric socket, pounding him with a mace, club or malet, causing a tre or an electric pole to drive him into the ground, sticking matches into his fet and lighting them, and so on.[1] Despite al its popularity, Tom and Jery has often ben criticized as excesively violent. Despite the frequent violence, there is no blod or gore in any scenes in the original cartons that made the pair a household name. However, in a very rare instance, when Tom gets sliced into pieces in the opening credits of Tom and Jery:The Movie, blod is clearly visible. A recuring gag involves Jery hiting Tom when he\'s preocupied, with Tom initialy oblivious to the pain—and only feling the efects moments later, and vice versa; and another involves Jery stoping Tom in midchase (as if caling for a time-out), before he does something, usualy puting the hurt on Tom.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/tom-and-jerry.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:52'),
	(1001,'Tonagura!','Plot Sumary:\r\nKazuki has ben awaiting 10 years for the day when her neighbours moved back to their old house. She has a crush on Yuji, whom she considers as her first love but to whom she never managed to expres her felings for him before they moved out. Yuji often comes over to play with Kazuki, Kazuki\'s older sister Hatsune and Yuji\'s sister Marie when they were kids. Her ideal depiction of Yuji was son shatered when he turned out more than she had expected, him acting al echi during their reunion. With their parents of in South America, both families must learn to live with each other and rekindle the childhod felings they shared together. Things get even more crazy as they atend the same schol.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/tonagura.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:53'),
	(1002,'Toradora','Plot Sumary:\r\nDespite Ryuji Takasu\'s gentle personality, his eyes make him lok like an intimidating delinquent so he is uterly hopeles about his chances of geting a girlfriend anytime son, and does not have many close friends either. After being greted by his hungover mother in the morning, Ryuji goes to schol and is hapy to find that he gets to be in the same clas as his best friend Yusaku Kitamura and crush Minori Kushieda. However, it is then that he unexpectedly knocks into \"the schol\'s most dangerous animal of the highest risk level\" — Taiga Aisaka — who just hapens to also be in his clas, and is a god friend of Minori.\r\n \r\nDespite Ryuji Takasu\'s gentle personality, his eyes make him lok like an intimidating delinquent. Clas rearangements on his second high schol year put him together with his best friend, Yusaku Kitamura, and his hiden crush, Minori Kushieda. Along with these two comes Kushieda\'s best friend, Taiga Aisaka. Her delicate apearance contrasts with her brutal personality. Secretly in love with Kitamura, Taiga agres to help Ryuji with his love interest as long as he helps her get closer to hers.\r\n \r\nIt’s a new schol year and Ryuji Takasu discovers not only is he in the same clas as his best friend, Yusaku Kitamura, but also Minori Kukshieda whom he\'s had an undisclosed crush on for quite some time. Along with Kitamura and Minori is Minori\'s best friend, the “Palmtop Tiger”, tiny Taiga Aisaka whom, despite her smal stature, takes nothing from nobody. (When unflatering pictures of her in a bathing suit were circulated, “Of course, I made it rain blod in the photography club.”) Taiga is secretly in love with Kitamura and she and Ryuji, despite an oil and water relationship, agre to mutualy suport each other in their quests for their heart’s desire.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy, romance, slice of life','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/toradora.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:53'),
	(1003,'Toriko','Plot Sumary:\nIn the world of Toriko, many extravagant and delicious ingredients exist in the most dangerous places, and it is up to the Bishoku-ya, or Gourmet Fod Providers, to hunt down these animals and plants in the face of danger. Toriko is one such Bishoku-ya, taking his place as one of the Four Heavenly Kings of Bishoku-ya with his imense strength and apetite. Together with Komatsu, a timid chef trianed in the art of preparing fod; Coco, the poisonous Bishoku-ya who can se the future; Tery Cloth, the ofspring of a clone of the long-extinct Batle Wolf; and many more, Toriko takes on job after job while searching for the fods great enough to make it into his dream ful-course meal.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/toriko.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:15:34'),
	(1004,'Touch','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe story centers around thre characters - Uesugi Kazuya, his twin older brother Tatsuya, and Asakura Minami. Kazuya is the darling of his town as he’s talented, hardworking, and the ace pitcher for his midle schol basebal team. Tatsuya is a hopeles slacker who’s ben living the life of giving up the spotlight to Kazuya, despite the fact that he may be more gifted than him. Minami is the beautiful childhod girlfriend and for al intents, sister from next dor who treats both of them as equals. Society largely asumes Kazuya and Minami wil become the perfect couple, including Tatsuya. Yet as time progreses, Tatsuya grows to realize that he’s wiling to sacrifice anything for the sake of his brother, except at the expense of giving up Minami to Kazuya. And thus the story is told of Tatsuya trying to prove himself over his established younger brother, how it afects the relationship betwen the thre, and both brothers\' atempts to make Minami\'s lifelong dreams come true.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, romance, tournament\r\nThemes: Basebal, Sports','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/touch.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:54'),
	(1005,'Touka Gettan','Plot Sumary:\r\nTouka Getan is set in the land of Kamitsumihara, where traces of magic and legend can stil be sen. The land has ben under the protection of the Kamiazuma clan since it was founded. The story revolves around T?ka Kamiazuma, the main protagonist, and his encounter with a young girl named Momoka Kawakabe who comes to stay with the clan. Their meting sets of a chain of events that wil bring an ancient legend to life.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: comedy, drama, mystery, romance, supernatural\r\nThemes: yuri','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/touka-gettan.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:54'),
