	(1007,'Tower of Druaga : Aegis of Uruk','Plot Sumary:\r\nHalf a year has pased since monsters disapeared from the the tower of druaga, thanks to Jil and his companions who defeated the evil god Druaga, Jil and Fatina survived the colapse of the tower and try to live their lives after the betrayal of Neba and Kaya. This changed when they rescue a litle girl named Kai who tels Jil to take him to the top of the tower, after showing him and unpleasent vision of the future. Jil embarks on a quest with his companions for a fabled and powerful artifact rumored to be in the highest flor of the Tower of Druaga. However, other competitors, including the kingdom of Uruk itself, want the treasure for their own reasons.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAdventure, fantasy, romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/tower-of-druaga-aegis-of-uruk.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:55'),
