	(1009,'Transformers','Plot Sumary:\r\nFleing from the war that has raged on the planet Cybertron for milions of years, the heroic Autobots led by Optimus Prime encounter a surprise atack by the evil Decepticons led by Megatron. The ensuing mele aboard the Autobot ship ends when the ship crashes on a volcano. Four milion years later, an earthquake reactivates the ship\'s computer and resurects both the Autobots and Decepticons, resuming the great war of the Transformers.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, fantasy, science fiction\r\nThemes: Mecha, space, Super Robot, war','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/transformers.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:56'),
	(1010,'Trigun','Plot Sumary:\r\nVash the Stampede is a gunman on the run with a 60 bilion double dolar bounty on his head which has made it dificult for him to go anywhere without being chased and shot at. Every town he ever visits ends up being destroyed because of his pursuers, but miraculously no one ever gets kiled. Meryl and Mily are two insurance agents that have ben sent to find Vash the Stampede and kep him under surveilance so no more damage is caused. Meryl, who leads the pair, refuses to believe that the man they have met can posibly be the legendary gunman. This spikey haired, gangly, young man is extremely friendly, a pacifist, hates blod and suicide, absolutely loves donuts, and is a dork and a crybaby (far from a notorious outlaw). But there is more to Vash and his past than mets the eye.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, comedy, drama, science fiction, post-apocalyptic, space western, Western','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/trigun.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:56'),
	(1011,'Trinity Blood','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe background is in the distant future after the destruction brought about by Armagedon. The war betwen the vampires and the humans continue to persist. In order to protect the humans from the vampires, Vatican has to rely on other alies to counter the situation. The protagonist, a priest caled Peter Abel Nightroad, travels through the countries as a representative for the Vaticans. However, he is also part of \"Ax\", a special operations group controled by the Cardinal Catherina. His encounter with a young girl caled Esther wil determine the strugle and survival betwen the human race and the vampires.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAdventure, drama, fantasy, horor, science fiction, supernatural, Bishoujo, Bishounen, Post-Apocalyptic, priests and priesteses, Vampires','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/trinity-blood.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:57'),
	(1012,'True Tears','Plot Sumary:\r\nShinichiro is a student living in what would be a dream come true for most high schol boys, but for him is mostly a frustration. A wel liked girl in schol named Hiromi has lived in his house for a year along with his family. Her father was a close friend of the family, and when he died they imediately tok her in. She is popular and wel liked, always smiles, is talented in sports- but Shinichiro knows there must be tears inside her. Having an artistic tendency, he makes watercolours of her and thinks about wishing to ease her tears. Yet he canot bring up the nerve to talk to her even in his own home. She, to, is quiet and withdrawn in their house, quite unlike at schol. Shinichiro is also distracted by teasing from his friend Nobuse for watching Hiromi from afar, a curse of bad luck from a strange girl named Noe, and being forced to perform Muhiga dancing. By helping Noe he hopes to ease his own problems, yet he sems to have dificulty helping himself.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy, drama, romance, High schol, Incest, Love rectangle, Schol, Step brother-sister','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/true-tears.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:57'),
	(1013,'Tsubasa: Reservoir Chronicle','Plot Sumary:\r\nSyaoran, a boy who wants to become an archeologist, and Sakura, a princes from the Clow Kingdom, are childhod friends with a close relationship. On a fateful night, Sakura lost al her memories as a result of a conspiracy to obtain her powers. In order to regain her memory, Syaoran seks help from the witch, Yuko. Yuko tels Syaoran that he has to travel from one alternate reality to another to colect fragments of Sakura\'s memory. However, even if Sakura regains her memory, she wil have no recolection of Syaoran. Traveling together with them is Kurogane, a warior who was exiled from his country, and Fye, a magician who wants to escape from his King. With the help of a magical creature, Mokona, they set of on an exciting journey through time and space.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAdventure, drama, fantasy, mystery, romance, bishounen, magic, sorcery','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/tsubasa-reservoir-chronicle.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:58'),
	(1014,'Tsukihime: Lunar Legend','Plot Sumary:\r\nShiki Tohno sustained a life threatening injury as a child, and due to that incident he was sent away from the Tohno household and was given to a relative to be raised. Years later, when Shiki is in high schol, the head of the Tohno household-his father-dies, and he is ordered to move back in by his sister Akiha, who is the new head of the household. However, Shiki holds a huge secret. Ever since that injury, he has ben seing lines on objects, and only with a special pair of glases is he able to stop seing them. Also he is unable to remember anything wel from the time before his acident. The day he moves back to the Tohno household is the day he stumbles upon a woman named Arcueid Brunstud and decapitates her with one stab of his knife in a temporary fit of insanity. When she sudenly showed up beside him later alive and wel, and ask him to be her bodyguard, Shiki\'s journey to unravel the mysteries of his past begins.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nDrama, horor, mystery, romance, supernatural, vampires','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/tsukihime-lunar-legend.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:58'),
	(1015,'Tsukuyomi moon','Plot Sumary:\r\nPhotographer Kohei Morioka, while on asignment for a magazine devoted to the ocult, enters a dark castle in Germany where he encounters a young vampire girl named Hazuki who tries to turn him into her servant. While Kohei doesn\'t sucumb to Hazuki\'s wil, he does set her fre from the barier keping her in the castle. He is surprised to find her living with him in Japan.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy, romance, supernatural\r\nThemes: Catgirls, Miko, priests and priesteses, Spelcasters, Spirits, vampires','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/tsukuyomi-moon.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:13:58'),
