	(1019,'Uchuu no Stellvia','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe year is 2356 A.D. - 189 years after a distant supernova caused a global catastrophe that wiped out 9% of the world population. To kep track on al space activities, mankind has built colosal space stations caled \"foundations\" al over the Solar System. After pasing the Space Academy entrance exams, Shima Katase embarks to the Earth-based foundation Stelvia to fulfil her dream of seing the galaxy and to prevent another interstelar catastrophe from destroying Earth.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, drama, romance, science fiction\r\nThemes: Mecha, Space','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/uchuu-no-stellvia.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:14:00'),
	(1020,'UFO Ultramaiden Valkyrie','Plot Sumary:\r\nPrinces Valkyrie crashlands on Earth like any other alien, except she lands on Kazuto, a smal time bath-house owner. To save him from death she gives him part of her soul. However loaning your soul does have its ups and downs. Having halved her soul Valkyrie has reverted into her child self. Kazuto and friends, with a spaceship crashed on his bath-house, must now deal with everyday chalenges and trouble while trying to figure out how to get Valkyrie back to normal. including more crash landings.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: comedy, magic, romance, science fiction\r\nThemes: catgirls','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ufo-ultramaiden-valkyrie.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:14:01'),
	(1021,'Ultimate Girls','Plot Sumary:\r\nDuring a monster atack on the city, which is something that hapens quite often, Silk and her two friends try get close to the atacking monster for a beter view. An unfortunate choice of location to watch from leads to UFO-man, the city’s giant protector, to land on the girls crushing them to death. Feling sory, UFO-man blames their death on the monster and promises to bring Silk and her friends back to life by lending them his power but the catch is that they now have to become the city’s protector as wel.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, magic, science fiction\r\nThemes: echi, fanservice','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ultimate-girls.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:14:01'),
	(1022,'Ultimate Muscle: The Kinnikuman Legacy','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the past evil superhumans invaded earth to conquer the human race. A group of superhuman caling themselves the muscle league chalenge the evil. One of the muscle league member, King Muscle displayed great strength and skil. With his help the muscle league defeated the evil and once again peace retuned to earth. 28 years later a new evil force has come to conquer the human race, but legendary heros who fought in the past were to weak and old to beat the new threat. Now they trained a new league of wariors to fight. One of the wariors is Kid Muscle the son of the legendary King Muscle. He and the new generation are the only hope for the human race against the new threat.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, comedy, science fiction, tournament\r\nThemes: Wrestling','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ultimate-muscle-the-kinnikuman-legacy.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:14:01'),
	(1023,'Ultra Maniac','Plot Sumary:\r\nNina Sakura, a young, clumsy witch travels from the magic kingdom to colect the five holy stones to win as the princes candidate, competing with her childhod friend,Maya Orihara. But eventualy, she develops new friendships in this world with people like Ayu Tateishi, Kaji Tetsushi, Tsujiai Hiroki. She also helps Ayu and Kaji to form a couple.Then she faces the dilema, whether to stay here or return to the world she belongs to.\r\n \r\nNina, a young girl from the Magic Kingdom, is a candidate for princes. She travels to Earth to search for Holy Stones required for her to be qualified as a candidate. On Earth, she mets Ayu Tateishi, who right away discovered her magical powers and who eventualy became her best friend. They continue their friendship as Ayu further learns about Nina\'s mision. Finaly, she colected the 5 Holy Stones. However, a dilema then came: Nina canot decipher on what road wil she take - to become a princes, or remain on Earth with her friends.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, magic, romance\r\nThemes: Magical Girl','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/ultra-maniac.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:14:02'),
