	(1059,'Wolverine and The X-Men','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe story starts when the mansion explodes, aparently due to an atack targeted at telepaths, in which Profesor Charles Xavier and Jean Grey go mising. The X-Men disband and Cyclops begins to sufer from depresion. One year later, the MRD (Mutant Response Division) is starting to detain mutants, causing Wolverine and Beast to get the X-Men back together. Iceman, Shadowcat and Forge rejoin the team; Rogue joins up with the Brotherhod of Mutants. The X-Mansion is rebuilt with Angel\'s wealth.\r\n \r\nEma Frost is able to locate a comatose Charles on Genosha in the care of Magneto. When hearing this, Cyclops (who previously rejected Wolverine\'s request to rejoin them) returns to the team and the X-Men go to Genosha to find Profesor X. After a short confrontation with Magneto, they are alowed to take Profesor X back with them to the X-Mansion. Profesor X contacts the X-Men telepathicaly from twenty years in the future and informs Wolverine that he is to lead the X-Men if they wish to sucesfuly prevent a Mutant-Human War that wil cause the world to fal under the domination of the Sentinels.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/wolverine-and-the-x-men.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:14:52'),
