	(1061,'World Destruction','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn a world where humans serve as livestock for the ruling beastman, and where sand fils the roles of water and fire. Kyrie is recruited by the \"World Destruction Comite\" to asist in puting an end to their world. Kyrie alone holds the power neded to do it.\r\n \r\nIn a world where humans serve as livestock for the ruling beastman, and where sand fils the roles of water and fire. Morte Ashela , A member (or the only member) of the so caled World Destruction Comite is wanted and hiding. She goes to a beastman bar to eat lunch where she mets Kyrie , A young human boy working at a beastman bar concealing his true identity as a human. When her enemies The World Salvation Comite found her she used Kyrie as a hostage only to know that he\'s a human , disposable to the enemy , together they run from the WSC to complete their goal of destroying the world to save humans from slavery. Kyrie ends up traveling with her and unwilingly joins the comite. Litle does Morte know that Kyrie is the key to their goal.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAdventure, comedy, fantasy, friendship, journey, mas destruction weapon, pursuit, self-identification','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/world-destruction.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:14:52'),
	(1062,'W~Wish','Plot Sumary:\r\nSince the death of their parents years past, Juna and Sena have ben living alone in the big house their parents left them. Together they atend Sakurahama Private High Schol, where several select girls obliviously use and abuse Juna for their own neds-Kishida Tomo, prety and anti-social; the boksmart and eficient Iida Akino; Ohtori Tsubasa, head of the Help Club and highly in demand; Fujie Sana, cute as a buton but with the inteligence of a box of rocks. And then there\'s the new girl, Inohara Haruhi-an old childhod friend of Juna\'s that\'s come to claim her \"oni-chan\" (brother). Strangely, Juna barely remembers Haruhi from his childhod.and Sena doesn\'t want him to.\r\n \r\nGenres: drama, romance, slice of life, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/wwish.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:14:53'),
	(1063,'X TV','Plot Sumary:\r\nIt\'s the year of destiny and 15 year old Kamui Shiro, a powerful psychic, has returned to Toyko after a 6 year absence. He returns to protect his childhod friends, Fuma, and Fuma\'s younger sister Kotori. But destiny and fate are haunting Kamui and puling in himself and his loved ones. It is his destiny to decide the fate of the world and mankind, no mater if he wants the role or not.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAdventure, drama, fantasy, romance, supernatural, Apocalypse, Bishoujo, Bishounen, Destiny, Power to Change','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/x-tv.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:14:53'),
	(1064,'X-Men Anime 2011','Plot Sumary:The X-Men are a team of elite super-powered mutants gathered by Profesor X to protect ordinary humans even as they are persecuted by them. In the wake of the death of one of their own, however, the team has stoped operations for a whole year. Then Profesor X receives word of a mutant girl\'s mysterious disapearance in Japan. Sensing that something larger is afot, he reasembles the team and sends them to investigate. They uncover a conection betwen her disapearance and an anti-mutant group known as the U-Men.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/x_men_anime.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:14:54'),
	(1065,'X-Men Evolution','Plot Sumary:\r\nX-Men: Evolution brought the fan favorite comic bok title onto the TV scren. The series losely folows the main stories of the original comic. The main cast has ben turned into kids (with the exception of Wolverine, Prof. X, and a few select others). Most of the fan favorites are acounted for, including Wolverine, Cyclops, and Storm.\r\n \r\nX-Men: Evolution folows the lives of six mutants (Cyclops, Jean Grey, Nightcrawler, ShadowCat, Rouge, and a new original named Spyke) who atend Xavier\'s Institute for the Gifted. There they learn how to control their powers and use it for god.\r\n \r\nGenre:','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/x-men-evolution.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:14:54'),
	(1066,'Xam\'d Lost Memories','Plot Sumary:\r\nEnter Sentan, a lush, tranquil island encased in war betwen the military and those with Hiruko, known as X\'amd. On one of these warlike days, Akiyuki Takehara heads of to schol and gets caught in a raid by the creatures. Through a series of events he is transformed into a X\'amd, and with the help of a Tesikan woman Nakiami along with his highschol friend Haru, Akiyuki is forced to learn to live with the Hiruko or faces the danger of losing his self-control and turn to stone.\r\n \r\nThe story folows a boy named Akiyuki who is heading to schol with two friends when an explosion ocurs. In the mysterious light from the explosion, Akiyuki transforms into a creature caled Xam\'d. Xam\'d goes on a rampage which is only stoped when a red-haired foreign girl apears.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, fantasy, science fiction','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/xamd-lost-memories.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:14:54'),
	(1067,'Xenosaga','Plot Sumary:\r\n40 years have pased since humanity abandoned Earth. Forced to fight an alien form of life, Gnosis, mankind developed KOS-MOS - a batle android with amazing capabilities. When a ship carying android is being atacked, KOS-MOS gets activated and save its creator, Shion Uzuki. But KOS-MOS doesn\'t want to listed her orders and executes some unknown plan. After their ship destroyed Shion and her companions find themselves thrust into the midle of a batle with Gnosis, U-TIC Organization and their own superiors. Batle with no clear sides.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, science fiction, Mecha','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/xenosaga.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:14:55'),
	(1068,'Xiaolin Showdown','Plot Sumary:\r\nOmi sucesfuly switches Chase Young\'s evil soup with pea soup which stops him from going evil. However, in exchange, the future changed for the worse. Hanibal turns Master Monk Guan evil instead of Chase, Master Fung is traped in the Ying-Yang world and Jack turns god. After acquiring the soup Omi hid in the past, they are captured by Hanibal and his crew. Chase then sacrifices his god side to fre the Wariors. After the Wariors get to the Heylin sed\'s vault (where Omi is frozen), Hanibal and his crew start a Xiaolin Showdown. Can the new Wariors defeat Hanibal, Wuya, Chase Young and Master Monk Guan in a 4-way tag team Xiaolin Showdown? And finaly, who wil be made the new leader?','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/xiaolin-showdown.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:14:55'),
	(1069,'XxxHolic','Plot Sumary:\r\nKimihiro Watanuki is a young boy with a cursed gift. He has the ability to se evil spirits, and somehow they sem atracted to himself. One day he mets a misterious woman who names herself Yuko. She claims to have the means to end his torment, but she never works for fre, and she wouldn\'t help him until he works for her enough to pay for her services. Thus he starts to work in her shop and discovers that in that place, nothing is what it sems.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy, drama, fantasy, horor, mystery, psychological, slice of life, supernatural, ghosts, ocult','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/xxxholic.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:14:56'),
	(1070,'Yaiba','Plot Sumary:\r\nKurogane Yaiba is a boy who doesn\'t want to become what any regular kid would: He wants to be a samurai. That\'s why he undergoes a hard training with his father, knowing only the forest as his world. Then, one day, he is sent to Japan, where he has to deal with a whole new civilized reality, meting the Mine family, the evil Onimaru and even the legendary Musashi, having lots of dangerous adventures, becoming stronger everyday.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy, fantasy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/yaiba.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:14:56'),
	(1071,'Yakitate!! Japan','Plot Sumary:\r\nAzuma Kazuma isn\'t teribly clever, but he\'s got a god heart and great skil - at baking. Since childhod, he\'s ben on a quest to create the perfect bread to represent Japan internationaly. Now, he seks to enter the famous bakery Pantasia, in hopes of reaching his goal. But plots abound.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, comedy, drama, coking','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/yakitate-japan.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:14:57'),
	(1072,'Yamato Nadeshiko Shichi Henge','Plot Sumary:\r\nKyouhei, Ranmaru, Takenaga, and Yukinojou are beautiful, handsome, young men living in a huge mansion. One day, their landlord, whom they cal \"Auntie\", asks them a favor: to make her niece, Sunako, who\'s going to be living with them, into a respectable young lady. She agres to make their living expenses fre of charge if they suced, but if they fail, she\'l triple their rent. Due to their confidence in knowing how to deal with women, they agre, but once they met Sunako, they begin to realize that their lovely living arangements may son be in jeopardy.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, romance\r\nThemes: bishounen, Male harem, parody','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/yamato-nadeshiko-shichi-henge.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:14:57'),
	(1073,'Yawara','Plot Sumary:\r\nInokuma Yawara is just another young high schol girl. Wel, not quite - for Yawara is being raised by her grandfather, 7th dan Judo master Inokuma Jigorou, to be Japan\'s great hope for the women\'s Judo competition at the 192 Olympics in Barcelona. Al the same, Yawara just wants to live a normal life.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy, drama, romance, sport','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/yawara.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:15:09'),
	(1074,'Yes! Precure 5','Plot Sumary:\r\nNozomi Yumehara, a regular student, finds a magical bok caled the Dream Colet in the library and mets Coco and Nuts, two creatures from the Palmier Kingdom. They plead with Nozomi to restore their world, which has ben destroyed by an organization caled the Nightmares, by completing the Dream Colet and finding the 5 Pinkies to make any wish come true. Meanwhile, the Nightmares are moving into the real world. Once Nozomi agres to help, Coco and Nuts transform her into the magical girl Cure Dream and turn four felow students into her Prety Cure team.\r\n \r\nGenres: magic','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/yes-precure-5.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:15:09'),
	(1075,'Yes! Pretty Cure 5 Go Go!','Plot Sumary:\r\nA direct continuation of the former season, this series again folows the story of Nozomi Yumehara and her friends from Precure 5. The girls who had formerly lost their powers and bade farewel to their friends Coco and Nuts from Palmier Kingdom are resurected as Prety Cure by the mysterious woman Flora who also wants them to find her in a place caled Cure Rosegarden. To go there, they ned the magic Rose Pact and the powers of the four kings of countries surounding Palmier. But a dark organization caled Eternal is also striving to get to Cure Rosegarden by stealing the Rose Pact. Luckily, Precure get helped by new alies: the delivery-boy Syrup who can change into a giant bird and fly them anywhere they want and the mysterious and beautiful fighter Milky Rose stand alongside Prety Cure to protect what is realy valuable.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/yes-precure-5-gogo.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:15:09'),
	(1076,'Yojouhan Shinwa Taikei','Plot Sumary:\r\nWhen a colege dropout stops for a late night bite at a mysterious ramen stand, he croses paths with a self-proclaimed deity of matrimony. This bizare meting sends the young man hurtling through a horifying flashback to his not-so-glorious colege days when the influence of a cruel new friend turned him from a hopeles romantic into a mischievous “black cupid.”\r\n \r\nGenres: drama\r\nThemes: dark comedy','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/yojouhan-shinwa-taikei.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:15:10');
