	(1077,'Yoku Wakaru Gendai Mahou','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe story revolves around Koyomi Morishita, a clumsy high schol freshman girl who is often mistaken for a grade-scholer because of her shortnes. Koyomi becomes a disciple of Misa Anehara, a 25-year-old graduate student who hapens to be one of the most powerful modern-day magicians.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, magic','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/yoku-wakaru-gendai-mahou.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:15:10'),
	(1078,'Yomigaeru Sora Rescue Wings','Plot Sumary:\r\nKazuhiro Uchida is transfered to a rescue centre located in a smal town while training to become a fighter pilot. Initialy, Kazuhiro thinks negatively about his new ocupation, due to the dificult misions and the harsh discipline he receives from his seniors. However, over the course of his training, he begins to acept the job for what it is and becomes a true member of the rescue force.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nDrama, Military','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/yomigaeru-sora-rescue-wings.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:15:11'),
