	(1080,'Yosuga no Sora','Plot Sumary:\r\nHaving lost both parents, the Kazugano twins, Haruka and Sora, decided to move in and live with their grandfather of whom they are fond of. Other motives, however, contributed to their decision to reside at their grandfather.\r\n \r\nGenres: romance\r\nThemes: Harem, incest','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/yosuga-no-sora.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:15:11'),
	(1081,'You\'re Under Arrest','Plot Sumary:\r\nNatsumi and Miyuki are policewomen at the Bokuto Police Station. This story recounts the exploits and adventures they have in dealing with the strange characters they are forced to deal with \'al in a day\'s work\'.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy\r\nThemes: police','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/youre-under-arrest.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:15:12'),
	(1082,'You\'re Under Arrest Mini Special','Plot Sumary:\r\nBest friends and partners Miyuki Kobayakawa and Natsumi Sujimoto, along with the rest of the gang at Bokuto station, confront a motley group of ofenders ranging from hi-tech panty thieves, purse-snatchers, and trafic violators. Using Miyuki\'s driving prowes and tech knowledge, as wel as Natsumi\'s spunk and strength, the duo at times must resort to unconventional methods to se that justice is served.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, comedy\r\nThemes: Police','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/youre-under-arrest-mini-special.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:15:12'),
	(1083,'Yozakura Quartet','Plot Sumary:\r\nThe story revolves around a quartet of tenaged heroes: A super-strong girl named Hime, a mind reader named Ao, a conjurer named Kotoha and an ordinary, powerles boy named Akina. The thre girls and Akina protect the city of Sakurashin from supernatural threats.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, comedy, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/yozakura-quartet.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:15:13'),
	(1084,'Yu Yu Hakusho','Plot Sumary:\r\nOne day, 14 year old Yusuke Urameshi sudenly finds himself dead, having died pushing a child out of the way of oncoming trafic. Since he has such a bad personality, even the Spirit World was caught by surpise that he would sacrifice himself. Yusuke son finds out he wasn\'t suposed to die and has a chance for resurection and bringing his body back to life. After being resurected, Yusuke becomes a Spirit Detective, along with his comrades, and one adventure after another hapens, whether it be an investigation or a fighting tournament.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, comedy, drama, supernatural, tournament','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/yu-yu-hakusho.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:15:13'),
	(1085,'Yu-Gi-Oh!','Plot Sumary:\r\nYugioh Series Zero is another version of Duel monsters. 4Kids considered this series of Yugioh to be “to violent” and was never released outside of japan or dubed in English. This series starts of earlier in the Manga than that of Duel Monsters, giving us more of a background into where Yugi found his milenial puzle and a few other things before it gets to the card game that Yugioh is famous for.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, drama, fantasy\r\nThemes: Card Games, Monsters','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/yugioh-season-0.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:15:14'),
	(1086,'Yu-Gi-Oh! 5D’s','Plot Sumary:\r\nMany years in the future after the exploits of Yugi Mutou, Domino City has become a shadow of its former self: Neo Domino City. There lies a strong divide betwen the rich and the por, and bridging that gap proves to be dificult. Neo Domino sems fit to entertain itself with a wild new event caled \"Riding Duels\", the newest form of playing the ever popular Duel Monsters card game. Enter Yusei Fudou, a young man who lives on the edge of the law, making his own rules. His desire to reclaim what is rightly his from an old friend turns into much more than what he and many of his newfound companions caled \"Signers\" would have ever bargained for.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/yu-gi-oh-5ds.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:15:14'),
	(1087,'Yu-Gi-Oh! Capsule Monsters','Plot Sumary:\r\nCapsule Monsters involves Yugi, Joey (Jonouchi), Téa (Anzu), Tristan (Honda), and Yugi\'s grandfather Solomon (Sugoroku) being puled into a world where Duel Monsters are real. They find monster capsules that they can use to sumon monsters. It is similar to the Virtual RPG arc in many respects, but it doesn\'t sem to have anything to do with the early Capsule Monster Ches game.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy\r\nThemes: Cards, Monsters, Other Worlds','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/yugiohcapsule-monsters.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:15:14'),
	(1088,'Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Monsters','Plot Sumary:\r\n30 Years ago marked the turning point of an Egyptian Dynasty; the Pharaoh\'s spirit was sealed inside one of the ancient relics, the Milenium Puzle, after saving the kingdom from an enemy army. Now, in the present age, the Milenium Puzle is found by a young boy, Yugi Mutou, who unlocks the spirit of the puzle and is posesed by the sprit of the old Pharaoh, who lost al of his memories from his old life. As a thank you to the spirit who saved him from bulies and gave him new friends, Yugi decided to help the spirit out and find a way to recover his lost memories and send him to the after life.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, drama, fantasy\r\nThemes: Card Games, Monsters','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/yugioh-duel-monsters.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:15:15'),
	(1089,'Yu-Gi-Oh! GX','Plot Sumary:\r\nSet a generation into the future, Yu-Gi-Oh! GX revolves around a boy named Jaden Yuki as he begins his life at Duel Academy, owned by Kaiba Corp. While runing late for his entrance exams, Jaden bumps into Yugi Muto, the King of Games! Seing a Duel Disk and deck, Yugi thinks he must be a duelist, Jaden confirms this as he says he\'s on his way for his entrance exams for the Duel Academy. Yugi decides to give him a Winged Kuriboh card, saying it is a lucky card, and he wishes Jaden luck on his exams as he runs of.\r\n \r\nAs Jaden enters the schol, he befriends Alexis Rhodes, Syrus Truesdale, Bastion Misawa, Zane Truesdale, and Chaz Princeton. Together they experience many adventures while trying to stop evil from spreading!\r\n \r\nThere are thre dorms in Duel Academy, Obelisk Blue for the Elite, Ra Yelow for those with potential, and Slifer Red, for the drop outs','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/yu-gi-oh-gx.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:15:15'),
	(1090,'Yu-Gi-Oh! Zexal','Plot Sumary:The story takes place in the distant future and focuses on a boy named Yuma Tsukumo, the number one bad boy at his schol. Something unexpected hapens when Ryoga chalenges him to a Duel as the mysterious ghost of Astral apears before them, a new legend begins.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/yu-gi-oh-zexal.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:15:16'),
	(1091,'Yumeiro Patissiere','Plot Sumary:\r\nThis series tels the story of 14 year old Ichigo Amano, a clumsy girl who dreams of becoming a pastry chef. She draws closer to fulfiling her dream when she enrols in the St. Mary Academy culinary schol and mets a tiny “spirit of swets.” \r\n \r\nGenres: fantasy, romance\r\nThemes: coking, schol life','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/yumeiro-patissiere.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:15:16'),
