	(1093,'Yumeria','Plot Sumary:\r\nOn his 16th birthday, Tomokazu Mikuri had a realistic dream where he ses a girl batling a giant floating monstrosity. When he wakes up, he is surprised that the girl is actualy sleping next to him. Whenever he sleps from now on, he ends up back at the dream world, and more and more people that he knows kep showing up there to. He finds out from a mysterious masked woman in the dream world named Silk that they are fighting against one named Faydom, and he is the one who provides the powers to those girls so that they can fight these monsters. And so it goes.\r\n \r\n\r\nGenres: action, comedy, magic, romance','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/yumeria.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:15:17'),
