	(1095,'Zaion: I Wish You Were Here','Plot Sumary:\r\nIn the future, a meteor crashes into Earth and brings with it a virulent form of life. This virus is known as M34 and atacks humans, turning them into vicious monsters. Most of the human population is wiped out, thus government agencies are formed to fight the virus. One of the groups, NOA, inserts nanomachines into the bodies of its soldiers; these machines alow them to transform and fight of the infected. Unfortunately, the virus mutates and becomes to strong for NOA to handle. Now the fate of the world rests in the hands of 16-year-old girl with the power to defeat the virus.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nDrama, romance, science fiction','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/zaion-i-wish-you-were-here.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:00','2012-03-07 02:15:18'),
	(1096,'Zan Sayonara Zetsubou Sensei','Plot Sumary:\r\nItoshiki Nozomu is the world\'s most negative person. To his way of thinking, there is no hope or meaning in this existence. Even the thre kanji of his name become the two-kanji word zetsubou, \"despair\", when compresed. What an ironic twist of fate, then, that he becomes teacher to a clas containing his precise oposite, the invincibly positive-minded Fura Kafuka.\r\n \r\nGenres: comedy, drama, slice of life\r\nThemes: harem, parody, schol, suicide','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/zan-sayonara-zetsubou-sensei.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:01','2012-03-07 02:15:18'),
	(1097,'Zatch Bell','Plot Sumary:\r\nTakamine Kiyomaro, a depresed don\'t-care-about-the-world guy, was sudenly given a litle demon named Gash Bel to take care of. Litle does he know that Gash is embroiled into an intense fight to se who is the ruler of the demon world. Al of the demons have to pick a master on Earth and duke it out with other demons until one survives. Nedles to say, Kiyomaro becomes Gash\'s master, and through their many batles, Kiyomaro learns the importance of friendship and courage.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, drama, supernatural, tournament','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/konjiki-no-gash-bell.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:01','2012-03-07 02:15:18'),
	(1098,'Zegapain','Plot Sumary:\r\nKyo, an avid swimer tries his best to kep the high schol swiming club going, which is prety hard when he\'s the only member. Facing the prospect of the club being closed by the student council, he tries to enlist beautiful Misaki to act in a promo video, shot by his god friend Ryoko, in a bid to start a recruitment drive. She agres but only if he pilots a mecha under the wing of Celebrum, a resistance organisation fighting to destroy Deutera Areas formed on Earth by the aliens Gards-orm. He agres but finds it al strangely familiar as if he\'s done it before.\r\n \r\nGenres: drama, mystery, romance, science fiction\r\nThemes: Mecha','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/zegapain.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:01','2012-03-07 02:15:19'),
	(1099,'Zero no Tsukaima','Plot Sumary:\r\nMet Louise, a buding magician. The students at the Tristein Academy cal her \"Zero Louise\", due to her curent record of zero suceses with magic. In fact, her magic tends to go spectacularly wrong. Now, as an important test of her aptitude for magic, she must sumon a familiar to be her servant. At this critical moment, she sumons up al her magic and wishes for a familiar that is \"devoted, beautiful and powerful\", and gets. Hiraga Saito, an ordinary Japanese boy. It\'s dificult to say who is more surprised and dismayed, but the rules don\'t alow for second atempts. Louise is stuck with her strange familiar, and he with her.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, comedy, magic, romance\r\nThemes: dragons, harem, Magical girl, schol','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/zero-no-tsukaima.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:01','2012-03-07 02:15:19'),
	(1100,'Zoids','Plot Sumary:\r\nPlanet Zi, a world where warior bio-machine lifeforms caled Zoids live. They are controled by human pilots in a war with the Republic and the Guylos Empire. One day a boy named Van being cased by bandits hides in some old ruins, he finds two pods in a hiden rom & opens one to find out its an od dragon-like Zoid caled an Organoid which he names Zeke. Zeke then resurects an old dead blue Shield Liger Zoid for Van to pilot. When Van opens the 2nd pod a very mysterious girl named Fiona comes out of it. They go on the adventure to find more about her past & to find the Zoid Eve, they met new friends & they get into some serious problems including the war which they try to stop.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, comedy, drama, science fiction\r\nThemes: Mecha, Real Robot','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/zoid-chaotic-century.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:01','2012-03-07 02:15:20'),
	(1101,'Zoids Genesis','Plot Sumary:\r\nNatural disasters have devastated planet Zi, kiling of almost al life. A thousand years later humans have gradualy re-established civilization, salvaging ancient Zoids through diving and mining eforts. In a vilage whose most previous item is a giant sword which they worship as a holy symbol. A tenage boy discovers an ancient Liger-type Zoid while on a dep water salvage operation. Sudenly the vilage is atacked by skeletal Bio-Zoids intent on stealing a powerful generator located in the vilage. Our tenage hero awakens the Liger and discovers that the town\'s sacred sword is the Liger\'s weapon, together they fight of the mysterious Bio-Zoids. At least for now.\r\n \r\nGenres: adventure, comedy, science fiction\r\nThemes: Mecha, Military','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/zoids-genesis.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:01','2012-03-07 02:15:20'),
	(1102,'Zoids New Century Zero','Plot Sumary:\r\nNew Century Zero takes place a long time after the events of Zoids: Chaotic Century. Zoids are no longer used for warfare; instead the combative natures of both Zoids and humans are focused and contained by a series of batle-competitions and tournaments, run by the Zoid Batle Comision.\r\n\r\nThe Zoid Batle Comision sems to be a significant power on Planet Zi, fielding a considerable arsenal of armed Zoids, orbital platforms serviced by their own launch facilities as wel as orbital based weapons systems. It is not made clear in the series if the Helic Republic and Guylos Empire stil exist, although the final batle upon the rusted Ultrasaurus, hinted to be same one in Zoids: Chaotic Century, could sugest neither were left and people had fre rein to batle in old batlefields.','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/zoids-new-century-zero.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:01','2012-03-07 02:15:21'),
	(1103,'Zoids: Fuzors','Plot Sumary:\r\nR.D. is a delivery boy who works for a company caled Mach Storm in order to earn money to search for the legendary Alpha Zoid. A Zoid that he heard rumors about from his dad that he pasionately believes in. Mach Storm also doubles as a Zoid Batling team. In R.D.\'s first Coliseum Zoid Batle, he encounters a team that can fuse Zoids. R.D. son discovers that he has a Zoid that can compatably fuse with his Zoid, Liger Zero. After this hapens R.D.\'s adventure to discover the truth about the Alpha Zoid begins.\r\n \r\nGenres: action, adventure, science fiction\r\nThemes: mecha, real robot','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/zoids-fuzors.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:01','2012-03-07 02:15:21'),
	(1104,'Zoku Natsume Yuujinchou','Plot Sumary:\r\nNatsume is again meting new youkai and helping them. A lot of friends join him along the way, he mets others who can also se the spirits and at times they join forces to solve the latest mystery. As always, Nyanko-sensei is there to help Natsume on his quests.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nComedy, drama, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/zoku-natsume-yuujinchou.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:01','2012-03-07 02:15:21'),
	(1105,'Zombie Loan','Plot Sumary:\r\nMichiru Kita is a special girl who poseses Shinigami Eyes, which alows her to se a dark ring around a person\'s neck. This ring symbolizes the person\'s impending death; once they are marked to die, a gray line, which is invisible to normal people, apears on their neck, and once the ring turns completely black, the person dies. Chika Akatsuki and Shito Tachibana, two boys in her clas, both have black rings around their necks, but to her surprise, they are not yet dead. It is revealed that after a tragic acident that was suposed to kil them both, the two boys made a deal with a secret loan ofice caled the Zombie-Loan. In return for keping them alive, the two have to hunt zombies for the loan ofice. When Michiru gets involved with them, she finds that her life has just become more complicated.\r\n \r\nGenre:\r\nAction, adventure, comedy, drama, horor, supernatural','<img  src=\"http://www.gogoanime.com/images/zombie-loan.jpg\">','2012-03-06 19:02:01','2012-03-07 02:15:22'),
